\id JER - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h Jeremia
\toc1 Jeremia
\toc2 Jeremia
\toc3 Jer
\mt1 Jeremia
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Weche Jeremia wuod Hilkia, achiel kuom jodolo man Anathoth e piny Benjamin.
\v 2 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirone e higa mar apar gadek e loch Josia wuod Amon ruodh Juda,
\v 3 kendo kokalo e loch Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda, kodhi nyaka e dwe mar abich mar higa mar apar gachiel mar Zedekia wuod Josia ruodh Juda, sa mane joma odak Jerusalem dhi e twech.
\b
\s1 Luong Jeremia
\p 
\v 4 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona, kawacho niya,
\q1 
\v 5 “Kane pok achweyi e ich ne angʼeyi,
\q2 kane pok onywoli ne asewali tenge;
\q2 ne ayieri kaka janabi ne pinje.”
\p 
\v 6 Ne awacho niya, “Yaye, Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto, ok angʼeyo wuoyo; an mana rawera matin.”
\p 
\v 7 To Jehova Nyasaye nowachona niya, “Kik iwach ni, ‘An mana nyathi.’ Nyaka idhi ir ji duto maori irgi kendo iwach gimoro amora ma achiki.
\v 8 Kik iluorgi, nimar an kodi kendo abiro resoi,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\p 
\v 9 Eka Jehova Nyasaye norieyo bade kendo omulo dhoga mi owachona niya, “Koro, aseketo wechega e dhogi.
\v 10 Ne, kawuononi ayieri ewi ogendini kod pinjeruodhi mondo ipudhi kendo iyiechi, mondo ikethi kendo ilok loch, mondo iger kendo ipudhi.”
\p 
\v 11 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona niya: “En angʼo mineno, Jeremia?” Anto ne adwoke ni,
\p “Aneno bad yath mar oyungu.”
\p 
\v 12 Jehova Nyasaye nowachona niya, “Ineno kare, nimar arito mondo ane ni wachna ochopo kare.”
\p 
\v 13 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nochako birona kendo kopenjo niya, “En angʼo mineno?”
\p Anto ne adwoke niya, “Aneno agulu mayienyo, kolokore oa yo nyandwat.”
\p 
\v 14 Jehova Nyasaye nowachona, “Koa yo nyandwat masira ibiro ol kuom jogo duto modak e piny.
\v 15 Achiegni luongo ji duto mag pinje ma yo nyandwat,” Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\q1 Ruodhigi biro biro kendo giniket kom duongʼ-gi
\q2 e kar donjo mar dhorangeye Jerusalem;
\q1 gibiro monjo ohingini duto molwore
\q2 kendo monjo mier madongo duto mag Juda.
\q1 
\v 16 Abiro ngʼadone joga bura
\q2 nikech timbegi mamono mar jwangʼa,
\q1 kuom wangʼo ubani ne nyiseche mamoko
\q2 kendo lamo gima lwetgi oseloso.
\p 
\v 17 “Bed moikore! Chungʼ malo kendo wachnegi gimoro amora machiki. Kik iwe gibwogi, ka ok kamano to abiro bwogi e nyimgi.
\v 18 Kawuono aseketi dala maduongʼ mochiel motegno, kendo gi siro mar chuma kod ohinga mar mula mondo ogengʼne piny ngima, ma gin ruodhi mag Juda, jotende, jodolo mage kod ji duto mag pinyno.
\v 19 Gibiro kedo kodi to ok gini loyi, nimar an kodi kendo abiro resi,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\c 2
\s1 Israel ojwangʼo Nyasaye
\p 
\v 1 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona:
\v 2 “Dhi kendo igo milome ka Jerusalem winjo ni:
\b
\p “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Aparo kaka ne ichiwori kane in rawera,
\q1 ne ihera ka nyako moikore ne kend,
\q1 ne iluwo bangʼa kama
\q1 otimo ongoro,
\q2 e piny ma ok purie.
\q1 
\v 3 Israel ne en oganda maler ne Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 kaka olembege mokwongo chiek;
\q1 jogo duto mane okidhe nomak kaka joketho,
\q2 kendo masira nomakogi,’ ”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 4 Winj wach Jehova Nyasaye, yaye od Jakobo,
\q2 un dhoudi duto mag dhood Israel.
\p 
\v 5 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “En ketho mane mane wuoneu oyudo kuoma,
\q2 momiyo ne gibaro mabor koda?
\q1 Negiluwo bangʼ nyiseche manono
\q2 mi gibedo manono gin giwegi.
\q1 
\v 6 Ne ok gipenjo ni, ‘Ere Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 mane ogolowa Misri,
\q1 kendo otelonwa e thim ma ok nyag gimoro,
\q2 ka wakalo piny motwo kod piny motimo bugni,
\q1 piny ongoro kod mudho,
\q2 piny maonge ngʼama wuothoe,
\q2 kendo onge ngʼama odakie?’
\q1 
\v 7 Ne akelou e piny momewo
\q2 mondo ucham olembege kod nyak mage momewo.
\q1 To ne ubiro mi unjawo pinya
\q2 kendo umiyo girkeni maga obedo gima odwanyore.
\q1 
\v 8 Jodolo ne ok openjo,
\q2 ‘Ere Jehova Nyasaye?’
\q1 Jogo matiyo gi chik ne ok ongʼeya;
\q2 jotelo nongʼanyona.
\q1 Jonabi nokoro gi Baal,
\q2 ka giluwo nyiseche manono.”
\b
\q1 
\v 9 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Emomiyo abiro kumou kendo.
\q2 Bende abiro kumo nyikwau.
\q1 
\v 10 Dhiuru loka e dho nembe mag Kitim
\q2 kendo ungʼigi kaka gichalo,
\q1 bende oruru ji Kedar mondo ginon maber;
\q2 mondo gine anena ka gima chal kama nosebetie:
\q1 
\v 11 Bende ogendini oseloko nyiseche nyaka nene?
\q1 (Kata kamano bende ok gin nyiseche.)
\q2 To joga osewilo duongʼ mar Nyasachgi,
\q2 gi nyiseche manono maonge tiendgi.
\q1 
\v 12 Kuom mano, agolonu chik, un polo,
\q2 mondo uyiengni malich, kuwuoro kendo kudhier nono,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 13 “Joga osetimo richo ariyo:
\q1 Gisejwangʼa,
\q2 an thidhna mar pi ngima,
\q1 kendo gisekunyo degnigi giwegi,
\q2 degni mobarore kendo ma ok nyal tingʼo pi.
\q1 
\v 14 Bende Israel en jatich,
\q2 ngʼat monywol ka misumba?
\q2 Kare en angʼo momiyo iyake?
\q1 
\v 15 Sibuoche oseruto;
\q2 kendo gisemorne.
\q1 Giseketho pinye;
\q2 dalane owangʼ kendo odongʼ gunda.
\q1 
\v 16 Bende, jo-Memfis gi jo-Tapanhes
\q2 oselielo osimbo mar wiyi.
\q1 
\v 17 Donge usekelo ma kuomu uwegi,
\q2 ka ujwangʼo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu,
\q2 kane otelonu e yo?
\q1 
\v 18 Koro angʼo momiyo udhi Misri
\q2 mondo umodh pi moa Shihor?
\q1 Kendo angʼo momiyo udhi Asuria
\q2 mondo umodh pi moa e Aora?
\q1 
\v 19 Timbeu maricho biro kelonu kum;
\q2 wech mane uweyago ema biro kelonu kum.
\q1 Nonuru kendo ubiro ngʼeyo malongʼo,
\q2 kaka en gima rach kendo lit ne un uwegi,
\q1 ka ujwangʼo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu,
\q2 kendo ubedo maonge kode gi luor kata matin,”
\q2 Ruoth Nyasaye ma en Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, owacho kamano.
\b
\q1 
\v 20 “Chon gi lala ne ituro jok magi
\q2 kendo ichodo rateke motweyigo;
\q2 kiwacho ni, ‘Ok anatini!’
\q1 Adier, ewi gode matindo duto
\q2 kendo e bwo yiende motimo otiep,
\q2 ninindo piny ka jachode.
\q1 
\v 21 Ne apidhoi kaka mzabibu mar kodhi,
\q2 moyier makare kendo manyak.
\q1 Kara ere kaka ne iweya mi idonjo e timbe moduwore,
\q2 kendo ichalo gi mzabibu mar bungu.
\q1 
\v 22 Kata bedni ilwoko lweti gi magadi
\q2 kendo itiyo gi sabun mangʼeny,
\q1 chilo mar ketho mari pod nitiere e nyima,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto owacho.
\q1 
\v 23 “Ere kaka diwachi ni,
\q2 ‘Ok adwanyora; pod ok aringo aluwo bangʼ Baal?’
\q1 Par kaka ne itimori e holo; par gima isetimo.
\q2 In ngamia ma nyako ma rikni maringo ka gi kacha,
\q1 
\v 24 punda mar thim mongʼiyo gi kama otwo,
\q2 ma ngʼweyo yamo kodwaro thuondi;
\q2 en ngʼa madigengʼe?
\q1 Onge thuon manyalo thagore
\q2 ka dware nikech yude yot ka kinde miringo kode ochopo.
\q1 
\v 25 Kik iringi nyaka tiendi dongʼ
\q2 nono kendo dwondi two.
\q1 To ne iwacho, ‘Onge tiende!
\q2 Ahero nyiseche mag pinje mamoko,
\q2 kendo nyaka aluw bangʼ-gi.’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 26 “Kaka jakuo wiye kuot ka omake,
\q2 omiyo od Israel wiye okuot,
\q1 gin gi ruodhigi kod jotendgi,
\q2 jodolo mag-gi kod jonabi mag-gi.
\q1 
\v 27 Giwachone yien ni,
\q2 ‘In wuonwa,’ kendo ne kidi ni,
\q2 ‘In ema ne inywola.’
\q1 Giselokona ngʼegi to ok wengegi,
\q2 to sa ma gin e thagruok, giwacho niya,
\q2 ‘Bi kendo ireswa!’
\q1 
\v 28 Kare ere nyisecheu mane uloso ne un uwegi?
\q2 We mondo gibi ka ginyalo resou ka un e thagruok!
\q1 Nimar un gi nyiseche mangʼeny,
\q2 mana kaka un gi dala mangʼeny, yaye Juda.”
\b
\q1 
\v 29 “Angʼo momiyo ungʼadona bura? To un duto
\q2 usengʼanyona,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 30 “Kum mane akumogo jou nobedo kayiem nono;
\q2 kendo ne ok gilokore.
\q1 Liganglani osekidho jonabi magi mana
\q2 kaka sibuor modenyo.”
\p 
\v 31 Un tiengʼ masani,
\q2 paruru wach mar Jehova Nyasaye mawacho niya:
\q1 “Bende asebedo piny motwo ne Israel kata
\q2 ka piny motimo mudho mandiwa?
\q1 Angʼo momiyo joga wacho kama:
\q2 ‘Wan thuolo mondo waba abaya; ok wanabi iri kendo?’
\q1 
\v 32 Bende miaha diwiye wil gi gik molichorego,
\q2 kata nyako midhi kendo gi lepe mag kisera?
\q2 Joga to wigi osewil koda, odiechienge ma ok kwan.
\q1 
\v 33 Mano kaka in gi lony e dwaro hera!
\q2 Kata mana mon ma timbegi richo,
\q2 nyalo somo timbegi.
\q1 
\v 34 Remb joma odhier ma unego
\q2 yudore e lepu,
\q2 kata obedo nine ok umakogi ka gituro uteu.”
\q1 To kuom magi duto,
\q2 
\v 35 iwacho ni, “ ‘Aonge ketho,
\q2 kendo iye ok owangʼ koda.’
\q1 To abiro ngʼadoni bura
\q2 nikech iwacho ni, ‘Pod ok atimo richo.’
\q1 
\v 36 Angʼo momiyo ilworori mangʼeny kiloko yoreni?
\q2 Ibiro kuod wiyi gi Misri kaka nokuod wiyi gi Asuria.
\q1 
\v 37 Bende ubiro aa kanyo gi lweteu ka uketo ewiu,
\q2 nimar Jehova Nyasaye osedagi joma ugeno kuomgi;
\q2 ok ginikonyu.”
\b
\b
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Ka dichwo oriembo chiege
\q2 kendo chiege odhi moweye mi okende gi dichwo machielo,
\q1 bende dodog ir dhakoni kendo?
\q2 Donge pinyni dibed mochido chuth?
\q1 To isedak kaka ochot man-gi johera mangʼeny
\q2 bende koro diduog ira?
\q1 
\v 2 Tingʼ wangʼi malo mondo ingʼiane
\q2 kuonde motimo ongoro motingʼore mondo ine.
\q1 Bende nitiere kamoro amora modongʼ
\q2 e piny mapok iterorigo?
\q1 E dir yo ne ibet piny ka irito johera magi,
\q2 ibet piny ka jakwath mamanyo pi ne dhoge e piny motwo.
\q1 Isedwanyo piny gi chode mari,
\q2 kod timbegi mamono.
\q1 
\v 3 Emomiyo osetuonu koth,
\q2 kendo kodh chwiri pod ok ochwe.
\q1 Kata kamano in gi neno
\q2 machalo gi mar ochot;
\q2 wiyi bende ok kuodi nikech ionge gi wichkuot.
\q1 
\v 4 Donge koro eka iwachona kama:
\q2 Wuonwa, osiepna chakre tin-na,
\q1 
\v 5 inisik ka iyi owangʼ?
\q2 Bende mirimbi biro bedo manyaka chiengʼ?
\q1 Ma e kaka iwuoyo,
\q2 to itimo timbe mamono duto minyalo.”
\s1 Israel ok ja-ratiro
\p 
\v 6 E kinde mar loch Ruoth Josia, Jehova Nyasaye nowachona niya, “Bende iseneno gima Israel ma ok ja-ratiro otimo? Osedhi ewi gode duto matindo maboyo kendo e bwo yiende duto motimo otiep mi osechodo kanyo.
\v 7 Ne aparo ni kane osetimo magi duto to ne odhi duogo ira makmana ne ok odwogo, kendo kata mana nyamin mare ma Juda ma ok ja-ratiro noneno mano.
\v 8 Ne amiyo Israel maonge gi yie baruwa mar weruok kendo mi ariembe nikech timbene duto mag chode. Kata kamano ne aneno ka nyamin-gi ma Juda maonge ratiro ne ok oluor; en bende nodhi kendo ochodo.
\v 9 Nikech anjawo mar Israel nonenore gima tin, ne gidwanyo piny ka gilamo kite kod bepe.
\v 10 To kuom magi duto, nyamin mare ma Juda ma ok ja-adiera ka en ne ok odwogo ira gi chunye duto, to mana kuom wuondruok,” Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\p 
\v 11 Jehova Nyasaye nowachona niya, “Israel maonge gi yie ler moloyo Juda ma ok ja-adiera.
\v 12 Dhi mondo iland wachni yo nyandwat ni:
\q1 “Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 ‘Duogi in Israel maonge gi yie,
\q2 ok anabed gi mirima kodi kendo,
\q1 nimar an jangʼwono,
\q2 iya ok bi wangʼ kodi nyaka chiengʼ.
\q1 
\v 13 Yie kethoni kende nikech isengʼanyone
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi,
\q1 isekayo timbegi mag ngʼwono mana ne nyiseche manono
\q2 e bwo yiende motimo otiep,
\q2 kendo pod ok iluora,’ ”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\p 
\v 14 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Dwoguru ira, un joga maonge yie, nimar an e chworu. Abiro yierou ka ngʼato achiel oa e dala to ji ariyo koa e anywola mi akelu Sayun.
\v 15 Eka anamiu jokwath ma chunygi chal koda, mabiro telonu gi rieko kod winjo.”
\v 16 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “E ndalogo, kakwanu osemedore mangʼeny e piny, ji ok nochak owuo kawacho ni, ‘Sandug Muma mar singruok mar Jehova Nyasaye.’ Ok enodonji e parogi bende ok ginipare; ok nodware, kata moro ok nolosi kendo.
\v 17 E kindeno gibiro luongo Jerusalem ni Kom Loch mar Jehova Nyasaye, kendo ogendini duto nochokre ei Jerusalem mondo omi nying Jehova Nyasaye duongʼ. Ok ginichak gitim tim wich teko, bende ok ginibed gi chuny mar timo richo.
\v 18 E ndalogo od Juda biro riwore gi od Israel, kendo giduto ginibi ka gia e piny ma yo nyandwat nyaka e piny mane amiyo kwereu kaka girkeni.
\p 
\v 19 “An awuon ne awacho niya,
\q1 “ ‘Mano kaka dabed mamor ka akawou kaka yawuota
\q2 kendo amiu piny mowinjore,
\q2 girkeni maber mogik mar piny moro amora.’
\q1 Ne aparo ni unyalo luonga ni ‘Wuonwa,’
\q2 kendo ni ok unuwe luwa.
\q1 
\v 20 To mana ka dhako ma ok ja-ratiro ne chwore,
\q2 omiyo usebedo maonge gadieri kuoma, yaye od Israel,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 21 Ywak iwinjo e kuonde motingʼore motimo ongoro,
\q1 en kuyo gi secho mar jo-Israel,
\q2 nikech gisejwangʼo yoregi,
\q2 kendo wigi osewil gi Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachgi.
\b
\q1 
\v 22 “Dwoguru, un joma onge yie;
\q2 abiro thiedhou kuom baro weyo yo.”
\b
\q1 “Ee, wabiro biro iri,
\q2 nimar in Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa.
\q1 
\v 23 Adiera lamo nyiseche mopa ewi gode matindo,
\q1 kod gode madongo en wuond;
\q2 adier kuom Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachwa,
\q2 ema warruok mar Israel yudore.
\q1 
\v 24 Chakre tinwa nyiseche manono mag wichkuot
\q2 osechamo olemb tije wuonewa,
\q1 ma gin kweth mar jamni,
\q2 kod kweth mag dhok, yawuotgi kod nyigi.
\q1 
\v 25 We wanind piny e wichkuot marwa,
\q2 kendo we timbewa maricho oumwa.
\q1 Wasetimo richo ne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa,
\q2 wan kaachiel gi wuonewa;
\q1 chakre ndalo mane wan rowere nyaka odiechiengni
\q2 pod ok waluoro Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa.”
\b
\c 4
\q1 
\v 1 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Ka ibiro duogo, yaye Israel,
\q2 to duog ira.
\q1 Ka igolo nyisechegi mopa
\q2 mamonogo e nyima ma ok ubaro,
\q1 
\v 2 kendo kikwongʼori gi adiera gi bura makare kendo gi tim malongʼo ni,
\q2 ‘Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima,’
\q1 eka abiro gwedho ogendini duto manie piny
\q2 kendo ogendini duto biro miya duongʼ.”
\p 
\v 3 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wachone jo-Juda kod Jerusalem:
\q1 “Pururu puotheu mag mbora
\q2 kendo kik ukom e kind kuthe.
\q1 
\v 4 Terreuru nyangu uwegi ni Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 teruru chunjeu nyangu,
\q2 un jo-Juda kod jo-Jerusalem,
\q1 ka ok kamano to mirimba biro muoch mi liel ka mach,
\q2 nikech tim mamono ma usetimo manowangʼu,
\q2 maonge ngʼama nyalo kweye.”
\s1 Masira moa yo nyandwat
\q1 
\v 5 “Land e Juda
\q1 kendo ior wach e Jerusalem kiwacho ni:
\q2 ‘Gouru turumbete e piny duto!’
\q1 Ywag matek kendo iwachi:
\q2 ‘Chokreuru kaachiel!
\q2 Waringuru wadhi e mier madongo mochiel motegno!’
\q1 
\v 6 Oruru wach odhi Sayun!
\q2 Ringuru udhi kar pondo ma ok odeko!
\q1 Nimar akelo masira koa yo nyandwat,
\q2 kata kethruok malich.”
\b
\q1 
\v 7 Sibuor osewuok e kare mar pondo;
\q2 jatiek ogendini osewuok oko.
\q1 Oseweyo kare mondo otiek pinyu.
\q2 Miechu nomuki madongʼ gunda,
\q2 maonge ngʼama nodagie.
\q1 
\v 8 Omiyo rwakuru lepu mag ywak,
\q2 ywaguru kendo denguru,
\q2 nimar mirimb Jehova Nyasaye mager pod ok oweyowa.
\b
\q1 
\v 9 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Chiengʼno ruoth kod jotelo chunygi biro aa,
\q1 jodolo nobed gi luoro maduongʼ,
\q2 kendo jonabi nobed gi bwok maduongʼ.”
\p 
\v 10 Eka ne awacho, “Yaye Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto, mano kaka isewuondo jogi kod Jerusalem ka iwacho ni, ‘Unubed gi kwe,’ mana sa ma ligangla ni e dwondwa.”
\p 
\v 11 E kindego jogi kod Jerusalem nonyisi niya, “Yamo maliet moa kama gimoro ok nyagie mana kama otwo futo kadhi ir joga, to ok mondo okwadhgi kata pwodhogi;
\v 12 to yamo motegno moloyo mano aa kuoma. Koro asengʼadonegi bura.”
\q1 
\v 13 Ne! Obiro ka boche polo,
\q2 gechene mag lweny biro ka kalausi,
\q1 farese mage ringo matek moloyo ongo.
\q2 Kagiwacho niya, mano kaka wan gi lit!
\q1 
\v 14 Yaye Jerusalem,
\q2 luok timbe mamono manie chunyu mondo iresri.
\q2 Nyaka karangʼo mi ibiro kano timbe richo e pachi?
\q1 
\v 15 Koko wuok koa Dan,
\q2 ka goyo milome mar masira koa e gode matindo mag Efraim.
\q1 
\v 16 “Nyis ogendini
\q2 kendo go milome ne Jerusalem niya,
\q2 ‘Jolweny mager biro iru kawuok e piny mabor,
\q1 ka gigoyo koko mar agengʼa
\q2 mar lweny kuom mier madongo mag Juda.
\q1 
\v 17 Gilwore mana ka joma rito puodho,
\q2 nikech osengʼanyona,’ ”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 18 “Kiti kod timbegi iwuon
\q2 osemiyo ma obiro kuomi.
\q2 Ma en kum mari. Mano kaka olit!
\q1 Mano kaka opowo nyaka e chuny!”
\b
\q2 
\v 19 Yaye, iya nyawni,
\q2 iya nyawni! An gi rem malit.
\q1 Yaye, lit mager mar chunya!
\q2 Chunya ridore, ok nyal lingʼ thi.
\q1 Nimar asewinjo koko mar turumbete;
\q2 asewinjo ywak mar kedo.
\q1 
\v 20 Masira bangʼ masira;
\q2 piny duto okethi.
\q1 Ka diemo wangʼ nono hembena omuki,
\q2 kara mar dak ka mil polo.
\q1 
\v 21 Nyaka karangʼo mabiro nenoe kedo machalo kama,
\q2 kendo winjo dwond turumbete?
\b
\q1 
\v 22 “Joga ofuwo; ok gingʼeya.
\q2 Gin nyithindo maonge wigi gionge rieko,
\q1 gilony mana kuom timo timbe maricho;
\q2 kendo ok gingʼeyo; kaka digitim maber.”
\b
\q1 
\v 23 Ne angʼiyo piny,
\q2 ne en nono kendo noonge gi kido;
\q1 kendo bende ne angʼiyo e polo,
\q2 to ler ne onge.
\q1 
\v 24 Ne angʼiyo gode madongo
\q2 kendo negiyiengni,
\q2 to gode matindo duto ne rundore koni gi koni.
\q1 
\v 25 Ne angʼicho to ne onge ji,
\q2 winy duto manie kor polo nosefuyo molal.
\q1 
\v 26 Ne angʼicho to piny
\q2 mane miyo nolokore kama otwo;
\q2 dalane duto nokethi e nyim mirimb Jehova Nyasaye mager.
\p 
\v 27 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q2 “Piny mangima ibiro kethi,
\q2 kata kamano ok nakethe chutho.
\q1 
\v 28 Omiyo piny biro dengo
\q2 kendo polo malo notim mudho,
\q1 nikech asewuoyo kendo ok analok pacha,
\q2 asengʼado wach chuth kendo ok anadog chien.”
\b
\q1 
\v 29 Ka dwol mar joidh farese
\q2 kod jo-asere owinji,
\q1 to dala ka dala golo aputh njiri.
\q2 Moko dhi e bunge modinore;
\q2 moko idho dhi ewi lwendni.
\q1 Mier duto ji odarie;
\q2 onge ngʼama odak eigi.
\b
\q1 
\v 30 En angʼo mitimo,
\q2 yaye ngʼama osetiekni?
\q1 Angʼo momiyo irwakori gi law marakwaro
\q2 kendo idusori gi gige dhahabu?
\q2 Angʼo momiyo ibuko wangʼi gi rangi.
\q1 Idusori kayiem nono.
\q2 Johera magi jari;
\q1 gidwaro mana ngimani.
\b
\q1 
\v 31 Awinjo ywak kaka mar dhako mamuoch kayo,
\q2 lit mana ka dhako ma nywolo nyathine makayo,
\q1 ywak mar Nyar Sayun ka gamo yweyo,
\q2 kotengʼo bedene kendo owacho,
\q1 “To mano kaka apodho;
\q2 ngimana omi jonek.”
\c 5
\s1 Onge ngʼama ja-ratiro
\q1 
\v 1 “Wuothi e yore mag Jerusalem duto,
\q2 rang koni gi koni kiparo,
\q1 kendo kimanyo kuondege duto.
\q2 Kinyalo yudo kata mana ngʼato achiel,
\q1 ma ja-ratiro kendo madwaro adiera,
\q2 to abiro ngʼwonone dala maduongʼni.
\q1 
\v 2 Kata obedo ni gisingore niya,
\q2 ‘Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima,’
\q2 pod gikwongʼore mar miriambo.”
\b
\q1 
\v 3 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, donge wengeni manyo adiera?
\q2 Ne igoyogi, to ne ok giwinjo rem;
\q2 ne ikidhogi matindo tindo, to ne ok gilokore.
\q1 Negimiyo wengegi obedo matek moloyo
\q2 kidi mi gitamore hulo richogi.
\q1 
\v 4 To ne aparo ni, “Magi gin mana joma odhier;
\q2 kendo gifuwo;
\q1 nimar ok gingʼeyo yor Jehova Nyasaye
\q2 kod dwaro mar Nyasachgi.
\q1 
\v 5 Omiyo anadhi ir jotelo
\q2 kendo awuo kodgi;
\q2 adiera gingʼeyo yor Jehova Nyasaye,
\q1 kod dwaro mar Nyasachgi.”
\q2 To gi chuny achiel gin bende negituro jok,
\q2 kendo gichodo rateke.
\q1 
\v 6 Emomiyo sibuor moa e bungu nomonjgi,
\q2 ondiek moa e thim nokidhgi,
\q1 kwach noliwgi but miechgi
\q2 mondo okidh matindo tindo,
\q2 ngʼato angʼata manohedhre wuok oko,
\q1 nimar ngʼanyo margi duongʼ
\q2 kendo gisebaro nyadi mangʼeny.
\b
\q1 
\v 7 Angʼo ma dimi awenu richou?
\q2 Nyithindu osejwangʼa,
\q1 kendo osekwongʼore gi nyiseche
\q2 ma ok nyiseche.
\q1 Asemiyogi gigo duto magidwaro,
\q2 kata kamano giterore
\q2 kendo gipongʼo ute ochode.
\q1 
\v 8 Jogo oowre gi gombo,
\q2 gichalo farese moyiengʼ,
\q1 ma gombo ohewo ka moro,
\q2 ka moro kuomgi gombo mana chi ngʼat machielo.
\q1 
\v 9 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Donge dakumgi kuom ma?”
\q2 Donge onego akel kum ne oganda machalo kama?
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Dhi e puothege mag mzabibu
\q1 kendo ichadhgi, to kik ikethgi chuth.
\q2 Lwer bedene, nimar jogi ok gin mek Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 11 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Od Israel kod od Juda ok osebedona jo-ratiro chutho.”
\b
\q1 
\v 12 Giseriambo kuom Jehova Nyasaye;
\q2 kagiwacho, “Onge gima obiro timo!
\q2 Ok wanahinyre; ok wanane ligangla kata kech.
\q1 
\v 13 Jonabi chalo mana yamo
\q2 kendo wach onge eigi;
\q1 omiyo we gima giwacho otimre ne gin giwegi.”
\p 
\v 14 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Nikech ji osewacho wechegi,
\q2 abiro keto wechega manie dhogi mach,
\q2 to jogi nobed yien maliel.”
\q1 
\v 15 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Yaye od Israel, akelo oganda moa mabor mondo oked kodu,
\q1 gin oganda machon kendo man-gi sinani,
\q2 jogo ma ok ungʼe dhogi,
\q2 bende wechegi ok unyal winjo tiendgi.
\q1 
\v 16 Gigegi mitingʼoe asere
\q2 chalo gi liel ma dhoge oyawore;
\q1 giduto gin jolweny maroteke.
\q1 
\v 17 Giniyak chambu kod chiembu,
\q2 ginitiek yawuotu gi nyiu;
\q2 kendo ginineg jambu kod dhou,
\q1 bende giniketh yiende mzabibu mau
\q2 kod yiende mag ngʼopeu.
\q1 Miechu madongo mochiel gohinga
\q2 motegno mugeno kuomgi nokethi gi ligangla.”
\p 
\v 18 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “To kata bende e ndalogo, ok anatieku chuth.
\v 19 To ka ji openjo ni, ‘Angʼo momiyo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa osetimonwa ma?’ Wachnegiuru ni, ‘Kaka usejwangʼa kendo usetiyone nyiseche mag pinje mamoko ei pinyu uwegi, omiyo koro ubiro tiyone ogendini mamoko ei piny ma ok maru.’
\q1 
\v 20 “Land ma ne od Jakobo
\q2 kendo go milomeno ne Juda:
\q1 
\v 21 Winj ma, un jogo mofuwo kendo onge wigi,
\q2 joma nigi wengegi to ok nen,
\q2 joma nigi it to ok winj wach:
\q1 
\v 22 Donge onego umiya luor?” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q2 “Donge dutetni e nyim wangʼa?
\q1 Ne aketo kuoyo obedo kiewo mar nam,
\q2 ragengʼ manyaka chiengʼ ma ok onyal kalo.
\q1 Apaka nyalo gingore, to ok ginyal kalo;
\q2 ginyalo ruto, to ok ginyal kalo dhi loka kocha.
\q1 
\v 23 To jogi wigi tek kendo chunygi bor
\q2 koda omiyo gisebaro mi giweya.
\q1 
\v 24 Ok giwach e kindgi giwegi,
\q2 ‘Mad waluor Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa,
\q1 mamiyowa kodh chwiri kod kodh opon e kinde mowinjore,
\q2 ma singonwa gadiera jumbe mag keyo.’
\q1 
\v 25 Timbeu maricho osetamou nwangʼo gigi;
\q2 richou osetamou neno maber.
\b
\q1 
\v 26 “E dier joga nitiere joma timbegi mono
\q2 ma buto ka jogo machiko winy,
\q2 kendo kaka jogo maketo obadho mar mako ji.
\q1 
\v 27 Kaka ute mopongʼ gi winy,
\q2 e kaka utegi bende opongʼ gi wuondruok;
\q1 gisebedo jo-mwandu,
\q2 kendo joma nigi teko mangʼeny,
\q1 
\v 28 kendo gisebedo machwe
\q2 kendo dendgi leny.
\q1 Timbegi mamono onge giko;
\q1 ok gikony nyithi kiye mondo olo bura,
\q2 bende ok gikony joma odhier e ratiro mag-gi,
\q1 
\v 29 donge dakumgi kuom ma?”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 “Donge dakel kum mara
\q2 kuom oganda machalo kama?
\b
\q1 
\v 30 “Gima lich kendo mabwogo ji osetimore e piny:
\q1 
\v 31 Jonabi koro miriambo,
\q2 jodolo tiyo gi tekogi giwegi,
\q1 kendo joga ohero mana gik ma kamago.
\q2 To en angʼo ma ibiro timo e ndalo mogik?
\c 6
\s1 Omonj Jerusalem
\q1 
\v 1 “Un jo-Benjamin, ringuru utony!
\q2 Ringuru ua Jerusalem!
\q1 Gouru turumbete Tekoa!
\q2 Keturu ranyisi ewi Beth Hakerem!
\q1 Nimar masira aa yo nyandwat,
\q2 kod kethruok malich.
\q1 
\v 2 Anatiek nyar Sayun,
\q2 ma ber neno kendo ma dende yom.
\q1 
\v 3 Jokwath kod jambgi noked kode;
\q2 ginigur hembegi molwore,
\q2 ka moro ka moro rito kare owuon.”
\b
\q1 
\v 4 “Ikri mar kedo kode!
\q2 Wuoguru, wadhi wamonjgi e dier odiechiengʼ!
\q1 To mano kaka ler mar odiechiengʼ bedo ma dimdim,
\q2 kendo tipo mag odhiambo yware.
\q1 
\v 5 Omiyo aa malo, wamonjgi gotieno
\q2 kendo waketh ohingane motegno!”
\p 
\v 6 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Ngʼad yiende kendo iger pidhe
\q2 mondo wamonj Jerusalem.
\q1 Dala maduongʼni nyaka kum;
\q2 nikech opongʼ gi joma hinyo jowadgi.
\q1 
\v 7 Kaka soko olo pige oko,
\q2 e kaka en bende oolo timbene mamono.
\q1 Lweny kod kethruok mor e iye;
\q2 tuone kod adhondene osiko e nyima.
\q1 
\v 8 Winj siem, yaye Jerusalem,
\q2 ka ok kamano to abiro weyi,
\q1 mi awe pinyi nono,
\q2 ma ngʼato angʼata ok nyal dak e iye.”
\p 
\v 9 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Mad gidwog jo-Israel modongʼ
\q2 kaka jochok olemb mzabibu;
\q1 ngʼauru bedeu e bede yath,
\q2 mana kaka ngʼama pono olemo.”
\b
\q1 
\v 10 En ngʼa ma anyalo wuoyogo
\q2 kendo miyo siemni?
\q2 En ngʼa manyalo winja?
\q1 Itgi odino omiyo ok ginyal winjo wach.
\q2 Wach Jehova Nyasaye chwanyogi;
\q2 ok gine gima ber kuome.
\q1 
\v 11 To apongʼ gi mirima mar Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 kendo ok anyal lingʼ kode.
\b
\q2 “Ole oko kuom nyithindo manie yore,
\q1 kendo kuom yawuowi mochokore kanyakla;
\q2 dichwo kaachiel gi dhako gini nomaki,
\q2 kod joma oti, jogo mahikgi oniangʼ.
\q1 
\v 12 Utegi ibiro miyo joma moko,
\q1 kaachiel gi puothegi kod mondegi,
\q2 ka arieyo lweta kuom jogo modak e piny,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 13 “Chakre ngʼama tin nyaka ngʼama duongʼ,
\q2 giduto girikni ka gidwaro mwandu e yor miganga;
\q1 jonabi kod jodolo chalre,
\q2 giduto gin jo-miriambo.
\q1 
\v 14 Githiedho adhonde mag joga mana
\q2 ka gima ok en gima lich.
\q2 Giwacho niya, ‘Kwe, kwe,’ kata mana ka kwe onge.
\q1 
\v 15 Bende gin-gi wichkuot kuom timbegi makwero?
\q2 Ooyo, gionge wichkuot kata mana matin;
\q2 ok gingʼeyo kata kaka ginyalo wuondore.
\q1 Omiyo gibiro podho mana kaka joma moko mopodho;
\q2 kendo ibiro dwokgi piny kakumogi,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\p 
\v 16 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Chunguru e akek yore
\q2 kendo urang wangʼ yore machon;
\q1 penjuru kuma yo maber nitie,
\q2 mondo uwuothie, kendo unuyud yweyo e chunyu.
\q2 To ne uwacho ni, ‘Ok wanaluwe.’
\q1 
\v 17 Ne aketonu jorito kendo awacho,
\q2 ‘Chikuru itu ne turumbete!’
\q2 To ne uwacho, ‘Ok wanachik itwa.’
\q1 
\v 18 Omiyo winjuru, yaye un ogendini;
\q2 ranguru malongʼo, yaye un joneno,
\q2 gima biro timore negi.
\q1 
\v 19 Winji, yaye piny:
\q2 Akelo masira ne jogi,
\q1 ma en olemo mar pachgi maricho,
\q2 nikech gitamore winjo wechena,
\q2 kendo gisedagi chikna.
\q1 
\v 20 Ere tiend ubani mangʼwe ngʼar moa kuom Sheba
\q2 kata niangʼ ma milimili moa e piny mabor?
\q1 Chiwo magu mag misengini miwangʼo pep ok ayiego;
\q2 misango magu ok mora.”
\p 
\v 21 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Anaket rachwany e nyim jogi.
\q2 Wuone kod yawuowi nochwanyre kuomgi;
\q2 jogo modak mokiewo kodgi kod osiepe nolal nono.”
\p 
\v 22 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Neuru, jolweny biro koa
\q2 e piny man yo nyandwat;
\q1 oganda maduongʼ itugo
\q2 koa e tunge piny.
\q1 
\v 23 Gimanore gi atungʼ kod tongʼ;
\q2 giger kendo gionge ngʼwono.
\q2 Gimor ka nam mogingore ka giriembo faresegi;
\q1 gibiro ka ji mochanore komanore gi gige
\q2 lweny mondo gimonju, yaye Nyar Sayun.”
\b
\q1 
\v 24 Wasewinjo humbgi,
\q2 kendo bedewa onge gi teko.
\q1 Rem malich osemakowa,
\q2 ka rem mar dhako mamuoch kayo.
\q1 
\v 25 Kik udhi e puothe kata uwuothie yore,
\q2 nimar jasigu nigi ligangla,
\q1 kendo nitie luoro kamoro amora.
\q1 
\v 26 Yaye joga, rwakuru lepu mag ywak
\q2 kendo ngʼielreuru e buru;
\q2 gouru nduru ka udengo malit mana ka ngʼama ywago wuode achiel kende,
\q1 nimar apoya nono jaketh gik
\q2 moko biro podho kuomwa.
\b
\q1 
\v 27 “Aseketi rapim mipimogo chumbe
\q2 to joga kama ikunye chumbe,
\q2 mondo mi ingʼi kendo ipim yoregi.
\q1 
\v 28 Giduto gin jongʼanyo ma tokgi tek ta,
\q2 ka gidhi ka gi kacha mar kuotho.
\q2 Gin nyinyo kod chuma; giduto gin jomecho.
\q1 
\v 29 Kata obedo ni jotheth
\q2 moko mach matek mondo oleny fedha,
\q1 kendo opwodhi, to mano en mana kayiem nono;
\q1 kamano bende joma
\q2 richo ok nyal pwodhore.
\q1 
\v 30 Iluongogi ni fedha mojwangʼ,
\q2 nikech Jehova Nyasaye osejwangʼogi.”
\c 7
\s1 Dinde manono onge tiendgi
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mane obirone Jeremia koa kuom Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 “Chungi e dhorangach mar od Jehova Nyasaye kendo kanyo land wachni:
\p “ ‘Winjuru wach Jehova Nyasaye, un jo-Juda duto madonjo gie dhorangeyegi mondo olam Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 3 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, Nyasach jo-Israel, wacho: Lok yoreu kod timbeu, to anami udagi kaye.
\v 4 Kik ugen kuom weche mag miriambo ka uwacho niya, “Ma en hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye!”
\v 5 Ka uloko yoreu gi timbeu adier kendo ungʼadone ngʼato ka ngʼato bura makare,
\v 6 kendo ka ok umayo jadak, kiye kata mon ma chwogi otho kendo ok uchwero remb joma onge ketho, kendo ka ok uluwo bangʼ nyiseche manono ma dihinyu un uwegi,
\v 7 to anami udag kae, e piny mane amiyo kwereu mondo odagie manyaka chiengʼ.
\v 8 To neuru, ugeno kuom weche mag miriambo maonge tich.
\p 
\v 9 “ ‘Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, Bende unukwal kendo uneki, uterru kendo ukwongʼru gi miriambo, uwangʼ ubani ni Baal kendo ulu bangʼ nyiseche manono ma pod ok ungʼeyo,
\v 10 to bangʼe ubiro kendo uchungʼ e nyima e odni, ma Nyinga nitie, kendo uwacho ni, “Wasetony” utony mondo utim gik mamonogi?
\v 11 Dibedi ni odni, ma iluongogo Nyinga, osebedonu kar pondo mar jomecho? To neuru arange! An Jehova Nyasaye ema asewacho kamano.
\p 
\v 12 “ ‘Koro dhi sani kama iluongo ni Shilo kama ne akwongo alosoe kar dak mar Nyinga, kendo mondo ine gima ne atimone nikech timbe mamono mag joga Israel.
\v 13 E sa ma ne utimo gigi duto, Jehova Nyasaye wacho, ne awuoyo kodu anwoya, to ne ok uchiko itu; ne aluongou, to ne ok udwoka.
\v 14 Emomiyo, gima ne atimone Shilo koro abiro timo ne ot miluongogo Nyinga, hekalu ma ugeno kuomeno, kama ne amiyou kod wuoneu.
\v 15 Anadaru e nyima, mana kaka ne atimone oweteu duto, ma jo-Efraim.’
\p 
\v 16 “Omiyo kik ilamne jogi kata chiwo kwayo moro amora kata kwayonegi lamo; kik isaya, nimar ok anawinji.
\v 17 Bende ineno gima gitimo e mier mag Juda kod yore mag Jerusalem?
\v 18 Nyithindo choko yien, wuone moko mach, to mon dwalo mogo mondo gilos godo makati ne Ruoth ma Dhako mar Polo. Gichiwo misango miolo piny ne nyiseche manono mondo ochwanya ma mi iya wangʼ.
\v 19 To uparo ni An ema gichwanyo? Jehova Nyasaye penjo. Donge gihinyore kendgi, kendo gikelo wichkuot ne gin giwegi?
\p 
\v 20 “ ‘Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto wacho: Ich wangʼ mara kod mirimba nool kaeni, kuom dhano kod le, kuom yiende manie puothe kod kuom olembe mag lowo, kendo nowangʼ ma ok nyal neg majno.
\p 
\v 21 “ ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel wacho: Dhiuru nyime, meduru chiwo magu mag misengini miwangʼo pep e misengini magu mamoko kendo ucham ringʼogo un uwegi!
\v 22 Nimar kane agolo kwereu Misri kendo awuoyo kodgi, ne ok amiyogi mana chike kuom misango miwangʼo pep kod misengini mamoko,
\v 23 to ne achiwo chikni: Luorauru, to anabed Nyasachu kendo unubed joga. Wuothuru e yore duto machikou, mondo duto odhi kodu maber.
\v 24 To ne ok gichiko itgi kata winja; makmana, negiluwo timbegi mag tok teko mag chunjegi maricho. Negidok chien ma ok gidhi nyime.
\v 25 Kochakore e kinde mane kwereu oa Misri nyaka sani, odiechiengʼ ka odiechiengʼ, ne asiko aoronegi jotich ma jonabi.
\v 26 To ne ok gichiko itgi kata winja. Tokgi ne tek ta kendo negitimo gik maricho moloyo mag kweregi.’
\p 
\v 27 “Ka inyisogi magi duto, ok giniwinji; ka iluongogi, ok gini miyi dwoko.
\v 28 Emomiyo wachnegi ni, ‘Ma en oganda mapok omiyo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasache luor kata ok giwinj puonj. Adiera oselalnigi; kendo osea e dhogi.
\p 
\v 29 “ ‘Lieluru yie wiyeu oko kendo uwitgi; ywaguru e kuonde motingʼore malo motwo, nimar Jehova Nyasaye osekwedo kendo osejwangʼo tiengʼni mantiere e bwo mirimbe.
\s1 Holo mar nek
\p 
\v 30 “ ‘Jehova Nyasaye wacho ni jo-Juda osetimo timbe maricho e nyima. Giseketo nyisechegi manono e ot ma Nyinga nitiere kendo gisenjawe.
\v 31 Gisegero kuonde motingʼore malo mar Tofeth e Holo mar Ben Hinom mondo gi wangʼ yawuotgi kod nyigi e mach ma en gima ne ok achiko, kata ne ok odonjo e pacha.
\v 32 Omiyo bed motangʼ, ndalo biro, Jehova Nyasaye owacho, ma ji ok nochak oluonge ni Tofeth kata Holo mar Ben Hinom, to ni Holo mar Yengʼo, nimar giniyik joma otho ei Tofeth maonge thuolo modongʼ.
\v 33 Eka ringre jogi nobed chiemo mar winy mafuyo e kor polo kod le mag bungu manie piny, kendo onge ngʼama nobwog-gi mondo gia.
\v 34 Anatieki koko mar ilo gi mor kendo gi dwond miaha kod wuon kisera e dala Juda kod yore mag Jerusalem, nimar piny nodongʼ gunda.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 “ ‘Jehova Nyasaye wacho ni e kindego, choke mag ruodhi kod jotelo mag Juda, choke mag jodolo kod jonabi, kendo choke mag jo-Jerusalem nogol oko e liete mag-gi.
\v 2 Chokego noyar oko e nyim chiengʼ gi dwe kod sulwe duto manie polo mane gihero kendo tiyonegi ma bende negiluwo bangʼ-gi ka gipenjo rieko kendo lamogi. Ok nochokgi kata ikgi, to ginichal ka owuoyo manie lowo.
\v 3 Kamoro amora ma ariembogi ka aterogie, to jogo duto motony mar oganda marachni noher tho kar ngima, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego owacho kamano.’
\s1 Richo gi kum
\p 
\v 4 “Wachnegi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Ka ji opodho mogore piny donge gia malo?
\q2 Ka ngʼato oa, donge odwogo?
\q1 
\v 5 Marangʼo jogi ongʼanyo oa?
\q2 Angʼo momiyo Jerusalem siko ringo?
\q2 Gimoko kuom miriambo; gitamore duogo.
\q1 
\v 6 Asechiko ita malongʼo,
\q2 to ok giwach gima adier.
\q1 Onge ngʼama lokore weyo kuom timbegi mamono,
\q2 kopenjo niya, “En angʼo ma asetimo?”
\q2 Moro ka moro luwo yore owuon ka faras madhi e lweny.
\q1 
\v 7 Kata mana nyamnaha manie
\q2 kor polo ongʼeyo kindene moketne,
\q1 kendo akuch odugla, opija gi ongo-wangʼ
\q2 bende ongʼeyo ndalo mar dargi.
\q2 To joga ok ongʼeyo dwach Jehova Nyasaye.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 “ ‘Ere kaka inyalo wacho niya, “Wariek,
\q2 nimar wan gi chik mar Jehova Nyasaye,”
\q1 ka gadiera kalamb miriambo
\q2 mar jondiko osetiyo kode e yor miriambo?
\q1 
\v 9 Jomariek nokuod wigi;
\q2 ginibed gi luoro mangʼeny kendo enomakgi.
\q1 Nimar gisedagi wach Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 en rieko manade ma gin godo?
\q1 
\v 10 Emomiyo anachiw mondegi
\q2 ne joma moko kendo puothegi ne jomanyien.
\q1 Kochakore kuom ngʼat matin nyaka ngʼat maduongʼ,
\q2 giduto giwuor ne yudo ohala;
\q1 jonabi gi jodolo machalre,
\q2 giduto gitimo timbe wuondruok.
\q1 
\v 11 Githiedho adhonde mag
\q2 joga mana ka gima ok en gima lich.
\q1 Giwacho niya, “Kwe, kwe,”
\q2 kata kwe onge.
\q1 
\v 12 Donge wigi kuot gi timbegi mamono?
\q2 Ooyo, gionge wichkuot kata matin;
\q2 bende gionge leny kata wichkuot.
\q1 Omiyo ginipodhi e dier joma opodho;
\q2 enolwargi piny ka ikumogi,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 13 “ ‘Anakaw nyak mag-gi.
\q2 Onge olemo manobedi e mzabibu.
\q1 Onge olemb ngʼowu manobedi ewi yath,
\q2 kendo itgi noner.
\q1 Gima asemiyogi nomagi.’ ”
\q2 An Jehova Nyasaye ema asewacho kamano.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Angʼo momiyo wabet ka?
\q2 Chokreuru kaachiel!
\q1 Waringuru wadhi e mier madongo mochiel motegno gohinga
\q2 kendo watho kuno!
\q1 Nimar Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 ma Nyasachwa osejwangʼowa mondo watho,
\q1 kendo osemiyowa pi moketie sum mondo wamodhi,
\q2 nikech wasetimo richo e nyime.
\q1 
\v 15 Ne wageno kwe
\q2 to onge ber mosebiro,
\q1 bende ne wageno kinde mag chang,
\q2 to ne nitie mana thagruok.
\q1 
\v 16 Giro mar farese mag wasigu
\q2 iwinjo koa Dan;
\q2 kendo ywak farese mathuondi miyo piny tetni.
\q1 Gibiro tieko piny duto kod gik moko manie iye,
\q2 dala maduongʼ kod ji duto modak kanyo.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 “Ne, anaor thuol man-gi kwiri e dieru,
\q2 thuonde mager ma ok bo, kendo gini kau.”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 18 Yaye Jahochna e lit,
\q2 chunya ool.
\q1 
\v 19 Winj ywak joga koa e piny man mabor:
\q2 “Donge Jehova Nyasaye ni Sayun?
\q2 Ruodhe bende pod ni kuno adier?”
\b
\q1 “Angʼo momiyo gisemiya ich wangʼ gigigo ma giloso,
\q2 kod nyisechegi mag pinje mamoko?”
\b
\q1 
\v 20 “Ndalo keyo kod ndalo oro osekalo,
\q2 to ok wakonyore.”
\b
\q1 
\v 21 Nimar joga osehiny, an bende ahinyora;
\q2 aywak kendo luoro omaka.
\q1 
\v 22 Yath tinde orumo Gilead koso?
\q2 Jathieth tinde onge kanyo koso?
\q1 Kare ere gima omiyo adhond joga ok nyal chango?
\c 9
\q1 
\v 1 Yaye, mad wiya bed ka soko mar pi
\q2 kendo pi wangʼa mol ka aora!
\q1 Dwaywak odiechiengʼ
\q2 kod otieno nikech nek mar joga.
\q1 
\v 2 Yaye, mad ne abed gi
\q2 kar nindo michulo ne jowuoth e piny ongoro,
\q1 mondo omi awe joga
\q2 kendo adhi mabor kodgi;
\q1 nimar giduto gin jochode,
\q2 kanyakla mar joma onge adiera.
\b
\q1 
\v 3 “Giketo lewgi moikore ka atungʼ,
\q2 mondo gidirgo miriambo;
\q1 to dhigi maber e piny
\q2 ok nikech giwacho adiera.
\q1 Gitimo richo bangʼ moro ka moro;
\q2 ok gidewa.”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 4 “Beduru motangʼ gosiepeu;
\q2 kik uket genou kuom oweteu.
\q1 Nimar oweteu duto jo-miriambo,
\q2 kendo osiep moro amora jakwoth.
\q1 
\v 5 Osiep wuondo osiep,
\q1 kendo onge ngʼama wacho adiera.
\q2 Gisepuonjo lewgi wacho miriambo;
\q1 kendo gisedonjo matut e richo
\q2 ma ok ginyal wuokie.
\q1 
\v 6 Idak e kind jo-miriambo;
\q2 e wuondruokgino gisedagi yie kuoma.”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\p 
\v 7 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Ne, abiro pwodhogi kendo temogi,
\q2 nimar en angʼo machielo manyalo timo,
\q2 nikech richo mar joga?
\q1 
\v 8 Lewgi en asere man-gi kwiri;
\q2 owacho miriambo.
\q1 Gi dhoge owuoyo mamuol ne jabathe,
\q2 to e chunye oketone obadho.”
\q1 
\v 9 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Donge dakumgi ne ma?
\q1 Donge dachul kuor
\q2 ne oganda ma kama?”
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Abiro ywak kendo dengo ne gode
\q2 bende anaywag lege motwo, mosedongʼ nono,
\q2 kendo onge gima wuothoe,
\q1 bende ywak mar jamni ok winjie.
\q2 Winy mafuyo e kor polo oseringo,
\q2 kendo le osedhi.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 “Anami Jerusalem obed gunda,
\q2 kama ondiegi ema odakie;
\q1 kendo anaketh mier mag Juda
\q2 mondo ngʼato kik dag kanyo.”
\p 
\v 12 En ngʼa mariek manyalo winjo tiend ma? En ngʼa mosetiegi gi Jehova Nyasaye kendo nyalo lero tiende? Angʼo momiyo piny osekethi modongʼ nono ka kama otwo maonge ngʼama nyalo luwo?
\p 
\v 13 Jehova Nyasaye nowacho niya, “Nikech gisejwangʼo chikna, mane amiyogi; omiyo ok giseluora kata luwo chikna.
\v 14 To giseluwo mana timbegi mag wich teko; bende giseluwo bangʼ Baal, mana kaka wuonegi nopuonjogi.”
\v 15 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: “Ne, anami jogi cham chiemo makech kendo modh pi sum.
\v 16 Anakegi e dier ogendini ma gin kata wuonegi ok ongʼeyo, kendo analawgi gi ligangla manyaka atiekgi.”
\p 
\v 17 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Parane! Luonguru mon madengo mondo obi;
\q2 to moloyo mago man-gi lony mamalo e ywak.
\q1 
\v 18 Giret piyo
\q2 mondo gidengnwa,
\q1 nyaka wengewa pongʼ gi pi wangʼ
\q2 ma oo kendo pi wangʼwa mol ma luokwa.
\q1 
\v 19 Koko mar dengo iwinjo koa Sayun:
\q2 ‘Mano kaka otiekowa!
\q1 Mano kaka wichkuot marwa duongʼ!
\q2 Nyaka waa e pinywa nikech utewa osemuki.’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 20 Koro, yaye mon,
\q2 winjuru wach Jehova Nyasaye;
\q1 yawuru itu ne weche mawuok e dhoge.
\q2 Puonjuru nyiu dengo;
\q2 puonjreuru ywak uwegi.
\q1 
\v 21 Tho oseidho gie dirisni magwa
\q2 kendo osedonjo kuondewa mochiel motegno gohinga;
\q1 osengʼado nyithindo oko e yore
\q2 kendo rowere e kuonde budho mag galamoro.
\p 
\v 22 Wach niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye owacho:
\q1 “ ‘Ringre joma otho nopie ka owuoyo e pap alanga,
\q2 kaka cham mokaa gi jakeyo,
\q2 maonge ngʼama nyalo chokogi.’ ”
\p 
\v 23 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Kik ngʼama riek sungre gi riekone
\q2 kata ngʼama tek sungre gi tekone,
\q2 kata ngʼama omewo sungre gi mwandu mage,
\q1 
\v 24 to ngʼat ma sungore mondo osungre kama:
\q2 ni ongʼeya, kendo owinja,
\q1 ni An e Jehova Nyasaye, matimo ngʼwono,
\q2 kendo mangʼado bura mar adier,
\q2 kendo matimo gik makare e piny,
\q1 nikech magi ema amorgo,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\p 
\v 25 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Ndalo biro ma anakumie joma oter nyangu e ringruok kende
\v 26 kaka Misri, Juda, Edom, Amon, Moab gi jogo duto modak kuonde motimo ongoro man maboyo. Nimar ogendinigi duto ok oter nyangu adier, kendo kata od Israel duto bende ok oter nyangu e chunygi.”
\c 10
\s1 Nyasaye kod nyiseche manono
\p 
\v 1 Winji gima Jehova Nyasaye wachoni, yaye od Israel.
\v 2 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Kik ipuonjri yore ogendini
\q2 kata ibed gi bwok gi ranyisi manie kor polo,
\q2 kata obedo ni gibwogo ogendini.
\q1 
\v 3 Nimar kit jogi kod timbegi onge tiende;
\q2 gingʼado yien koa e bungu,
\q2 bangʼe japecho paye gi koyo mare.
\q1 
\v 4 Giwire gi fedha gi dhahabu;
\q2 giriwe motegno gi musmal ka gigoye gi nyundo,
\q2 mondo kik oyiengni.
\q1 
\v 5 Mana kaka gima ibwogogo gik moko e puothe mag budho,
\q2 e kaka nyisechegi manonogo ok nyal wuoyo;
\q2 nyaka tingʼ-gi nikech ok ginyal wuotho.
\q1 Kik uluorgi;
\q2 ok ginyal hinyou
\q2 kata timonu gima ber.”
\b
\q1 
\v 6 Onge ngʼama chalo kodi, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
\q2 iduongʼ, kendo nyingi maratego nigi teko.
\q1 
\v 7 En ngʼa ma ok onego miyi luor,
\q2 yaye Ruodh ogendini?
\q2 Ma gima iwinjori godo.
\q1 Kuom jorieko duto mag ogendini kod
\q2 kuom pinjeruodhigi duto,
\q2 onge ngʼama chalo kodi.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Giduto gionge paro kendo gifuwo;
\q2 ipuonjogi gi nyiseche manono mag bepe mopa maonge tich.
\q1 
\v 9 Fedha mothedhi ikelo koa Tarshish
\q2 kendo dhahabu koa Ufaz.
\q1 Gima japecho kod jatheth oseloso
\q2 irwako gi lewni marambulu gi maralik,
\q2 giduto olosgi gi jotich molony.
\q1 
\v 10 To Jehova Nyasaye e Nyasaye madieri;
\q2 en e Nyasaye mangima, Ruoth manyaka chiengʼ.
\q1 Ka iye owangʼ, to piny tetni;
\q2 ogendini ok nyal mirimbe.
\p 
\v 11 “Nyisgi ma: ‘Nyiseche manonogi, mane ok ochweyo polo gi piny, nolal nono e piny kendo e bwo polo.’ ”
\q1 
\v 12 To Nyasaye nochweyo piny gi tekone;
\q2 ne ochako piny gi riekone,
\q2 kendo oyaro polo gi ngʼeyo mare.
\q1 
\v 13 Ka omor ka polo, to pige manie polo wuo;
\q2 omiyo boche polo dhwolore koa e giko piny.
\q1 Ooro mil polo gi koth
\q2 kendo okelo yamo koa e kuondege mag keno.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Ji duto parogi ok ti
\q2 kendo gionge ngʼeyo;
\q1 jotheth duto wigi
\q2 kuot gi nyisechegi manono ma githedho.
\q1 Kido mage moloso gin gik manono;
\q2 gionge muya eigi.
\q1 
\v 15 Gionge tich, gin gik minyiero;
\q2 ka ndalogi mar ngʼado bura ochopo,
\q2 to ginilal nono.
\q1 
\v 16 Jalno ma en Pok mar Jakobo ok chal kodgi,
\q1 nimar en e Jachwech mar gik moko duto,
\q2 nyaka Israel, ma en dhood girkeni mare,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego e nyinge.
\s1 Masira mabiro gi sand mabiro
\q1 
\v 17 Chokuru giu duto mondo ua e pinyno,
\q2 un joma ogengʼnigi.
\q1 
\v 18 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q2 “E kindeni machalo kama,
\q1 abiro daro ji modak e pinyni;
\q2 anakel sandruok kuomgi mondo mi omakgi.”
\b
\q1 
\v 19 To mano kaka litna nikech hinyruok mara!
\q2 Adhonda ok thiedhre!
\q1 Kata kamano awacho ne an owuon ni,
\q2 “Ma en twona, kendo nyaka angʼi kode.”
\q1 
\v 20 Hemba okethi; tonde mitweyego duto ochodi.
\q2 Yawuota oweya kendo ok gin koda;
\q1 onge ngʼama odongʼ manyalo
\q2 gurona hemba kata gerona kambi.
\q1 
\v 21 Jokwath onge rieko to
\q2 bende ok gipenj Jehova Nyasaye wach;
\q1 mano emomiyo ok gidhi nyime maber
\q2 kendo rombe mag-gi duto oke.
\q1 
\v 22 Chik iti! Wach biro niya,
\q2 tungni maduongʼ koa e piny man yo nyandwat!
\q1 Anami dala mag Juda odongʼ nono,
\q2 kama ondiegi ema odakie.
\s1 Lemo mar Jeremia
\q1 
\v 23 Angʼeyo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 ni ngima dhano ok en mare owuon;
\q2 ok en mar dhano mondo ochik yorene.
\q1 
\v 24 Rieya, Jehova Nyasaye, to mana gi bura
\q2 makare ma ok e ich wangʼ,
\q2 ka ok kamano to ditieka chuth.
\q1 
\v 25 Ol mirimbi kuom
\q2 ogendini ma ok ongʼeyi,
\q2 kuom ji ma ok luong nyingi.
\q1 Nimar gisetieko Jakobo;
\q2 gisetieke chuth kendo giseketho dalane.
\c 11
\s1 Oketh singruok
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mane obirone Jeremia koa ir Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 “Chik iti ne chike mag singruokni kendo inyis jo-Juda kod mago modak Jerusalem.
\v 3 Nyisgi ni ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Okwongʼ ngʼatno ma ok oluoro gima singruokni dwaro,
\v 4 chike mane amiyo kwereu kane agologi Misri, e kendo maliet makakni mach.’ Ne awacho ni, ‘Luora kendo itim gigo duto machikou to unubed joga, an bende nabed Nyasachu.
\v 5 Bangʼe anachop singo mane asingone kwereu, mar miyogi piny mopongʼ gi chak kod mor kich’ ma en piny mauntiere kawuono.”
\p Ne adwoko Jehova Nyasaye niya, “Amin.”
\p 
\v 6 Jehova Nyasaye nowachona niya, “Go milome mar wechegi duto e mier mag Juda kod jogo manie yore mag Jerusalem: ‘Chikuru itu ne chike mag singruokni kendo ulugi.
\v 7 Kochakore kinde mane akelo kwereu koa Misri nyaka kawuono, ne asiemogi nyadingʼeny, ka awacho niya, “Luorauru.”
\v 8 To ne ok gichiko itgi kata winja; kuom mano, negiluwo mana timbegi mag jendeke mag chunjegi maricho. Omiyo nakelo kuomgi kwongʼ duto mag singruok mane achikogi mondo gilu to ne ok girito.’ ”
\p 
\v 9 Eka Jehova Nyasaye nowachona, “Nitiere winjruok ma lingʼ-lingʼ e kind jo-Juda kod jogo modak Jerusalem.
\v 10 Gisedok e richo mag kweregi, mane otamore winjo wechega. Giseluwo bangʼ nyiseche manono mondo gitinegi. Od Israel gi od Juda giduto oseketho singruok mane atimo gi kweregi.
\v 11 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Anakelnegi masira ma ok ginyal tonye. Kata bed ni giywakna, ok anawinjgi.
\v 12 Mier mag Juda kod jo-Jerusalem nodhi kendo ywakne nyiseche manono ma giwangʼone ubani, to ok ginikonygi ngangʼ ka masira ochopo.
\v 13 Un gi nyiseche manono mangʼeny mana kaka dalau, yaye Juda; bende kendo mar misango museiko mudwaro wangʼone nyasaye manono mar wichkuot miluongo ni Baal ngʼeny mana ka yore mag Jerusalem.’
\p 
\v 14 “Kik ilam ne jogi kata chiwonegi kwayo moro amora kata sayonegi, nikech ok anawinji ka gibiro ira e seche mag masira.
\q1 
\v 15 “Angʼo ma jaherana timo e hekalu mara
\q2 kochano timbe mamono gi ji mathoth?
\q2 Bende ringʼo mowal tenge nyalo loko kum mari?
\q1 Seche mitimo timbe marichogo,
\q2 ema inie gi mor.”
\b
\q1 
\v 16 Jehova Nyasaye noluongi ni yadh zeituni
\q2 madongo maber man-gi olemo moolo maber.
\q1 To mor matek mar yamb
\q2 auka enowangʼe ka mach,
\q2 kendo bedene notur.
\m 
\v 17 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego mane opidhou kaka yath osegolo chik mondo unwangʼ masira, nikech od Israel kod od Juda osetimo maricho kendo gisechwanya ma iya owangʼ kuom wangʼo ubani ne Baal.
\s1 Chano timo marach ne Jeremia
\p 
\v 18 Nikech Jehova Nyasaye nohulona marach mane gichano timo, ne angʼeyo wachno, nimar e kindeno nosefwenyona gima negitimo.
\v 19 Asebedo kaka nyarombo mamuol mitero kar yengʼo; ne ok afwenyo nine gisechano timona marach, kagiwacho niya,
\q1 “Watiek yath kaachiel gi olembene;
\q2 wagole oko oaye piny joma ngima,
\q2 mondo nyinge kik par kendo.”
\q1 
\v 20 To, yaye Jehova Nyasaye Maratego,
\q2 in ma ingʼado bura gi ratiro kendo pimo chuny kod paro,
\q1 yie ane mirimbi kuom jogi,
\q2 nimar in ema aseketoni kwayona.
\p 
\v 21 “Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom jo-Anathoth madwaro ngimani, ‘Kik ikor e nying Jehova Nyasaye ka ok kamano to ibiro tho e lwetwa.’
\v 22 Kuom mano Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho ni, ‘Anakumgi. Rowere mag-gi noneg gi ligangla, yawuotgi kod nyigi kech nonegi.
\v 23 Onge ngʼato kuomgi manodongʼ, nikech anakel masira ne jo-Anathoth e higa manokumgie.’ ”
\c 12
\s1 Ywagruok Jeremia
\q1 
\v 1 In kare kinde duto, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 sa moro amora makelo bucha e nyimi.
\q1 To kata kamano we mondo awuoye kodi
\q2 kuom ngʼado bura mari makare:
\q1 Ere gima omiyo yore mag joma
\q2 timbegi mono dhi maber?
\q2 Angʼo momiyo jogo maonge yie odak maber?
\q1 
\v 2 Isepidhogi, kendo tiendegi osenyaa;
\q2 gidongo kendo ginywolo olemo.
\q1 Wechegi osiko e dhogi kinde
\q2 duto to chunygi bor kodi.
\q1 
\v 3 Kata kamano ingʼeya, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
\q2 inena kendo ipimo pacha kaka aparo kuomi.
\q1 Ywagi tenge kaka rombo mitero kar yengʼo!
\q2 Ketgi tenge ne odiechieng yengʼo!
\q1 
\v 4 Nyaka karangʼo ma piny biro
\q2 siko kotwo kendo lum motwi e lege ner?
\q1 Nikech joma odak e iye timbegi mono,
\q2 le kod winy osetho.
\q1 Kata kamano,
\q2 jogo wacho, “Ok none gima timorenwa.”
\s1 Dwoko mar Nyasaye
\q1 
\v 5 Ka isepiem gi jogo
\q2 mawuotho gi tielo ma gioli,
\q1 to ere kaka inyalo piem gi farese?
\q2 Ka ichwanyori e piny man-gi kwe,
\q2 ere kaka inyalo wuotho e bungu man Jordan?
\q1 
\v 6 Oweteni ma jo-dalau bende osendhogi;
\q2 kendo gisegolo ywak maduongʼ ka gikwedi.
\q1 Kik igen kuomgi,
\q2 kata obedo ni giwuoyo maber kuomi.
\b
\q1 
\v 7 “Anajwangʼ oda, anabol girkeni maga;
\q2 anachiw ngʼatno mahero e lwet wasike.
\q1 
\v 8 Girkeni osebedona ka sibuor manie bungu.
\q2 Orutona; omiyo amon kode.
\q1 
\v 9 Donge girkeni maga osebedona
\q2 ka kweth mag achudhe,
\q1 ma achudhe mamoko lworo mondo okedgo?
\q2 Dhi kendo ichok le mag bungu duto;
\q2 kelgi mondo gikidh joga.
\q1 
\v 10 Jokwath mangʼeny biro ketho puotha mar mzabibu
\q1 kendo ginyon puotha;
\q1 gibiro loko puotha mamiyo
\q2 bedo puodho motwo mojwangʼ.
\q1 
\v 11 Enobed puodho mojwangʼ,
\q2 motwo, kendo machalo gunda e nyima;
\q2 pinyno duto noyugno nikech onge ngʼama dewe.
\q1 
\v 12 Kuonde duto mag ongoro
\q2 motingʼore gi malo mantiere kama otwo,
\q1 joketho nopongʼ,
\q2 nimar ligangla Jehova Nyasaye notiekgi,
\q1 koa e tungʼ piny konchiel nyaka komachielo;
\q2 maonge ngʼama notony.
\q1 
\v 13 Ginipidh ngano makmana ginikaa kuthe;
\q2 gini nyagre gi tich to onge ohala ma giniyudi.
\q1 Omiyo yuduru wichkuot mar
\q2 keyo maru nikech mirimb Jehova Nyasaye mager.”
\p 
\v 14 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: “To ne jobatha duto ma timbegi mono mamayo joga Israel girkeni mane amiyogi, anapudhgi e pinjegi kendo anagol od Juda e diergi.
\v 15 To bangʼ ka asegologi, anakechgi kendo, bende anaduog moro ka moro ir girkeni mare owuon kod pinye owuon.
\v 16 Kendo ka gipuonjore maber yore mag joga kendo gikwongʼore gi nyinga, kagiwacho ni, ‘Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima,’ mana kaka negipuonjo joga mondo okwongʼre ne Baal, eka gibiro dak e dier joga.
\v 17 To ka oganda moro amora ok dwar chiko ite, to anapudhe chuth mi atieke,” Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\c 13
\s1 Okanda mar law
\p 
\v 1 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye nowachona: “Dhi kendo ingʼiew kamba mar law kendo itweye e nungoni, to kik iweye omak pi.”
\v 2 Omiyo nangʼiewo kamba, kaka Jehova Nyasaye nochika, mi atweye e nungona.
\p 
\v 3 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona kendo mar ariyo:
\v 4 “Kaw kamba mane ingʼiewo kendo itweyo e nungoni, kendo idhi Perath mi ipande kanyo e bur manie kind lwanda.”
\v 5 Omiyo ne adhi mi apande Perath, mana kaka Jehova Nyasaye nonyisa.
\p 
\v 6 Bangʼ ndalo mangʼeny Jehova Nyasaye nowachona niya, “Dhi sani Perath kendo ikaw kamba mane anyisi ni ipand kanyo.”
\v 7 Omiyo ne adhi Perath mi akunyo kambano kendo akawe kama ne apande, makmana nosekethore kendo obedo maonge tich chuth.
\p 
\v 8 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona:
\v 9 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Anatiek sunga mar Juda kod sunga malich mar Jerusalem mana e yo machalre kamano.
\v 10 Joma timbegi mono gi, motamore winjo wechega, matimo gima chunygi ema ohero, ma bende luwo bangʼ nyiseche manono mondo gitine kendo gilamgi, biro chalo gi kambani makoro onge tich chuth!’
\v 11 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya, ‘Nimar kaka okanda itweyo e nungo dhano, omiyo ne atweyo od Israel duto kod od Juda duto kuoma, mondo gibed joga miluongo gi nyinga, ma kelona pak kod duongʼ. To kata kamano negitamore winja.’
\s1 Ndede mag divai
\p 
\v 12 “Wachnegi ni: ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Ndede duto mag divai onego opongʼ gi divai.’ To kagiwacho ni, ‘Donge wangʼeyo ni ndede mag divai onego pongʼ gi divai?’
\v 13 To nyisgi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Anami ji duto modak e pinyni njawre gi mer, kaachiel gi ruodhi mobet e kom duongʼ mar Daudi, jodolo, jonabi kod jogo duto modak Jerusalem.
\v 14 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya, Anami ji duto tuomre ngʼato gi ngʼato, wuone kod yawuotgi machalre. Kechna gi herana kod ngʼwonona ok nomona tiekogi.’ ”
\s1 Kihondko mar twech
\q1 
\v 15 Winji kendo ichik iti,
\q2 kik ibed jangʼayi, nimar Jehova Nyasaye osewuoyo.
\q1 
\v 16 Mi Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachi duongʼ
\q2 ka pod ok okelo mudho,
\q1 kapok tiendeni ochwanyore,
\q2 e gode matindo motimo mudho.
\q1 Ugombo ler, to enoloke mudho
\q2 mandiwa mi oloke kuyo malich.
\q1 
\v 17 To ka ok uchiko itu,
\q2 anaywagi apanda nikech sunga magu;
\q1 wengena noywagi malit,
\q2 ka gipongʼ gi pi wangʼ,
\q2 nikech rombe mag Jehova Nyasaye noter e twech.
\b
\q1 
\v 18 Wachne ruoth kod min ruoth niya,
\q2 “Loruru uaye kombeu mag duongʼ,
\q1 nimar osimbo mau mag duongʼ
\q2 nolwar koa e wiyeu.”
\q1 
\v 19 Mier madongo man Negev nolor,
\q2 kendo onge ngʼama noyawgi.
\q1 Juda duto noter e twech,
\q2 notergi mabor chuth.
\b
\q1 
\v 20 Tingʼuru wangʼu malo
\q2 kendo une joma aa yo nyandwat.
\q1 Ere kweth mane oket e lwetu,
\q2 rombe mane usungorugo?
\q1 
\v 21 Unuwach angʼo ka Jehova Nyasaye oketo ewiu,
\q2 jogo mane uparo ni osiepeu kaka jotendu?
\q1 Donge rem nokayi
\q2 kaka dhako mamuoch kayo?
\q1 
\v 22 Kendo ka ipenjori iwuon,
\q2 “Angʼo momiyo ma osetimorena?”
\q1 En nikech richo mau mangʼeny omiyo
\q2 dugu oseneno kendo dendu osekethore.
\q1 
\v 23 Bende ja-Kush nyalo loko kit
\q2 piene kata kwach nyalo loko kido man kuome?
\q1 Kamano bende ok inyal timo maber,
\q2 in ngʼatno mongʼiyo gi timbe maricho.
\b
\q1 
\v 24 “Anakeu ka mihudhwe
\q2 miriembo gi yamb kalausi.
\q1 
\v 25 Ma e pokni
\q2 ma asechiwoni,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho,
\q1 “nikech wiu osewil koda
\q2 kendo useketo genou kuom nyiseche manono.
\q1 
\v 26 Anaelu duge mi aum wengeu
\q2 mondo omi wichkuot mau onere,
\q1 
\v 27 kaka terruok mau kod gombo mau mandhaga,
\q2 kod chode mau maonge wichkuot!
\q1 Aseneno timbeu mamono
\q2 ewi gode matindo kod e pewe.
\q1 Mano kaka nine malit, yaye Jerusalem!
\q2 Nyaka karangʼo mibiro bedo mochido?”
\c 14
\s1 Oro, kech gi ligangla
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach Jehova Nyasaye mane omiyo Jeremia e wach oro:
\q1 
\v 2 “Juda ywak,
\q2 mieche madongo winjo lit;
\q1 gidengo ne piny,
\q2 kendo ywak winjore koa Jerusalem.
\q1 
\v 3 Joka ruoth oro jotichgi manyo pi;
\q2 gidhi e sokni to ok giyud pi.
\q1 Gidwogo gi agulni mag-gi ka ok otuome pi,
\q2 ka giluor kendo gibuok, giumo wiyegi.
\q1 
\v 4 Lo nigi okak nikech onge koth e piny;
\q2 jopur luoro omako kendo giumo wiyegi.
\q1 
\v 5 Kata mwanda manie puodho
\q2 jwangʼo nyathine nikech onge lum.
\q1 
\v 6 Punde mag bungu chungʼ
\q2 ka kuonde motwo motingʼore gi malo,
\q1 kendo gigamo yweyo ka ondiegi;
\q2 wengegi ok nyal neno nimar onge kar kwath.”
\b
\q1 
\v 7 Kata obedo ni richowa nyisowa ni wan joketho,
\q2 yaye Jehova Nyasaye, tim gimoro nikech nyingi.
\q1 Wasebaro waweyo yoreni;
\q2 kendo wasetimo richo e nyimi.
\q1 
\v 8 Yaye geno mar Israel,
\q2 Jares mare e kinde mag thagruok,
\q1 en angʼo momiyo ichalo wendo e piny,
\q2 kaka jawuoth mobuoro otieno achiel?
\q1 
\v 9 Ere gima omiyo ichalo gi ngʼat mobuok,
\q2 kata ka jalweny maonge gi teko ma dokonygo ngʼato?
\q1 In e dierwa, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 kendo iluongowa kod nyingi; kik ijwangʼwa!
\p 
\v 10 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom jogi:
\q1 “Gihero bayo alanda
\q2 kendo tiendegi ok ywe.
\q1 Kuom mano, Jehova Nyasaye ok orwakogi;
\q2 omiyo koro obiro paro timbegi mamono,
\q2 kendo okumgi kuom richogi.”
\p 
\v 11 Eka Jehova Nyasaye nowachona, “Kik ilam mondo jogi odhi maber.
\v 12 Kata ka gitweyo chiemo; ok anawinj ywakgi; kata bed ni gichiwo misango miwangʼo pep kod chiwo mag cham, ok anarwakgi. To kata kamano ananeg-gi gi ligangla, kech kod dera.”
\p 
\v 13 To ne awacho niya, “Yaye, Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto, jonabi osebedo kanyisogi ni, ‘Ok unune ligangla kata kech bende ok nokau. Adiera, anamiu kwe mochwere kaeni.’ ”
\p 
\v 14 Eka Jehova Nyasaye nowachona, “Jonabigo koro miriambo e nyinga. Pok aorogi, kata walogi kata wuoyo kodgi. Ginyisou fweny manono, gikoro weche manono gilamo nyiseche manono kod pachgi giwegi morundore.
\v 15 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom jonabi makoro e nyinga: Ne ok aorogi, kata bed ni giwacho niya, ‘Onge ligangla kata kech manobi e pinyni.’ Jonabi gogo-go notiek gi ligangla kod kech.
\v 16 Kendo jogo ma gikorone nowit oko e yore mag Jerusalem nikech kech kod ligangla. Onge ngʼama noikgi kata mondegi, yawuotgi kata nyigi. Anaol kuomgi masiche mowinjore kodgi.
\p 
\v 17 “Wachnegi wachni:
\q1 “ ‘Mad wangʼa pongʼ gi pi wangʼ
\q2 otieno gi odiechiengʼ ma ok rum;
\q1 ne nyara mangili, joga,
\q2 osewinjo lit mar adhola,
\q2 gi hinyruok mapek.
\q1 
\v 18 Ka adhi e pinyno,
\q2 aneno jogo monegi gi ligangla;
\q1 ka adhi e dala maduongʼ,
\q2 to aneno masiche ma kech okelo.
\q1 Janabi kaachiel gi jadolo
\q2 osedhi e piny ma ok gingʼeyo.’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 19 Bende isekwedo Juda chuth?
\q2 Dibed ni ichayo Sayun?
\q1 Angʼo momiyo isehinyowa ma ok wanyal chango?
\q2 Ne wageno kwe to onge ber mosebiro,
\q2 kinde mar chang to nitie mana thagruok.
\q1 
\v 20 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 wayie gi timbewa mamono kod ketho mag wuonewa;
\q2 adiera wasetimoni richo.
\q1 
\v 21 Ne kuom nyingi kik ijarwa;
\q2 kik ijwangʼ kom duongʼ mari malich.
\q1 Par singruok mari kodwa kendo kik ikethe.
\q1 
\v 22 Bende nyiseche manono maonge
\q2 tich mar ogendini bende nyalo kelo koth?
\q1 Bende boche kendgi kelo ngʼidho?
\q2 Ooyo, en in, yaye Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa.
\q1 Emomiyo genowa ni kuomi,
\q2 nimar in ema itimo magi duto.
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 Eka Jehova Nyasaye nowachona kama: “Kata dabed ni Musa gi Samuel ema nyalo chungʼ e nyima, to ok anyal weyonegi richogi. Golgi oko e nyima! Wegi gidhi!
\v 2 To ka gipenji ni, ‘Ere kama wanyalo dhiyoe?’ To nyisgi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Mago matho ochomo, tho nonegi;
\q1 mago ma ligangla ochomo, noneg gi ligangla;
\q1 to mago ma kech ochomo, kech nonegi;
\q1 to mago ma twech ochomo, noter e twech.’ ”
\p 
\v 3 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya, “Abiro oro masiche angʼwen mopogore opogore, ma gin ligangla mar nek kod guogi maywayo gi mabor gi winy mafuyo e kor polo gi ondiegi mag bungu mondo okidhgi kendo tiekogi.
\v 4 Anami pinjeruodhi duto mag piny bed gibuok kuomgi nikech gima Manase wuod Hezekia ruodh Juda notimo e Jerusalem.
\q1 
\v 5 “Ere ngʼama nokechi,
\q2 yaye Jerusalem? Ere ngʼama biro ywagi?
\q2 Ere ngʼama nochungʼ ma penji kaka idhi?”
\q1 
\v 6 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya,
\q2 “Isedaga. Isiko mana kibaro iweyo yo.
\q1 Omiyo anaket lweta kuomi kendo tieki;
\q2 ok anatimni ngʼwono kendo.
\q1 
\v 7 Anapiedhgi gi odhech pietho e dhorangeye
\q2 mag dala maduongʼ mar piny.
\q1 Anakel lit kod kethruok ne joga,
\q2 nimar gitamore loko yoregi.
\q1 
\v 8 Anami mon ma chwogi otho mag-gi bedo mathoth
\q2 moloyo kwoyo manie dho nam.
\q1 E odiechiengʼ tir anakel ngʼama nego mana rowere;
\q2 kendo apoya nono anakelnegi lit kod bwok maduongʼ.
\q1 
\v 9 Miyo man-gi nyithindo abiriyo
\q2 nobed mool matho.
\q1 To chiengʼ marienyne nopodhi kapod en odiechiengʼ;
\q2 wiye nokuodi kendo chunye nochandre.
\q1 Ananeg jogo motony gi ligangla,
\q1 e nyim wasikgi,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Wuololo, minwa, angʼo momiyo ne inywola,
\q2 an ngʼat ma piny ngima piemgo kendo kedogo!
\q1 Pok aholo ngʼato kata an bende pok ohola,
\q2 to kata kamano ji duto kwongʼa.
\p 
\v 11 Jehova Nyasaye nowacho,
\q1 “Adier anaresi gi gima omiyo maber;
\q2 adier anami wasiki sayi,
\q2 e kinde mag masira kod kinde mag thagruok.
\b
\q1 
\v 12 “Bende dhano nyalo turo chuma,
\q2 chuma moa yo nyandwat kata mula?
\b
\q1 
\v 13 “Mwandu magu kod mago ma
\q2 ukano anachiw mondo yaki, maonge chudo,
\q2 nikech richo magu duto e pinyu mangima.
\q1 
\v 14 Anaketu ubed wasumbini ne wasiku
\q2 e piny ma ok ungʼeyo,
\q2 nimar mirimba biro moko mach mabiro wangʼou.”
\b
\q1 
\v 15 In ingʼeyo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
\q2 para kendo konya.
\q2 Chul kuor ne joma sanda.
\q1 Isenano koda omiyo kik iweya;
\q2 par kaka osesanda kochaya nikech in.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka wechegi nobiro,
\q2 ne achamogi;
\q1 ne gin morna,
\q2 kendo ilo mar chunya,
\q1 nimar iluonga gi nyingi,
\q2 yaye Jehova Nyasaye Maratego.
\q1 
\v 17 Ne ok abedo e kanyakla mar jojaro,
\q2 ne ok atimo nyasi kodgi;
\q1 to ne abedo kenda nikech lweti ne ni kuoma
\q2 kendo ne ipongʼa gi mirima.
\q1 
\v 18 Angʼo momiyo rem mara ok rum
\q2 kendo adhonda lich ma ok nyal thiedhore?
\q1 Bende inyalo bedona ka aora modwono,
\q2 mana ka soko motwo?
\p 
\v 19 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Ka ilokori iweyo richoni,
\q2 anaduogi mondo itina;
\q1 ka iwacho weche mowinjore, ma ok manono,
\q2 to ni inibed ngʼat ma wuoyo e loya.
\q1 We jogi oduog ira,
\q2 to in kik idog irgi.
\q1 
\v 20 Anaketi ibed ohinga ne jogi,
\q2 ohinga moger motegno mar mula;
\q1 giniked kodi to ok gini loyi,
\q1 nimar an kodi mondo akonyi kendo resi,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 21 “Anaresi e lwet joma timbegi mono
\q2 kendo akonyi e lwet joma ger.”
\c 16
\s1 Odiechiengʼ masira
\p 
\v 1 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona:
\v 2 “Kik ikendi mondo kik inywol yawuowi kata nyiri ka.”
\v 3 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom yawuowi gi nyiri monywol e pinyni kendo kuom mon ma minegi kod chwo ma wuonegi:
\v 4 “Ginitho gi tuoche maricho richo. Ok nogo nduchgi kata ik bende ok noikgi, to ginichal ka owuoyo manie lowo. Ligangla kod kech noneg-gi, to ringregi nobed chiemb winy mafuyo e kor polo kod le manie piny.”
\p 
\v 5 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: “Kik idonj e ot mantiere chiemb liel; kik iywagi bende kik ikechgi, nikech asegolo gwethna, herana kod ngʼwonona kuom jogi.
\v 6 Joma iwuoro to gi ji ajiya notho e pinyni. Ok noikgi kendo ok noywag-gi, bende onge ngʼama nongʼad dende kata lielo wiye nikech gin.
\v 7 Onge ngʼama nochiw chiemo mondo oogo joma goyo nduch joma otho kata mana newuoro kata miyo bende onge ngʼama nomigi math mondo oogi.
\p 
\v 8 “Kendo kik idonj e ot mantiere nyasi ma ibed piny mondo ichiem kendo metho.
\v 9 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: E ndalo ngimau kendo ka uneno anatiek koko mar ilo kae kod wende mag nyako midhi kendi kod wuowi madhi kendo.
\p 
\v 10 “Ka inyiso jogi gigi duto to gipenji ni, ‘Angʼo momiyo Jehova Nyasaye osechikonwa masira malich ka ma? Angʼo ma wasetimo marach? Richo mane ma wasetimo ne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa?’
\v 11 Eka iwachnegi ni Jehova Nyasaye owacho ni, ‘Nikech wuoneu nojwangʼa, mi giluwo bangʼ nyiseche manono mi gitiyonegi kendo lamogi. Ne gikweda kendo ok girito chikna.
\v 12 To usebedo joma timbegi mono moloyo wuoneu. Ne kaka ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomu luwo timbe manono mag chuny kar mondo gilwora.
\v 13 Kuom mano, anawitu oko mar pinyni nyaka e piny ma un kata wuoneu ok osengʼeyo, kendo kanyo unutine nyiseche moko manono odiechiengʼ gi otieno, nimar ok anangʼwon-nu.’ ”
\p 
\v 14 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya, “Kata kamano, ndalo biro, ma dhano ok nochak owachi ni, ‘Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima, manogolo jo-Israel Misri,’
\v 15 to giniwach ni, ‘Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima, manogolo jo-Israel e piny ma yo nyandwat kendo koa e pinje duto kama ne oseriembogie.’ Nimar anadwog-gi e piny mane amiyo kweregi.”
\p 
\v 16 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya, “To anaor jolupo mangʼeny kendo ginimakgi. Bangʼ mano anaor jodwar mangʼeny, kendo ginidwargi e got maduongʼ kod mago matindo kendo e kuonde pondo mokunyore e lwendni.
\v 17 Wengena ne oneno timbegi duto; ok gipondona, bende richogo ok opondona.
\v 18 Anachulgi nyadiriyo kuom timbegi mamono kod richo mag-gi, nikech gisenjawo pinya kod gigi mopa maonge ngima kendo gisepongʼo girkeni mara gi nyisechegi manono maonge tich.”
\q1 
\v 19 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, in e tekona kod ohingana,
\q2 kar pondona e ndalo chandruok,
\q1 in ema ogendini nobi iri koa e
\q2 tungʼ piny ka tungʼ piny mi giwachi ni,
\q1 “Wuonewa ne onge gimoro to mana nyiseche manono mag miriambo,
\q2 nyiseche mopa maonge tich mane ok otimonegi ber moro amora.
\q1 
\v 20 Bende ji loso nyisechegi giwegi?
\q2 Ee, to ok gin nyiseche!”
\b
\q1 
\v 21 “Emomiyo anapuonjgi
\q2 kendo tinendeni anapuonjgi,
\q2 tekona gi nyalona.
\q1 Eka giningʼe
\q2 ni nyinga en Jehova Nyasaye.”
\b
\c 17
\q1 
\v 1 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Richo mar Juda ondik gi kalamb chuma;
\q2 ogor gi gima bith e chunygi,
\q1 kendo e tunge
\q2 kende mag misango miwangʼoe liswa.
\q1 
\v 2 Kata mana nyithindgi paro
\q2 kendegi mag misango miwangʼoe liswa,
\q1 kod sirni mag Ashera
\q2 mantie bath yiende motimo otiep,
\q2 kendo e gode matindo motingʼore gi malo.
\q1 
\v 3 Goda maduongʼ manie piny
\q2 kod mwanduni gi nyak magi duto anami wasiki,
\q1 kaachiel gi kuonde magi motingʼore gi malo,
\q2 nikech richo manie pinyu duto.
\q1 
\v 4 Kethou uwegi nomi nomau girkeni mane amiyou.
\q2 Anami ubed wasumb wasiku e piny ma ok ungʼeyo,
\q1 nimar usemedo mirimba,
\q2 kendo enowangʼ nyaka chiengʼ.”
\p 
\v 5 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q2 “Okwongʼ ngʼatno ma genone ni kuom dhano,
\q1 ngʼatno mogeno kuom ringruok
\q2 mondo omiye teko,
\q2 kendo ma chunye aa kuom Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 6 Enochal ka bungu manie thim;
\q2 ok enowinj maber ka ber obiro.
\q1 Enodag kuonde motwo motimo ongoro,
\q2 kama otimo chumbi maonge ngʼama odakie.
\b
\q1 
\v 7 “To ogwedh ngʼatno moketo
\q2 geno mare kuom Jehova Nyasaye, kendo oyie kuome.
\q1 
\v 8 Enochal gi yien mopidh
\q2 but pi ma tiende nyaa e tiend aora.
\q1 Ok obed gi luoro ka liet obiro;
\q2 ite osiko mana ka ngʼich.
\q1 Oonge gi parruok e higa mar oro
\q2 kendo ok owe ma ok onyago olemo.”
\b
\q1 
\v 9 Chuny en jawuond moloyo gik moko duto
\q2 kendo ok nyal thiedhe.
\q2 En ngʼa manyalo ngʼeye?
\b
\q1 
\v 10 “An Jehova Nyasaye ema anono chuny
\q2 kendo apimo paro,
\q1 mondo achiwne ngʼato
\q2 kaluwore gi timne,
\q2 kendo kaluwore gi kaka kite chalo.”
\b
\q1 
\v 11 Kaka winyo ma butno e tongʼ mane ok onywolo,
\q2 e kaka ngʼatno mayudo mwandu gi yore ma ok kare.
\q1 Ka nus ngimane oserumo, mwandune noweye,
\q2 kendo gikone nonere malongʼo ni en ngʼama ofuwo.
\b
\q1 
\v 12 Kom duongʼ, motingʼ malo aa chakruok,
\q2 e kama ler mar lemo marwa.
\q1 
\v 13 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, geno mar Israel,
\q2 jogo duto mojwangʼi noyud wichkuot.
\q1 Jogo molokoni ngʼegi nondik nying-gi e buru
\q2 nikech gisejwangʼo Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 soko mar pi ngima.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Changa, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 kendo anachangi;
\q1 resa kendo anaresra,
\q2 nimar in kendi ema apaki.
\q1 
\v 15 Gisiko ka giwachona ni,
\q2 “Ere wach Jehova Nyasaye? Dak otimre sani!”
\q1 
\v 16 Pok aweyo bedo jakwath mari;
\q2 ingʼeyo ni pok agombo odiechiengʼ mar thagruok.
\q2 Gima wuok e dhoga ingʼeyo.
\q1 
\v 17 Kik ilokrina masira;
\q2 in e kar pondana e kinde mar thagruok.
\q1 
\v 18 Mad jogo masanda ne wichkuot,
\q2 to an kik wiya kuodi;
\q1 mad gibed gi bwok maduongʼ
\q2 to an kik ibwoga.
\q1 Kel gigi kuomgi e kinde mar masira;
\q2 kethgi gi kethruok manyadiriyo.
\s1 Rito odiechiengʼ lemo maler
\p 
\v 19 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye nowachona: “Dhi kendo ichungʼ e dhorangach miluongo ni dhoranga ji, kama ruodhi mag Juda donjogo kendo wuok godo oko; chungʼ bende e rangeye duto mag Jerusalem.
\v 20 Wachnegi, ‘Winj wach Jehova Nyasaye, yaye ruodhi mag Juda kod jo-Juda duto gi ngʼato angʼata modak e Jerusalem madonjo gie rangeyegi.
\v 21 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Bed motangʼ ma kik itingʼ misigo chiengʼ Sabato kata ikele kokalo e rangeye mag Jerusalem.
\v 22 Kik ukel misike koa ei uteu kata timo tich moro chiengʼ Sabato, to rit chiengʼ Sabato maler, mana kaka ne achiko kwereu.
\v 23 Kata kamano ne ok gichiko itgi kata winja; tokgi ne tek ta ma ok ginyal winjo wach kata winjo puonj.
\v 24 To ka inyalo bedo motangʼ kiluora, Jehova Nyasaye owacho, kendo onge misigo mikadhogo dhoranga dala maduongʼni chiengʼ Sabato, to irito chiengʼ Sabato maler ma ok itimo tich moro chiengʼno,
\v 25 eka ruodhi mabet e kom duongʼ Daudi nobi kakalo e rangeye mag dala maduongʼni gi jotendgi. Gin kod jotelo mag-gi ginibi ka giriembo geche kod farese, ka gin kaachiel gi jo-Juda kod jogo modak e Jerusalem, kendo dala maduongʼni enodage nyaka chiengʼ.
\v 26 Ji nobi koa e dala mag Juda kod mier molworo Jerusalem, koae gwengʼ Benjamin gi tiend gode matindo ma yo podho chiengʼ, koa e piny manie gode matindo kod Negev, ka gikelo misango miwangʼo pep kod misengini mamoko, chiwo mag cham, ubani gi chiwo mag goyo erokamano e od Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 27 To ka ok umiya luor mondo urit Sabato maler ma ok utingʼo misigo ka udonjo e rangeye Jerusalem chiengʼ Sabato, to anamok mach ma ok tho e rangeye mag Jerusalem manowangʼ kuondegi mochiel motegno.’ ”
\c 18
\s1 E od jachwe agulni
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mane obirone Jeremia koa ir Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 “Dhiyo e od Jachwe agulni, kendo kanyo anamiyie otena.”
\v 3 Omiyo ne adhi e od jachwe agulni, kendo ne ayude kar chwecho.
\v 4 To agulu mane ichweyo gi lowo nokethore e lwete; omiyo jachwechno nochweye agulu machielo, kochweye maber kaka ne odwaro.
\p 
\v 5 Bangʼe wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona:
\v 6 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya, “Yaye od Israel, donge anyalo timonu kaka jachwe agulni timo? Kaka lowo manie lwet jachwe agulni, e kaka un bende e lweta, yaye od Israel.
\v 7 Kapo ni sa moro amora alando ni piny kata pinyruodhi opudh oko, kata kethgi matiekgi,
\v 8 kendo ka ogandano mane asiemo olokore oweyo timbegi maricho, eka analok pacha mi ok anakelnegi masira mane asechano.
\v 9 Kendo ka kinde machielo alando ni piny kata pinyruoth onego ger kendo gur motegno,
\v 10 to kotimo tim marach e nyima kendo ok oluora, to anapar kendo kuom ber mane asechano mar timone.
\p 
\v 11 “Emomiyo koro wachne jo-Juda kod jogo modak Jerusalem, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Neuru! Aiko masira nikech un kendo achano chenro marach nikech un. Omiyo weuru yoreu maricho, ngʼato ka ngʼato, kendo ulok yoreu gi timbeu.’
\v 12 To gini dwoke ni, ‘Onge tiende. Wanadhi nyime gi chenro magwa wawegi; ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomwa noluw mana timbe mamono mar chunye marach.’ ”
\p 
\v 13 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Penjieuru ogendini:
\q2 En ngʼa mosewinjo gima chalo kama?
\q1 Gima lich mokadho osetim gi
\q2 Nyako Ngili ma en Israel.
\q1 
\v 14 Bende pe mag Lebanon rumo ngangʼ
\q2 koa kuondege maridore motimo lwendni?
\q1 Bende pige mangʼich mokwe mamol,
\q2 koa kuonde maboyo dwono?
\q1 
\v 15 To joga wigi osewil koda,
\q2 giwangʼo ubani ne nyiseche mopa manono,
\q1 manomiyo gichwanyore e yoregi
\q2 kendo e yore matindo machon.
\q1 Giseketogi gi wuotho e yore matindo mogondore,
\q2 kendo e yore ma ok opa.
\q1 
\v 16 Pinygi nodongʼ gunda,
\q2 mi enobedi gima inyiero manyaka chiengʼ;
\q1 jogo duto makalo bute nobwogi
\q2 kendo gini kin wigi.
\q1 
\v 17 Kaka yamo ma aa yo wuok chiengʼ,
\q2 anakegi e nyim wasikgi;
\q1 ananyisgi ngʼeya to ok wangʼa e
\q2 kinde mar masichegi.”
\p 
\v 18 Negiwacho, “Biuru, wangʼad rieko mar hinyo Jeremia; nimar puonj mar chik mikelo gi jadolo ok nolal, kata ngʼado rieko moa kuom joma riek, kata weche moa ir jonabi. Omiyo biuru, wahangne wach kendo kik wachik itwa ne gimoro amora mowacho.”
\q1 
\v 19 Winja, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
\q2 winj gima joma donjona wacho!
\q1 
\v 20 Bende ber inyalo chul gi tim marach?
\q2 To kata kamano gisekunyona bugo.
\q1 Par nine achungʼ e nyimi
\q2 kendo awuoyo ka akwayonegi,
\q2 mondo kik iol mirimbi kuomgi.
\q1 
\v 21 Omiyo we nyithindgi kech oka;
\q2 bolgi e teko mar ligangla.
\q1 We mondegi obed maonge nyithindo
\q2 kendo mon ma chwogi otho;
\q1 mad chwogi negi,
\q2 rowere mag-gi negi gi ligangla e kedo.
\q1 
\v 22 Mad ywak winji koa e utegi
\q2 ka ikelo joma dwaro monjogi apoya nono,
\q1 nimar gisekunyona bugo mondo gimaka
\q2 kendo giseketo obadho mondo gimak godo tienda.
\q1 
\v 23 To in ingʼeyo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 chenrogi duto mar nega.
\q2 Kik ingʼwon-negi kuom timbegi mag jendeke,
\q1 kata rucho richo mag-gi e nyim wangʼi.
\q2 Mad logi e nyimi;
\q2 kendo kumgi e kinde mag mirimbi.
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: “Dhiyo kendo ingʼiew njage mar lowo kuom jachwe agulni. Dhi gi jodong ji moko kod jodolo
\v 2 kendo idhi e Holo mar Ben Hinom, mantiere machiegni gi kar donjo mar Dhoranga Potshad. Go milome kanyo mar weche manyisi,
\v 3 kendo iwach ni, ‘Winjuru wach Jehova Nyasaye, yaye ruodhi mag Juda kod jo-Jerusalem. Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Winjuru! Anakel masira kae mano mi it ngʼato ka ngʼato mowinjo nosakni,
\v 4 nimar gisejwangʼa mi giseketo ka obedo mar nyiseche mamoko, gisewangʼo misengini e iye ne nyiseche ma gin kata wuonegi kata ruodhi mag Juda ne ok ongʼeyo, kendo gisepongʼo kae gi remb joma onge ketho.
\v 5 Gisegero kuonde motingʼore gi malo ne Baal mondo giwangʼ yawuotgi e mach kaka chiwo ne Baal, gimoro mane ok achiko kata tuomo, bende ne onge e pacha.
\v 6 Omiyo tangʼ, kinde biro, Jehova Nyasaye owacho, ma ji ok nochak oluong kae ni Tofeth kata Holo mar Ben Hinom, to noluonge ni Holo mar Nek.’
\p 
\v 7 “ ‘Ka eri ema nakethie chenro mag Juda kod Jerusalem. Anawe neg-gi gi ligangla e nyim wasikgi, e lwet jogo madwaro ngimagi, kendo anachiw ringregi kaka chiemo ne winy mafuyo e polo kod le manie piny.
\v 8 Anaketh dala maduongʼni kendo mi obed gima ijaro; jogo duto makalo bute nohum nono kendo gininyiere ka gineno adhondene duto.
\v 9 Anami gicham ringre yawuotgi kod nyigi, kendo ginichamre kendgi e kinde marach ma wasikgi ogengʼonigi ka dwaro ngimagi.’
\p 
\v 10 “Bangʼe initoo njageno ka jok midhigo neno,
\v 11 kendo iwachnegi, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho: Anaketh pinyni kod dala maduongʼni mana kaka aguch jachwecho itoyo mi ok nyal los kendo. Giniyik joma otho ei Tofeth ma thuolo nobed maonge.
\v 12 Ma e gima anatimne pinyni kod joma odak ka, Jehova Nyasaye owacho. Anami dala maduongʼni chal gi Tofeth.
\v 13 Ute man Jerusalem kod mago mag ruodhi Juda nodwany mana machal gi ute man Tofeth, mane giwangʼoe ubani ewi tado mag udi ne gik mochwe mae kor polo kendo olo misango miolo piny ne nyiseche manono.’ ”
\p 
\v 14 Bangʼe Jeremia noduogo koa Tofeth, kama Jehova Nyasaye noore mondo okore wach, kendo nochungʼ e agola mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye mi owachone ji duto ni,
\v 15 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Winjuru! Adhi kelone dala maduongʼni kod gwenge molwore masiche duto mane alando kuomgi, nikech ne tokgi tek ta kendo ne ok ginyal winjo wechena.’ ”
\c 20
\s1 Jeremia kod Pashur
\p 
\v 1 Ka jadolo Pashur wuod Imer, jatelo maduongʼ manie hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, nowinjo Jeremia kakoro gigie,
\v 2 nomiyo Jeremia janabi ogo mi otweye e lodi mar Dhorangach Mamalo mar Benjamin mantiere e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 3 Kinyne, ka Pashur nogonye e lodi, Jeremia nowachone niya, “Jehova Nyasaye ok luongi ni Pashur, to oluongi ni Magor-Misabib.
\v 4 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Anami ibed masira ni in iwuon kaachiel gi osiepeni duto; gi wengeni iwuon ininegi ka inegogi gi ligangla mar wasikgi. Anachiw jo-Juda duto ni ruodh Babulon, manotergi e piny Babulon kata negogi gi ligangla.
\v 5 Anami wasikgi mwandu duto mar dala maduongʼni gige duto moloso, gige duto ma nengogi tek kod mwandu duto mokan mag ruodhi Juda. Ginikawgi kaka gima opee mi notingʼ-gi ka iterogi Babulon.
\v 6 To in, Pashur, kod jogo duto modak e odi noteru e twech Babulon. Kanyo unuthoe kendo noyiku, in kod osiepeni duto mane isekoronegi miriambo.’ ”
\s1 Ywagruok Jeremia
\q1 
\v 7 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, ne iwuonda kendo nowuonda;
\q2 ne ihewa kendo iloya giteko.
\q1 Itugo koda odiechiengʼ mangima;
\q2 kendo ji duto nyiera.
\q1 
\v 8 Sa moro amora ma awuoyo,
\q2 aywak ka goyo milome mar lweny kod kethruok.
\q1 Omiyo wach Jehova Nyasaye osekelona ayany
\q2 kod wichkuot odiechiengʼ mangima.
\q1 
\v 9 To ka awacho.
\q2 “Ok analuonge kata wuoyo kendo e nyinge,”
\q2 wachne chalo mach e chunya,
\q1 mana ka mach marewo chokega.
\q2 Aol gi tingʼe e chunya; adier, ok anyal.
\q1 
\v 10 Awinjo ji mangʼeny kakwodho wach,
\q1 “Bwok nitie koni gi koni!
\q2 Wadonjneuru! Wadonjneuru!”
\q1 Osiepena duto rito mondo dhoga okier,
\q2 kagiwacho, “Sa moro inyalo wuonde;
\q2 eka bangʼe wanapodh kuome kendo wanachul kuor kuome.”
\b
\q1 
\v 11 To Jehova Nyasaye ni koda kaka jalweny maratego;
\q2 omiyo jogo masanda nochwanyre kendo ok giniloya.
\q1 Ok ginilo kendo ginibedi gi wichkuot malich;
\q2 wichkuot margi wich ok nowil godo.
\q1 
\v 12 Yaye Jehova Nyasaye Maratego,
\q2 in ngʼatno manono joma ratiro,
\q2 kendo manyo matut mar chuny kod paro,
\q1 mad iol gero mari kuomgi,
\q2 nimar ne in asetieko kora.
\b
\q1 
\v 13 Werne Jehova Nyasaye! Pak Jehova Nyasaye!
\q2 Oreso ngima joma nigidwaro,
\q2 e lwet joma timbegi mono.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Okwongʼ chiengʼ mane onywola!
\q2 Mad odiechiengʼ mane minwa onywola kik gwedhi!
\q1 
\v 15 Okwongʼ ngʼatno mane okelone wuonwa wach,
\q2 manomiye obedo gi mor, kowacho,
\q2 “Nyathi monywolni en wuowi!”
\q1 
\v 16 Mad ngʼatno chal gi mier mane
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owito oko maonge ngʼwono.
\q1 Mad owinj dengo gokinyi
\q2 kod ywak mar kedo e dier odiechiengʼ tir.
\q1 
\v 17 Nimar ne ok onega e ich,
\q2 ka ii minwa bedo kaka bur miika,
\q2 noyawre nyaka chiengʼ.
\q1 
\v 18 Angʼo momiyo ne awuok e ich
\q2 mondo ane thagruok kod lit,
\q2 kendo atiek odiechiengega e wichkuot?
\c 21
\s1 Nyasaye otamore winjo kwayo mar Zedekia
\p 
\v 1 Wach nobiro ne Jeremia koa ir Jehova Nyasaye kane Ruoth Zedekia noorone Pashur wuod Malkija kod jadolo Zefania wuod Maseya. Negiwacho:
\v 2 “Koro lamnwa Jehova Nyasaye nikech Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon monjowa. Sa moro Jehova Nyasaye nyalo timonwa honni mana kaka osetimonwa e kinde mosekalo mondo omi oa kuomwa.”
\p 
\v 3 To Jeremia nodwokogi niya, “Nyisuru Zedekia,
\v 4 ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho: Achiegni loko gige lweny manie lwetugo mondo ogou, magin mago mutiyogo mondo ukedgo gi ruodh Babulon kod jo-Babulon mantiere oko mar ohinga. Kendo anachokgi duto ei dala maduongʼni.
\v 5 An awuon abiro kedo kodi ka iya owangʼ kendo ka an gi mirima mager.
\v 6 Ananeg jogo modak e dala maduongʼni, chwo kaachiel gi le kendo masira malich noneg-gi.
\v 7 Bangʼ mano, Jehova Nyasaye wacho, anachiw Zedekia ruodh Juda, jotende kod joma ni e dala maduongʼni ma notony e masira, ligangla kod kech, ne Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon to gi wasikgi madwaro ngimagi. Enoneg-gi gi ligangla; ok enowenegi kata kechogi kata ngʼwononegi.’
\p 
\v 8 “To bende, med nyiso ji ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Ne, aketo e nyimi yor ngima kod yor tho.
\v 9 Ngʼato angʼata modak e dala maduongʼni noneg gi ligangla, kech kod masira. To ngʼatno mowuok kendo otingʼo bade ne jo-Babulon molworou; notony gi ngimane.
\v 10 Aramo mar timo ne dala maduongʼni marach ma ok maber, Jehova Nyasaye owacho. Enochiwe e lwet ruodh Babulon, kendo enotieke gi mach.’
\p 
\v 11 “Kuom mano, wachne od joka ruoth mar od Juda ni, ‘Winj wach Jehova Nyasaye;
\v 12 Yaye od Daudi, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Ngʼad bura makare okinyi ka okinyi;
\q2 kony ngʼatno ma imayo e lwet joma thire,
\q2 ka ok kamano to mirimba noolre oko,
\q1 kendo liel ka mach nikech
\q2 timbe mamono misetimo nowangʼ,
\q2 maonge ngʼama nyalo kweye.
\q1 
\v 13 Ok adwari, in Jerusalem,
\q2 un jogo modak ewi holoni,
\q1 e got mar mesa motimo lwanda,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho;
\q1 un ma uwacho niya, “En ngʼa manyalo kwedowa?
\q2 En ngʼa manyalo donjo kar pondowa?”
\q1 
\v 14 Anakumu moromo gi timbeu,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 Anamok mach e bunge magu manowangʼ
\q2 gimoro amora machiegni kodu.’ ”
\c 22
\s1 Kum ne ruodhi ma timbegi mono
\p 
\v 1 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: “Dhiyo e kar dak mar ruodh Juda kendo iland wachni kanyo:
\v 2 ‘Winj wach Jehova Nyasaye, yaye ruodh Juda, un joma bet e kom duongʼ Daudi, in, jotendi kod jogi madonjo gie dhorangeyegi.
\v 3 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Tim gima nikare kendo mowinjore. Res ngʼatno e lwet ngʼama thire, ngʼatno mosemaye. Kik itim marach kata tugo lweny gi jadak, kiye kata mon ma chwogi otho, kendo kik ichwer remo maonge gi wach ka eri.
\v 4 Nimar ka urito chikegi maber, eka ruodhi mabet e kom duongʼ mar Daudi nondonji gi e dhorangeye mag kar dak ruoth, ka giriembo geche kendo giidho farese, ka gin gi jotendgi kod jogegi.
\v 5 To ka ok urito chikegi, Jehova Nyasaye wacho, akwongʼora an owuon ni kar dak ruodhni nolal nono.’ ”
\p 
\v 6 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom kar dak mar ruodh Juda:
\q1 “Kata obedo ni in kaka Gilead ne an,
\q2 kaka wi got Lebanon,
\q1 adiera analoku kaka kama otwo,
\q2 ka mier maonge joma odakie.
\q1 
\v 7 Anaor joma tiekou,
\q2 ngʼato ka ngʼato gi gige lweny,
\q1 kendo ginitongʼ sirniu mabeyo mag sida
\q2 mi giwitgi ei mach.
\p 
\v 8 “Ji moa e pinje mangʼeny nokal e dala maduongʼni kendo ginipenjre kendgi giwegi ni, ‘Angʼo momiyo Jehova Nyasaye timo gima chalo kama ne dala maduongʼni?’
\v 9 To dwoko nobed: ‘Nikech gisejwangʼo singruok mar Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachgi kendo giselamo kendo tiyone nyiseche mamoko.’ ”
\q1 
\v 10 Kik uywag ruoth motho kata goyo nduru ne lal mare;
\q2 to onego, uywag malit ne ngʼatno moter e twech,
\q1 nikech ok enoduogi kata
\q2 neno piny mane onywole kendo.
\m 
\v 11 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye osewacho kawuoyo kuom Shalum wuod Josia, mane okawo loch bangʼ wuon-gi kaka ruodh Juda, “Osea ka kendo ok nodwogi.
\v 12 Enotho kama gisetere e twech; ok enone pinyni kendo.”
\q1 
\v 13 “Mano kaka none malit
\q2 ngʼatno magero kare mar dak maonge ratiro,
\q1 utene mamalo e yor mecho
\q2 koketo jothurgi tiyo maonge chudo.
\q1 
\v 14 Owacho, ‘Anagerne an owuon kar dak mara maduongʼ
\q2 ka en-gi ute mamalo malach.’
\q1 Omiyo oloso dirisni malach kuome,
\q2 olwore gi fito mar yiend sida,
\q2 kendo obuke gi range marakwaro.
\b
\q1 
\v 15 “Bedo gi yiende mag sida
\q2 mangʼeny nyalo miyo ibed ruoth?
\q1 Donge wuonu ne nigi chiemo kod math?
\q2 Notimo gima ratiro kendo nikare,
\q2 omiyo duto nobedo maber kode.
\q1 
\v 16 Ne ochungʼ motegno ne joma odhier
\q2 kendo ni gidwaro, kendo duto nobedo maber kode.
\q1 Donge mano e tiend ngʼeya?”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 17 “To wengeu kod chunyu ochikore
\q1 mana e yor yudo ohala gi mecho,
\q1 e chwero remo maonge gi wach
\q2 kuom thiro ji kod lweny.”
\m 
\v 18 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda:
\q1 “Ok giniywage ni:
\q2 ‘Yaye, owadwa! Yaye, nyamera!’
\q1 Ok giniywage ni:
\q2 ‘Yaye, jatenda! Yaye, duongʼ mari!’
\q1 
\v 19 Enoyike ka punda,
\q2 moywa kendo owit oko mar dhorangeye Jerusalem.”
\b
\q1 
\v 20 “Dhiyo Lebanon kendo iywag matek,
\q2 mad dwondi winjre Bashan,
\q1 ywagi ka ia Abarim,
\q2 nimar joma osiepenigo oseduny matindo tindo.
\q1 
\v 21 Ne amiyou siem e kinde mane uparo ni uritoru maber,
\q2 to ne iwacho ni, ‘Ok anachik ita!’
\q1 Ma osebedo yori chakre ibed rawera;
\q2 ok iseluora.
\q1 
\v 22 Yamo noriemb jokwadhu duto,
\q2 kendo joma osiepeni noter e twech.
\q1 Eka wiyi nokuodi kendo nogengʼni
\q2 nikech timbegi maricho.
\q1 
\v 23 Un jogo modak Lebanon,
\q2 modak e ute bao mag sida moger gi malo,
\q1 mano kaka unuywag malit ka rem ochopo kuomu,
\q2 rem machalo gi mar dhako mamuoch kayo!”
\p 
\v 24 Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya, “An Jehova Nyasaye mangima akwongʼora ni kata ne bed ni in Jehoyakin wuod Jehoyakim ruodh Juda, ni in e tere manie lweta ma korachwich, to pod dawuodhi oko.
\v 25 Anachiwi ne jogo madwaro ngimani kendo miluoro. Abiro chiwou ne Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon kod jo-Babulon.
\v 26 Anadiri oko kod miyo mane onywoli e piny machielo, kama onge ngʼama nonywole kuomu, kendo kanyo ema uduto unuthoe.
\v 27 Ok unuduogie piny ma ugombo duogoeni.”
\q1 
\v 28 Bende ngʼatni Jehoyakin en ngʼama ojar,
\q2 agulu motore, gino maonge ngʼama dwaro?
\q1 En angʼo momiyo en kod nyithinde
\q2 nyaka witgi oko e piny ma ok gingʼeyo?
\q1 
\v 29 Yaye piny, piny, piny,
\q2 winj wach Jehova Nyasaye!
\q1 
\v 30 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Kwan ngʼatni ka ngʼama onge nyathi,
\q2 ngʼatno ma ok nyal dhi nyime maber,
\q1 e kinde mar ngimane,
\q1 nimar onge gunde mane dhi maber,
\q2 onge manobed e kom duongʼ Daudi,
\q2 kata bed gi loch kendo ei Juda.”
\c 23
\s1 Bad yath makare
\p 
\v 1 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Mano kaka unune malit un jokwath maketho kendo keyo romba kar kwadhgi!”
\v 2 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wachone jokwath makwayo joga: “Nikech usekeyo romba kendo uriembogi kendo ok useritogi, anakumu kuom timbe mamono musetimo,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\v 3 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “An awuon anachok romba modongʼ e pinje duto kuonde maseriembogie anadwog-gi legegi kama gibiro nyaa kendo kwan-gi nomedre.
\v 4 Anamigi jokwath manoritgi, kendo ok ginibed maluor kata ok ginibwogi, bende onge manolal,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 5 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Kinde biro ma anami Daudi Bad Yath makare,
\q1 Ruoth manobed gi loch mar rieko
\q1 kendo tim gima kare kendo ratiro e piny.
\q1 
\v 6 E ndalone Juda noresi
\q1 kendo Israel nodag gi kwe.
\q1 Ma e nying ma ibiro luongego:
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye mamiyo wabedo jo-ratiro.”
\m 
\v 7 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Ndalo biro ma ji ok nowach kendo ni, ‘Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima, manogolo jo-Israel Misri,’
\v 8 to giniwachi, ‘Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima, mane ogolo nyithind Israel e piny ma yo nyandwat kendo e pinje duto mane oseriembogie.’ Bangʼe gibiro dak e pinygi giwegi.”
\s1 Jonabi ma jo-miriambo
\p 
\v 9 Kuom jonabi:
\q1 Chunya maiye ool;
\q2 chokega duto tetni.
\q1 Achalo ngʼama omer,
\q2 mana ka ngʼama divai osemero,
\q2 nikech Jehova Nyasaye kod wechene maler.
\q1 
\v 10 Piny opongʼ gi joma terore;
\q1 nikech kwongʼ, piny obaro okak
\q2 kendo kuonde kwath otimo ongoro.
\q1 Jonabi luwo bangʼ timbe mamono
\q2 kendo gitiyo gi teko mag-gi e yo ma ok nikare.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Jonabi kod jodolo ok oluoro Nyasaye;
\q2 kata mana ei hekalu mara ayudoe timbegi maricho.”
\q1 
\v 12 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Emomiyo yoregi nobed mapoth poth;
\q1 notergi e mudho
\q2 kendo kanyo ginipodhie piny.
\q1 Anakel masira kuomgi
\q2 e higa mokumgie.
\b
\q1 
\v 13 “Kuom jonabi mag Samaria
\q2 ne aneno gino mawangʼo ich:
\q1 Ne gikoro e nying Baal
\q2 kendo ma gimiyo joga Israel obayo yo.
\q1 
\v 14 Kendo e kind jonabi
\q2 mag Jerusalem aseneno gimoro malich mokadho:
\q1 Giterore kendo gidak e ngima mar miriambo.
\q2 Gijiwo joma timbegi mono,
\q1 mondo omi kik ngʼato
\q2 olokre owe timbene maricho.
\q1 Giduto gichalo Sodom ne an;
\q2 jo-Jerusalem chalo gi Gomora.”
\p 
\v 15 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho kuom jonabi:
\q1 “Anami gicham chiemo makech
\q2 kendo modh pi motimo sum,
\q1 nikech koa kuom jonabi mag
\q2 Jerusalem kia Nyasaye oselandore e piny ngima.”
\p 
\v 16 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q2 “Kik uchik itu ne gigo ma jonabi koronu;
\q1 gipongʼo itu gi geno mag miriambo.
\q2 Giwachonu fweny moa e pachgi giwegi,
\q2 ok moa e dho Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 17 Gisiko giwachone jogo ma jara ni,
\q2 ‘Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Unubed gi kwe.’
\q1 Kendo ne jogo maluwo timbe achach mag chunjegi wacho ni,
\q2 ‘Onge gima biro hinyowa.’
\q1 
\v 18 To en ngʼa kuomgi mosechungoe
\q2 kar ngʼado bura mar Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 mondo one kata owinji wachne?
\q1 
\v 19 Neuru, apaka mar Jehova Nyasaye
\q2 nomwomre gi mirima,
\q2 ka kalausi mafuyo e wiye joma timbegi richo.
\q1 
\v 20 Mirimb Jehova Nyasaye ok nodog
\q2 chien nyaka one ni ochopo thoro mar chunye.
\q2 E ndalo mabiro iniwinj tiende malongʼo.
\q1 
\v 21 Ne ok aoro jonabigi,
\q2 kata kamano giseringo gi wechegi;
\q1 ne ok awuoyo kodgi,
\q2 to kata kamano gisekoro wach.
\q1 
\v 22 To kane ginyalo chungoe
\q2 kara mar ngʼado bura,
\q1 dine gilando wechena ne joga
\q2 kendo gilokore gia e yoregi mamono,
\q2 kod timbegi mamono.”
\b
\q1 
\v 23 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Ok an Nyasaye mantie machiegni kende,
\q2 to an Nyasaye man mabor bende.”
\q1 
\v 24 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Bende ngʼato nyalo pondo
\q2 kuonde mopandore mondo omi kik anene?
\q2 Donge apongʼo polo gi piny?”
\p 
\v 25 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Asewinjo gima jonabi makoro e nyinga gi miriambo wacho. Giwacho ni, ‘Ne aleko! Ne aleko!’
\v 26 Nyaka karangʼo ma gigi nosik e chunje jonabi mariambogi, makoro gigo moa e pachgi giwegi?
\v 27 Giparo ni lek ma ginyisore giwegi nomi ji wigi nowil gi nyinga, mana kaka wuonegi wigi nowil koda kaluwore gilamo mane gilamogo Baal.”
\v 28 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “We janabi man-gi lek owach lekne, to we ngʼat man giwachna owache gadiera. Nimar en angʼo ma miudhwe nyalo timo gi cham?”
\v 29 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Donge wachna chalo gi mach kendo ka nyundo matoyo kidi matindo tindo?”
\p 
\v 30 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Emomiyo amon gi jonabi makwalo weche ma giwacho ni oa kuoma e kindgi giwegi.”
\v 31 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Ee, ok ahero jonabi ma milo lewgi giwegi kagiwacho ni, ‘Jehova Nyasaye owacho.’ ”
\v 32 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Adiera, ok ahero jogo makoro lek mag miriambo. Ginyisogi kendo giwito joga gi miriambo mag-gi maonge korgi gi atachgi, to ne ok aorogi kata yierogi. Ok gimi jogi ohala kata matin,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\s1 Wach mar miriambo kod jonabi ma jo-miriambo
\p 
\v 33 “Ka jogi, kata janabi kata jadolo, openji ni, ‘Wach mar Jehova Nyasaye en mane?’ To penjgi ni, ‘Wach mane? Anajwangʼu, Jehova Nyasaye owacho.’
\v 34 Ka janabi kata jadolo kata ngʼato angʼata owacho ni, ‘Ma en wach mar Jehova Nyasaye,’ to anakum ngʼatno kod joode duto.
\v 35 Ma e gima ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomu siko wachone osiepne kata watne: ‘Dwoko Jehova Nyasaye en angʼo?’ kata, ‘En angʼo ma Jehova Nyasaye wacho?’
\v 36 To kik ichak iwach kendo ni, ‘wach mar Jehova Nyasaye,’ nikech wach ngʼato ka ngʼato owuon ema bedone wach maber bangʼe ijaro weche Nyasaye mangima, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego ma Nyasachwa.
\v 37 Ma e gima usebedo ka unyiso janabi: ‘Jehova Nyasaye miyi dwoko mane?’ kata, ‘Jehova Nyasaye osewacho angʼo?’
\v 38 Kata obedo ni iwacho ni, ‘Ma e wach mar Jehova Nyasaye,’ to ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Ne itiyo gi weche ka iwacho ni, ‘Ma e wach mar Jehova Nyasaye,’ kata obedoni ne awachonu ni kik uwach ni, ‘Ma e wach mar Jehova Nyasaye.’
\v 39 Emomiyo, adiera wiya nowil kodu kendo ma agolu oko e nyim wangʼa kaachiel gi dala maduongʼ mane amiyou kod wuoneu.
\v 40 Anakelnu wichkuot manyaka chiengʼ ma en wichkuot ma wich ok nowilgo.”
\c 24
\s1 Kikepni ariyo mag ngʼope
\p 
\v 1 Bangʼ ka Jehoyakin wuod Jehoyakim ruodh Juda kod jotelo, jopecho kod jogoro mag Juda ne oseter e twech koa Jerusalem nyaka Babulon gi Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon, Jehova Nyasaye nonyisa kikepni ariyo mag ngʼope koketi e nyim hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 2 Okapu achiel ne nigi ngʼope mabeyo ahinya, kod mago mane osechiek chon; okapu machielo ne nigi ngʼope maricho, marach moloyo ma ok nyal cham.
\p 
\v 3 Eka Jehova Nyasaye nopenja niya, “En angʼo mineno, Jeremia?”
\p Ne odwoko niya, “Aneno ngʼope. Mabeyo to beyo ahinya, to maricho to richo ahinya ma ok nyal cham.”
\p 
\v 4 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona:
\v 5 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Ka ngʼope mabeyogi, akawo jogo moa Juda kodhi e twech kaka joma beyo, mane agolo kae kadhi e piny jo-Babulon.
\v 6 Wengena nongʼigi mondo gidhi maber, kendo anadwog-gi e pinyni. Anagergi kendo ok anamukgi; anapidhgi kendo ok anapudhgi.
\v 7 Anamigi chuny mar ngʼeya ni an Jehova Nyasaye. Ginibed joga kendo anabed Nyasachgi, nimar giniduog ira gi chunygi duto.’
\p 
\v 8 “Jehova Nyasaye wacho ni, ‘To mana kaka ngʼope maricho, ma ok nyal cham, e kaka anatimne Zedekia ruodh Juda, jotende kod jogo motony moa Jerusalem, kata obedo ni gidongʼ e pinyni kata gidak Misri.
\v 9 Abiro kelo kuomgi achaya kendo joma ok dwar gi pinjeruodhi duto manie piny, ma wangʼo ich kendo itiyo godo kaka ranyisi, gima ibwogogo ji kendo ikwongʼogo, ka moro amora ma aterogie.
\v 10 Anakel ligangla, kech kod masira kuomgi nyaka tiekgi e piny mane amiyogi kod wuonegi.’ ”
\c 25
\s1 Higni piero abiriyo mag twech
\p 
\v 1 Wach nobiro ne Jeremia kuom jo-Juda e higa mar angʼwen mar Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda, mane en higa mokwongo mar Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon.
\v 2 Omiyo Jeremia janabi nowachone jo-Juda duto kod jogo duto modak Jerusalem niya:
\v 3 Kuom higni piero ariyo gadek, kochakore e higa mar apar gadek mar Josia wuod Amon ruodh Juda nyaka kawuononi, wach Jehova Nyasaye osebirona kendo asewuoyonu pile ka pile, to pod ok uchiko itu.
\p 
\v 4 To kata obedo ni Jehova Nyasaye oseoronu jotichne ma jonabi duto pile ka pile, pod ok uchiko itu kata winjo.
\v 5 Negiwacho niya, “Lokreuru koro, ngʼato ka ngʼato, uwe yoreu mamono kod timbeu maricho, kendo unyalo dak e piny mane Jehova Nyasaye omiyou kod wuoneu nyaka chiengʼ.
\v 6 Kik ulu bangʼ nyiseche manono mondo utinegi kendo ulamgi; kik umi mirima maka gi gik ma lwetu oseloso. Eka ok anahinyu.”
\p 
\v 7 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “To ne ok uwinja, kendo usechwanya gi gik ma lwetu oseloso, kendo usekelo hinyruok kuomu uwegi.”
\p 
\v 8 Emomiyo Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho kama: “Nikech utamuru winjo wechena,
\v 9 analuong ji duto moa yo nyandwat kod jatichna Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon,” Jehova Nyasaye wacho, kendo giniked gi pinyni kod joma odakie kod ogendini molworogi duto. Anatiekgi chuth mi gibed gima bwogo ji kendo minyiero, kendo gima okethi nyaka chiengʼ.
\v 10 Anagol kuomgi koko mar ilo kod mor, dwond miaha kod mar wuowi madwaro kendo, koko mar kite rego kod ler mar taya.
\v 11 Pinyni mangima nobed piny mojwangʼ mokethore, kendo ogendinigi noti ne ruodh Babulon higni piero abiriyo.
\p 
\v 12 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “To ka higni piero abiriyo orumo, anakum ruodh Babulon kod pinye, piny jo-Babulon, nikech ketho mag-gi, kendo anakethe nyaka chiengʼ.
\v 13 Anakel kuom pinyno gik moko duto masewacho kuome, mago duto mondiki e kitabuni kendo okor gi Jeremia kuom ogendini duto.
\v 14 Gin giwegi ginibed wasumbini pinje mangʼeny kod ruodhi maroteke; anachulgi kaluwore gitimbegi kod tije mag lwetgi.”
\s1 Kikombe mar mirimb Nyasaye
\p 
\v 15 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, nowachona: “Kaw e lweta kikombeni moole divai mopongʼ mar mirimba kendo iket ogendini duto ma aori kuomgi omadhe.
\v 16 Ka gimadhe, ginibagni kendo ginilokre jonekni nikech ligangla ma abiro oro e kindgi.”
\v 17 Omiyo ne akawo kikombe mane ni e lwet Jehova Nyasaye kendo ma aketo ogendini duto mane oora irgi omadhe.
\b
\li1 
\v 18 Jerusalem kod dala duto mag Juda, ruodhi mag-gi kod jotende, mondo okethi kendo obed gima bwogo ji kendo gibed maonge luor kendo gima okwongʼ, mana kaka gin kawuono;
\li1 
\v 19 jogo monego madh divai gin, Farao ruodh Misri, jotije, jotende, kod joge duto;
\v 20 jopinje mamoko duto modak kanyo gi;
\li1 ruodhi duto mar piny Uz;
\li1 ruodhi duto mag jo-Filistia (mago mag Ashkelon, Gaza, Ekron kod jogo mane odongʼ Ashdod);
\li1 
\v 21 Edom, Moab kod Amon;
\li1 
\v 22 ruodhi duto mag Turo kod Sidon;
\li1 ruodhi mag pinje mokiewo e dho nam loka kocha;
\li1 
\v 23 Dedan, Tema, Buz kod jogo duto mantiere kuonde maboyo;
\li1 
\v 24 ruodhi duto mag Arabu kod ruodhi duto mag welo modak kama otwo;
\li1 
\v 25 kod ruodhi duto mag Zimri, Elam kod Media;
\li1 
\v 26 kod ruodhi duto moa yo nyandwat, machiegni kod man maboyo, achiel bangʼ machielo, pinjeruodhi duto mantiere e wangʼ piny.
\li1 Eka mogik, ruodh Sheshak bende nomadhe.
\b
\p 
\v 27 “Eka inyisgi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Methi, mer kendo ngʼogi, mi ipodh piny ma ok inyal chungo malo kendo nikech ligangla ma anaor e dieru.’
\v 28 To ka gitamore kawo kikombe e lweti kendo ok gimetho, to nyisgi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho: Nyaka umadhe!
\v 29 Neuru, asechako kelo masira kuom dala maduongʼ mondikie Nyinga, to adiera bende unyalo tony ne kum? Ok unutonyne kum nimar akelo ligangla kuom jogo modak e piny, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego owacho.’
\p 
\v 30 “Koro kor wechegi duto kuomgi kendo wachnegi ni:
\q1 “ ‘Jehova Nyasaye noruti koa malo;
\q2 nomor ka polo koa e kar dak mare maler,
\q2 kendo oruti gi teko kuom pinye.
\q1 Enokogi ka jogo ma biyo olemb mzabibu,
\q2 kogoyo koko ne jogo modak e piny.
\q1 
\v 31 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 Koko nowinjre e tungʼ piny ka tungʼ piny,
\q2 nimar Jehova Nyasaye noyar gik modonjnego ogendini;
\q1 nongʼadne ji duto bura
\q2 kendo joma timbegi richo noneg gi ligangla.’ ”
\p 
\v 32 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Neuru! Masira landore ne oganda koganda,
\q2 yamo mager futo koa e tunge piny.”
\m 
\v 33 E kindeno jogo moneg gi Jehova Nyasaye nokere kuonde duto kochakore e giko piny konchiel nyaka komachielo. Ok noywag-gi kata chokogi kata ikogi, to ginichal gi owuoyo mokee piny.
\q1 
\v 34 Ywaguru kendo denguru; un jokwath;
\q2 ngʼielreuru e buru, un jokwadh rombe.
\q1 Nimar sa mar negou osechopo;
\q2 unupodhi kendo ungʼinjru matindo tindo,
\q2 ka agulu molos mongʼith.
\q1 
\v 35 Onge kama jakwath noring dhiye,
\q2 jokwadh rombe bende onge kama nopondie.
\q1 
\v 36 Winj ywak jokwath,
\q2 dengo mar jokwadh rombe,
\q2 nimar Jehova Nyasaye ketho kuondegi mag kwath.
\q1 
\v 37 Kuonde dak man-gi kwe iketho
\q2 nikech mirima mager mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 38 Kaka sibuor enowe kare mar dak,
\q2 kendo pinygi nodongʼ nono,
\q1 nikech ligangla mar ngʼama thiro ji
\q2 kendo ligangla mar mirimb Jehova Nyasaye mager.
\c 26
\s1 Jeremia obwog gi tho
\p 
\v 1 E chakruok mar loch Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda, wachni nobiro koa ir Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Chungi e laru mar od Jehova Nyasaye kendo iwuo gi ji duto manie dala mar Juda ma lemoga e od Jehova Nyasaye. Nyisgi gik moko duto manyisi; kik iwe kata wach achiel.
\v 3 Sa moro ginichik itgi kendo ngʼato ka ngʼato olokre owe yorene maricho. Eka analok pacha kendo ok anakel kuomgi masira mane achano nikech timbe maricho magisetimo.
\v 4 Wachnegi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Ka ok uwinja kendo uluwo chikena, ma aseketo e nyimu,
\v 5 kendo ka ok uwinjo weche mag jotichna ma jonabi, maseoronu pile ka pile (kata kamano pod ok uwinjo),
\v 6 bangʼe anami odni obed ka Shilo kendo dala maduongʼni ka gima okwongʼ e dier ogendini duto mag piny.’ ”
\p 
\v 7 Jodolo, jonabi kod ji duto nowinjo Jeremia kawacho wechegi e od Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 8 To bangʼ ka Jeremia nosetieko nyiso ji duto gik moko duto mane Jehova Nyasaye ochike mondo owachi, jodolo, jonabi kod ji duto nomake kendo owachone niya, “Nyaka itho!
\v 9 Angʼo ma omiyo ikoro e nying Jehova Nyasaye ni odni biro chalo ka Shilo kendo ni dala maduongʼni nojwangʼ kendo nokethi maonge ngʼama nodagie?” Kendo ji duto nochokore kolworo Jeremia e od Jehova Nyasaye.
\p 
\v 10 Ka jotend jo-Juda nowinjo wechegi, negia kar dak mar ruoth ma gidhi nyaka e od Jehova Nyasaye kendo negikawo keregi e kar donjo mar Dhorangach Manyien mar od Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 11 Eka jodolo kod jonabi nowachone jotelo kod ji duto niya, “Ngʼatni onego ngʼadne buch nek nikech nokoro kuom dala maduongʼni. Usewinje gi itu uwegi!”
\p 
\v 12 Eka Jeremia nowachone jotelo duto kod ji duto niya, “Jehova Nyasaye ne oora mondo akor kuom odni kod dala maduongʼni gigo duto musewinjo.
\v 13 Koro lokuru yoreu gi timbeu kendo uluor Nyasachu. Eka Jehova Nyasaye nolok pache kendo ok nokel masira kuomu mosechano timonu.
\v 14 Anto an e lweti; timnauru gima uneno ka ber kendo nikare.
\v 15 To ngʼeuru gadieri ni, ka unega, to unukel ketho kuom chwero remo maonge ketho kuomu uwegi kendo kuom dala maduongʼni gi jogo modak e iye, nimar adiera Jehova Nyasaye oseora iru mondo awachnu wechegi duto ka uwinjo gi itu.”
\p 
\v 16 Eka jotelo duto kod ji duto nowachone jodolo gi jonabi niya, “Ngʼatni ok onego ngʼadne buch tho! Osewuoyonwa e nying Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa.”
\p 
\v 17 Jodongo moko mag piny nosudo nyime e lela kendo owachone chokruok mangima mar ji ni,
\v 18 “Mika maa Moresheth nokoro e ndalo Hezekia ruodh Juda. Nonyiso jo-Juda duto ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Sayun ibiro pur ka puodho,
\q2 Jerusalem biro dongʼ gunda,
\q2 got matin mogerie hekalu nobed ka bungu motwere moyugno.’
\m 
\v 19 Bende Hezekia ruodh Juda kata ngʼato angʼata man Juda nonegi? Donge Hezekia noluoro Jehova Nyasaye kendo omanyo ngʼwono mare? Kendo donge Jehova Nyasaye noloko pache, mi omiyo ne ok okelo masira kuomgi? Wachiegni kelo masira malich kuomwa wawegi!”
\p 
\v 20 (Koro Uria wuod Shemaya moa Kiriath Jearim ne ngʼat machielo mane okoro e nying Jehova Nyasaye; nokoro mana gik machalre kuom dala maduongʼni kendo pinyni mana kaka Jeremia notimo.
\v 21 Ka Ruoth Jehoyakim kod jotende duto nowinjo wechege, ruoth ne dwaro mondo onege. To Uria nowinjo ma kendo oringo ka luoro omake nyaka Misri.
\v 22 Ruoth Jehoyakim, kata kamano, nooro Elnathan wuod Akbor nyaka Misri, kaachiel gi chwo mamoko.
\v 23 Negigolo Uria Misri kendo gitere ne Ruoth Jehoyakim, mane omiyo onege gi ligangla kendo dende owiti e kar yiko mar ji ajiya.)
\p 
\v 24 Bende, Ahikam wuod Shafan noriwo Jeremia lwedo, kendo omiyo ne ok ochiwe e lwet jogo mondo onege.
\c 27
\s1 Juda noti ne Nebukadneza
\p 
\v 1 E chakruok mar loch Zedekia wuod Josia ruodh Juda, wachni nobiro ne Jeremia koa ir Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye nowachona: “Los jok gi tol kod lodi moriw kendo ikete e ngʼuti.
\v 3 Eka ior wach ne ruodhi mag Edom, Moab, Amon, Turo kod Sidon kokalo kuom jombetre mosebiro Jerusalem ir Zedekia ruodh Juda.
\v 4 Migi ote mar jotendgi kendo iwachi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego ma, Nyasach Israel, wacho: “Nyisuru jotendu kama:
\v 5 Kuom tekona maduongʼ asechweyo piny gi joge kod le duto manie iye, kendo achiwo gigagi ne ngʼato angʼata mahero.
\v 6 Koro anachiw pinjeu ne jatichna Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon; anami kata le mag bungu winje.
\v 7 Ogendini duto notine kod wuode kod nyakware ma wuowi nyaka kinde mar pinye chopi; eka pinje mangʼeny kod ruodhi maroteke nokete obed jatichgi.
\p 
\v 8 “ ‘ “Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya: Kapo ni piny kata gwengʼ moro amora ok noti ne Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon kata kulo wiye e bwo jok mare, to anakum pinyno gi ligangla, kech kod masira, nyaka ane ni atieke gi lwete.
\v 9 Omiyo kik uchik itu ne jonabi magu, jokor wach magu, joloknu lek, jo-nyakalondo kata ajuoke magu manyisou ni ok unutine ruodh Babulon.
\v 10 Gikoronu miriambo ma biro miyo idarou mabor gi pinyu; anariembu kendo unutho.
\v 11 To ka oganda moro amora enokulre e bwo jok mar ruodh Babulon mi otine, to anami ogandano odongʼ e pinye owuon mondo opure kendo mondo odagi kanyo, Jehova Nyasaye owacho.” ’ ”
\p 
\v 12 Ne amiyo Zedekia ruodh Juda wach achielni. Ne awacho niya, “Kul wiyi e bwo jok mar ruodh Babulon; tine kod joge, to ibiro dak.
\v 13 Angʼo madimi in kod jogi tho e dho ligangla, kech kod masira mano ma Jehova Nyasaye osechano timo ni ogendini ma ok bi tiyone ruodh Babulon?
\v 14 Kik uchik itu ne jonabi mawachonu ni, ‘Ok ubi tiyone ruodh Babulon,’ nimar gikoronu miriambo.
\v 15 Jehova Nyasaye wacho ni, ‘Ok aorogi. Gikoro miriambo e nyinga. Emomiyo, anariembu kendo unulal nono, un kaachiel gi jonabi ma koronu.’ ”
\p 
\v 16 Eka ne awachone jodolo kod jogi duto niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Kik uchik itu ne jonabi mawacho ni, ‘Machiegnini koro gigo duto moa e od Jehova Nyasaye ibiro duogi koa Babulon.’ Gikoronu miriambo.
\v 17 Kik iwinjgi. Tine ruodh Babulon, to inibed mangima. Angʼo momiyo dala maduongʼni nyaka kethi?
\v 18 Ka gin jonabi kendo gin-gi wach Jehova Nyasaye, to mondo gikwa Jehova Nyasaye Maratego gigo mabeyo modongʼ e od Jehova Nyasaye kod e kar dak mar ruodh Juda kod e Jerusalem kik ter Babulon.
\v 19 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho kuom sirni, Nam, gik minyalo tingʼ kod gik mamoko modongʼ e dala maduongʼni,
\v 20 mane Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon ne ok okawo sa mane otero Jehoyakin wuod Jehoyakim ruodh Juda e twech kogole Jerusalem nyaka Babulon kaachiel gi joka ruoth moa Juda gi Jerusalem,
\v 21 ee, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho kuom gigo mane odongʼ e od Jehova Nyasaye kendo e kar dak mar ruodh Juda kod e Jerusalem:
\v 22 ‘Notergi Babulon kendo kanyo ginidongʼ nyaka odiechiengʼ ma anabi kawogie. Eka anadwog-gi kendo aketgi kae.’ ” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\c 28
\s1 Hanania jakoro ma ja-miriambo
\p 
\v 1 E dwe mar abich mar higa nogono, higa mar angʼwen, e chakruok mar loch mar Zedekia ruodh Juda, janabi Hanania wuod Azur, manoa Gibeon, nowachona e od Jehova Nyasaye e nyim jodolo kod ji duto ni:
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Anatur jok mar ruodh Babulon.
\v 3 Kuom higni ariyo abiro duogo kae gik moko duto mag od Jehova Nyasaye mane Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon ogolo kae kendo otero Babulon.
\v 4 Bende anaduog kae Jehoyakin wuod Jehoyakim ruodh Juda kod jogo mamoko duto mane oter e twech koa Juda mane odhi Babulon,’ Jehova Nyasaye owacho, ‘nimar anatur jok mar ruodh Babulon.’ ”
\p 
\v 5 Eka janabi Jeremia nodwoko janabi Hanania e nyim jodolo kod ji duto mane ochungʼ e od Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 6 Nowacho niya, “Amin! Mad Jehova Nyasaye tim kamano! Mad Jehova Nyasaye chop singruok mar weche misekoro kuom kelo gige od Jehova Nyasaye kod joma notwe duto kae koa Babulon.
\v 7 Kata kamano, chik iti ne gima adwaro wachonu ka uwinjo kendo ka ji duto winjo:
\v 8 E kinde machon jonabi mane obiro moteloni kendo otelona nokoro kuom lweny, chandruok kod masira kuom pinje mangʼeny kod pinjeruodhi madongo.
\v 9 To janabi makoro kwe nowinji mana ka ngʼatno moor gi Jehova Nyasaye adier mana ka gima okoro otimore.”
\p 
\v 10 Eka janabi Hanania nogolo jok e ngʼut janabi Jeremia kendo oture,
\v 11 kendo nowacho e nyim ji duto niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Mana e yo machalre gima ema anagolie jok mar Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon mane oketo e ngʼut ogendini kapok higni ariyo orumo.’ ” Bangʼ wacho ma, janabi Jeremia nochungo modhi.
\p 
\v 12 Mapiyo bangʼ ka janabi Hanania ne oseturo jok e ngʼut janabi Jeremia, wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia:
\v 13 “Dhiyo kendo inyis Hanania, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Iseturo jok mar bao, to e kar mano enoketni jok mar chuma.
\v 14 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Anaket jok mar chuma e ngʼut ogendinigi mondo gitine Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon, kendo ginitine. Kendo anamiye teko ewi le mag bungu.’ ”
\p 
\v 15 Eka janabi Jeremia nowachone janabi Hanania, “Winji Hanania! Jehova Nyasaye pok oori, to isehoyo ogandagi mondo ogen kuom miriambo.
\v 16 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Achiegni goli e pinyni. Mana e higani idhi tho, nikech iseyalo ngʼanyo ne Jehova Nyasaye.’ ”
\p 
\v 17 E dwe mar abiriyo mar higa onogono, Hanania janabi notho.
\c 29
\s1 Baruwa ne joma ni e twech
\p 
\v 1 Ma e baruwa mane janabi Jeremia ooro koa Jerusalem ne jodongo mane otony e dier jotwech kod ne jodolo, jonabi kod ji mamoko duto mane Nebukadneza notero e twech koa Jerusalem nyaka Babulon.
\v 2 (Ma ne en bangʼ ka Ruoth Jehoyakin kod min ruoth, jotelo mag agola kod jotend Juda gi Jerusalem, jopecho gi jogoro osedhi e twech koa Jerusalem.)
\v 3 Nomiyo Elasa wuod Shafan kod Gemaria wuod Hilkia baruwa, jogo mane Zedekia ruodh Juda nooro Babulon ir Ruoth Nebukadneza. Kawacho niya:
\pm 
\v 4 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho ne jogo duto mane atero e twech koa Jerusalem nyaka Babulon:
\v 5 “Geruru udi kendo udag kanyo; pidhuru puothe kendo ucham gik ma ginyago.
\v 6 Nyomburu mondo onywol yawuowi kod nyiri; yuduru mon ne yawuotu kendo uchiw nyiu mondo onyuom, magin bende ginywol yawuotgi kod nyigi mondo kwanu omedre kendo kik udog chien.
\v 7 Bende, dwaruru kwe kod mwandu mar dala maduongʼ ma aseterou e twech. Lamuru Jehova Nyasaye, ndalono nikech kodhi maber to un bende unudhi maber.”
\v 8 Ee, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: “Kik iwe jonabi kod joma neno wach e lek manie dieru wuondu. Kik uchik itu ne lek ma gileko nikech mano miyo gimedo leko.
\v 9 Gikoro miriambo gi nyinga. Ok aorogi,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\pm 
\v 10 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: “Bangʼ ka usetieko higni piero abiriyo e Babulon, to anabi iru kendo achop singo mara mar ngʼwono mondo aduogu ka.”
\v 11 Nimar Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Angʼeyo chenro ma an-go kodu. Chenro mar dhi maber to ok mar hinyou, chenro mar miyou geno kod ngima mabiro.
\v 12 Eka unuluonga mi anabi kendo ulama, to anawinju.
\v 13 Unudwara kendo unuyuda ka udwara gi chunyu duto.
\v 14 Ununwangʼa kendo anaduogu ka ua e twech. Anachoku ka ua e pinje duto kod kuonde ma asekeyoue kendo anaduogu kama ne uae ka aterou e twech,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\pm 
\v 15 Unyalo wacho niya, “Jehova Nyasaye osemiyowa jonabi ei Babulon,”
\v 16 to ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom ruoth mobet e kom duongʼ mar Daudi kod jogo duto modongʼ e dala maduongʼni, jopinyu mane ok odhi kodu e twech;
\v 17 adiera, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho: “Anaor ligangla, kech kod masira kuomgi kendo analokgi ka ngʼope maricho ma ok nyal cham.
\v 18 Analawgi gi ligangla, kech kod masira kendo anami gibed joma bwogo gwenge duto manie piny kendo gir kwongʼ kod bwok, gima ok onego mi luor kendo ma jaricho, e dier ogendini duto mane aseriembogie.”
\v 19 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Nimar pok giwinjo wechena, ma gin weche mane aoronegi kuom jotichna ma jonabi. To kata mana un joma ne oter e twech pok uwinja,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\pm 
\v 20 Emomiyo, winjuru wach Jehova Nyasaye, un joma ni e twech duto ma aseriembo koa Jerusalem nyaka Babulon.
\v 21 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho kuom Ahab wuod Kolaya kod Zedekia wuod Maseya, ma koronu miriambo e nyinga: “Anachiwgi ne Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon, kendo enoneg-gi e nyimu ka uneno.
\v 22 Nikech gin, joma ni e twech duto moa Juda man Babulon noti gi kwongʼni kawacho ni: ‘Mad Jehova Nyasaye timnu mana kaka notimone Zedekia kod Ahab, mane ruodh Babulon owangʼo e mach.’
\v 23 Nimar gisetimo gik mamono ei Israel; giseterore gi monde jobathgi kendo e nyinga gisewacho miriambo, mane ok anyisogi mondo giwachi. Angʼeye kendo an janeno kuom wachno,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\s1 Wach ne Shemaya
\p 
\v 24 Nyis Shemaya ja-Nehelam,
\v 25 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Ne ioro barupe e nyingi iwuon ne ji duto man Jerusalem, ne Zefania wuod Maseya jadolo, kendo ne jodolo mamoko duto. Ne iwachone Zefania ni,
\v 26 ‘Jehova Nyasaye oseyieri jadolo kar Jehoyada mondo ibed jarit od Jehova Nyasaye; omiyo koro ngʼato ma janeko mawuondore ni janabi onego itwe gi nyororo kod chuma molworo ngʼute.
\v 27 Marangʼo pod ok imako Jeremia moa Anathoth, ma ketore ni janabi e dieru?
\v 28 Oseoranwa wachni Babulon: Enobed kinde marabora. Emomiyo geruru udi kendo udagie eigi; pidhuru puothe kendo ucham gigo ma ginyago.’ ”
\p 
\v 29 Zefania jadolo, kata kamano, nosomo baruwani ne Jeremia janabi.
\v 30 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia ni,
\v 31 “Or wachni ne joma ni e twech duto: ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom Shemaya ja-Nehelam: Nikech Shemaya osekoronu, kata obedo ni ne ok aore, kendo osemiyo uyie gi miriambo,
\v 32 ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Adier, anakum Shemaya ja-Nehelam kod gunde. Onge ngʼama nodongʼ kuom joge, kata neno gik mabeyo mabiro timo ne joga, nikech oselando mondo ji ongʼanyna. An Jehova Nyasaye ema awacho kamano.’ ”
\c 30
\s1 Oduog jo-Israel
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mane obirone Jeremia koa kuom Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Ndik e kitabu weche duto masewachoni.’
\v 3 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, ‘Ndalo biro ma anaduog joga Israel kod Juda koa e twech kendo achokgi e piny mane amiyo kweregi mondo okaw,’ Jehova Nyasaye owacho.”
\p 
\v 4 Magi e weche mane Jehova Nyasaye owacho kuom Israel gi Juda:
\v 5 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Ywak mar luoro winjore,
\q2 en bwok malich, to ok kwe.
\q1 
\v 6 Koro lingʼuru mondo uparane:
\q2 Bende dichwo nyalo nywolo nyithindo?
\q2 To kare angʼo momiyo aneno dichwo ka dichwo maratego,
\q1 komako iye ka dhako mamuoch kayo,
\q2 ka luoro omakogi ka joma chiegni tho?
\q1 
\v 7 Mano kaka odiechiengʼno nobed malich!
\q2 Onge manochal kode.
\q1 Enobed kinde mag chandruok ne Jakobo,
\q2 to norese.’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho niya,
\q2 “ ‘E odiechiengʼno anatur jok manie ngʼutgi,
\q1 kendo anachod nyoroche motwegigo;
\q2 joma welo ok nochak oketgi wasumbini mag-gi kendo.
\q1 
\v 9 To kata kamano ginitine Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachgi
\q2 kod Daudi ruodhgi,
\q2 ma anamigi.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 “ ‘Omiyo kik iluor, yaye Jakobo jatichna;
\q2 kik ibwogi, yaye Israel,’
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 ‘Adier anaresi kia e piny mabor,
\q2 in kaachiel gi nyikwayi koaye piny motwegie.
\q1 Jakobo nobed gi kwe
\q2 kendo norite maonge ngʼama nomiye luoro.
\q1 
\v 11 Anabed kodi kendo anaresi,’
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\q1 ‘Kata obedo ni atieko chuth ogendini
\q2 duto ma akeyou e diergi,
\q1 ok anatieki chuth.
\q2 Anakumu ka angʼadonu bura makare;
\q2 ok anaweu ma ok akumou.’
\p 
\v 12 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Adhola mari ok nyal thiedhi,
\q2 hinyruok mari okalo chango.
\q1 
\v 13 Onge ngʼama nyalo chiwo kwayoni kari,
\q2 kendo onge gima nyalo thiedhoni adhola,
\q2 kata manyalo changi.
\q1 
\v 14 Joma ne osiepeni duto wigi osewil kodi;
\q2 kendo ok gidewi.
\q1 Asegoyi mana ka jasigu
\q2 kendo kumi mana ka ngʼama kwiny,
\q1 nikech ketho mari duongʼ
\q2 kendo richoni ngʼeny.
\q1 
\v 15 Angʼo momiyo iywak kuom adhondi,
\q2 to in-gi rem ma ok thiedhre?
\q1 Asekumou kamano nikech richou ngʼeny,
\q2 kendo nikech timbeu maricho lich.
\b
\q1 
\v 16 “ ‘To jogo duto motiekou notieki;
\q2 wasiku duto noter e twech.
\q1 Jogo momayou nomagi;
\q2 jogo moketonu obadho anaketnegi obadho.
\q1 
\v 17 Anamiyi ngima maber
\q2 kendo anathiedh adhondeni,’
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho,
\q1 ‘nikech iluongi ni ngʼama owit oko,
\q2 Sayun maonge ngʼama dewo.’
\p 
\v 18 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “ ‘Anaduog mwandu mag hembe Jakobo
\q2 kendo abed gi ngʼwono e kuondege mag dak;
\q1 dala maduongʼ noger kendo e kuondege mano okethe,
\q2 kendo kar dak ruoth noger e kare malongʼo.
\q1 
\v 19 Jogi nodwok erokamano ka giwer
\q2 kendo ka gikok gi mor.
\q1 Anamed kwan mag-gi,
\q2 kendo ok ginidog chien;
\q1 mi anamigi duongʼ,
\q2 kendo ok nokawgi matin.
\q1 
\v 20 Nyithindgi nochal kaka e ndalo machon,
\q2 kendo anagur anywolagi motegno,
\q2 mi anakum jogo duto ma thirogi.
\q1 
\v 21 Jatendgi nobed achiel kuomgi;
\q2 jatendgi noa e diergi.
\q1 Anakele machiegni kendo enobi machiegni koda,
\q2 nimar en ngʼa manyalo chiwore,
\q2 mondo obed machiegni koda?’ ”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 22 “ ‘Omiyo unubed joga,
\q2 kendo anabed Nyasachu.’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 23 Neuru, apaka mar Jehova Nyasaye biro mwomore gi mirimbe,
\q2 yamo mafuto malich ka futo e wiye joma timbegi mono.
\q1 
\v 24 Mirima mager mar Jehova Nyasaye ok nodog chien
\q2 nyaka one ni ochopo dwaro mar chunye.
\q2 E ndalo ma biro iniwinj tiend wachni.
\c 31
\p 
\v 1 Jehova Nyasaye nowacho e kindeno niya, “Anabed Nyasach dhout Israel duto, kendo ginibed joga.”
\p 
\v 2 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q2 “Jogo motony e ligangla noyud ngʼwono e piny motimo ongoro;
\q2 anabi mondo ami Israel yweyo.”
\p 
\v 3 Jehova Nyasaye nofwenyorenwa chon, kawacho niya:
\q1 “Aseherou gihera manyaka chiengʼ;
\q2 aseomou gihera mar ngʼwono.
\q1 
\v 4 Anageru kendo to bende enogeru,
\q1 yaye Israel ma nyako ngili.
\q2 Bende unugo nyiduongeu kendo,
\q2 mi udhi oko ma umiel gi ilo.
\q1 
\v 5 Bende unupidh mzabibu e gode
\q2 matindo mag Samaria;
\q1 jopur nopidhgi,
\q2 kendo ginibed mamor gi olembegi.
\q1 
\v 6 Odiechiengʼ moro nobedie ma jorit noywagi
\q2 e gode matindo mag Efraim niya,
\q2 ‘Biuru wadhi Sayun, ir Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa.’ ”
\p 
\v 7 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q2 “Wer gi ilo ne Jakobo;
\q2 kog matek ne jotelo madongo mag ogendini.
\q1 Onego pak magu owinjre, kendo uwachi niya,
\q2 ‘Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, res jogi, jo-Israel mane otony.’
\q1 
\v 8 Ne, anakelgi ka gia e piny
\q2 man yo nyandwat,
\q1 kendo achokgi ka gia e tungʼ
\q2 piny ka tungʼ piny duto.
\q1 Dhano ma galamoro nodwogi motingʼo muofni
\q2 kod rongʼonde,
\q2 mine ma yach kod mamuoch kayo.
\q1 
\v 9 Giniduogi ka giywak;
\q2 gini lem sa ma aduogogi.
\q1 Anatelnegi e bath aore man-gi pi,
\q2 e kuonde mopie ma ok ginichwanyre,
\q1 nikech an wuon Israel,
\q2 kendo Efraim e wuoda makayo.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 “Winjuru wach Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 yaye ogendini,
\q1 kendo landeuru e kuonde maboyo manie dho nembe:
\q2 ‘Ngʼama nokeyo jo-Israel nochokgi,
\q2 kendo enorit rombe kaka jakwath.’
\q1 
\v 11 Nimar Jehova Nyasaye nokony Jakobo
\q2 e lwet wasike,
\q2 kendo enoresgi e lwet jogo matek moloyogi.
\q1 
\v 12 Ginibi kendo ginikogi gi ilo
\q1 e kuonde motingʼore gi malo mag Sayun;
\q2 ginibed gi ilo kuom chiwo mabup mar Jehova Nyasaye,
\q1 ma gin cham, divai manyien kod mo,
\q2 nyithi rombe kod dhok.
\q1 Ginichal gi puodho moole pi maber,
\q2 kendo ok ginibed gi kuyo kendo.
\q1 
\v 13 Eka jotich ma nyiri nomiel
\q1 kendo bed mamor,
\q2 yawuowi matindo kod joma oti machalre.
\q1 Analok ywakgi obed mor;
\q2 anahogi kendo anamigi ilo kar kuyo.
\q1 
\v 14 Anami jodolo gik mathoth mongundho,
\q2 kendo joga nopongʼ,
\q2 gi chiwo mara mabup,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\p 
\v 15 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q2 “Dwol winjore Rama, ka goyo nduru,
\q1 kendo ywak malich,
\q2 Rael ywago nyithinde kendo odagi ni ok nyal hoye,
\q2 nikech gisetho.”
\p 
\v 16 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Lingʼ iwe ywak kendo ywe pi wangʼi,
\q2 nimar nochuli kuom tichni.
\q2 Giniduogi ka gia e piny wasigu.” Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\q1 
\v 17 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Omiyo nitiere geno kuom ndaloni mabiro.
\q2 Nyithindu nodwogi e pinygi giwegi.
\b
\q1 
\v 18 “Adiera asewinjo ywak Efraim:
\q2 Ne imiya kum ka nyaroya ma lelo,
\q2 kendo osekuma.
\q1 Duoga, kendo anaduogi,
\q2 nikech in Jehova Nyasaye Nyasacha.
\q1 
\v 19 Bangʼ kane asebaro, ne akwayo weruok;
\q1 bangʼ kane wach osedonjona, ne agoyo agoga.
\q2 Wiya nokuot kendo ne awinjo lit,
\q2 nikech ne atingʼo wichkuot mar bedona rawera.
\q1 
\v 20 Donge Efraim en wuoda makende,
\q2 nyathi ma amor godo?
\q1 Kata obedo ni awuoyoga kuome marach,
\q2 to pod apare. Emomiyo chunya ywage,”
\q2 an-gi kech kuome, Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 21 “Keturu ranyisi mag yore;
\q2 keturu gik matayo ji.
\q1 Paruru yore moriere, yorno miluwo.
\q2 Duogi, yaye Israel ma nyako ngili, duogi e dalau.
\q1 
\v 22 Nyaka karangʼo ma ibiro bayo,
\q2 yaye nyako maonge adiera?
\q1 Jehova Nyasaye enochwe gima nyien e piny,
\q2 dhako nokwak dichwo.”
\p 
\v 23 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: “Kagologi gia e twech, joma ni e piny Juda kod dalagi noti gi wechegi kendo ni: ‘Jehova Nyasaye ogwedhu, yaye kar dak maler, yaye got mowal.’
\v 24 Ji nodag kaachiel e kanyakla ei Juda kod miechgi duto, jopur kod jogo mawuotho ka gi kacha gi jambgi.
\v 25 Anami joma ool teko kendo joma chunygi onyosore anajiw.”
\p 
\v 26 Kuom mani ne achiewo kendo ne angʼiyo alworana. To nindo mara nobedona mamit.
\p 
\v 27 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Ndalo biro ma anapidhe od Israel kod od Juda gi koth ji kod mar le.
\v 28 Mana kaka ne angʼiyogi mondo apudhgi kendo kethogi, mondo awitgi oko ka atiekogi kendo kelonegi chandruok, anaritgi mondo agergi kendo pidhogi,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\v 29 “E ndalono ji ok nochak owach kendo niya,
\q1 “ ‘Wuone osechamo olembe ma wach-wach,
\q2 to leke nyithindo ema tho.’
\m 
\v 30 Makmana, ngʼato ka ngʼato notho nikech richone owuon; ngʼato angʼata mochano olemo ma wach-wach, lake owuon ema notho.”
\q1 
\v 31 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Kinde biro ma anatim
\q2 singruok manyien gi dhood jo-Israel kod dhood jo-Juda.
\q1 
\v 32 Singruokno ok nochal gi mano
\q2 mane atimo gi kweregi,
\q1 kane amako lwetgi
\q2 mi atelonegi kagologi e piny Misri,
\q1 nikech negiketho singruokna,
\q2 kata obedo nine an chworgi,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 33 “Ma e singruok ma anatim
\q2 gi dhood jo-Israel bangʼ ndalogo,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 “Abiro keto chikena e pachgi
\q2 kendo ndikogi e chunygi.
\q1 Anabed Nyasachgi
\q2 kendo ginibed joga.
\q1 
\v 34 Koro ngʼato ok nochak opuonj jabathe,
\q2 kata nyawadgi kowacho ni,
\q1 ‘Ngʼe Jehova Nyasaye,’ nikech giduto giningʼeya,
\q2 kochakore ngʼat matinie moloyo nyaka ngʼat maduongʼie moloyo,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 “Nimar anawenegi timbegi maricho
\q2 kendo ok anachak apar richogi kendo.”
\p 
\v 35 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho,
\q1 ngʼatno mayiero chiengʼ
\q2 mondo orieny godiechiengʼ,
\q1 machiko dwe gi sulwe
\q2 mondo orieny gotieno,
\q1 mamiyo apaka mag nam
\q2 ruto, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego e nyinge:
\q1 
\v 36 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Mana ka chikegi olal e wangʼa,
\q2 e kaka nyikwa Israel nowe bedo oganda e nyima.”
\p 
\v 37 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Kane ni polo malo inyalo pim
\q2 kendo mise mar piny inyalo many,
\q1 eka anakwed nyikwa Israel
\q2 nikech gigo duto magisetimo,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\p 
\v 38 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Kinde biro, ma dala maduongʼ ibiro gerona kendo, kochakore Kar Ngʼicho Motingʼore gi Malo mar Hananel nyaka e Dhoranga Kona.
\v 39 Tond pimo norie kochakore kanyo tir nyaka e got matin mar Gareb bangʼe ogomo kochiko Goa.
\v 40 Holono duto mopongʼ gi ringre joma otho kendo kama ipuke buru, kod kuonde duto mokuny duto, nodhi e Holo mar Kidron man yo wuok chiengʼ mochopo nyaka e kona ma Dhoranga Faras, nobed maler ne Jehova Nyasaye. Dala maduongʼni ok nomuki kata kethi.”
\c 32
\s1 Jeremia ongʼiewo puodho
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mane obirone Jeremia koa kuom Jehova Nyasaye e higa mar apar mar Zedekia ruodh Juda, ma ne en higa mar apar gaboro mar Nebukadneza.
\v 2 Jolwenj ruodh Babulon ne monjo Jerusalem, kendo Jeremia janabi ne otwe e agola moriti e kar dak mar ruodh Juda.
\p 
\v 3 Koro Zedekia ruodh Juda nokete e twech kanyo, kawacho niya, “Angʼo momiyo ikoro wach kamano? Ka iwacho ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye owacho: Achiegni chiwo dala maduongʼni ne ruodh Babulon, kendo enoloye.
\v 4 Zedekia ruodh Juda ok notony e lwet jo-Babulon to enochiwe ne ruodh Babulon, kendo enowuo kode wangʼ gi wangʼ mi enonene gi wengene owuon.
\v 5 Noter Zedekia Babulon, kama enosikie nyaka atimne gima adwaro, Jehova Nyasaye owacho. Ka ukedo gi jo-Babulon, to ok unulogi.’ ”
\p 
\v 6 Jeremia nowacho niya, “Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirona:
\v 7 Hanamel wuod Shalum ma wuod owadgi wuonu nobi iri kendo nowach ni, ‘Ngʼiew lopa man Anathoth, nikech kaka watna machiegni koda en ratiro mari kendo tiji mondo ingʼiewe.’
\p 
\v 8 “Eka, mana kaka Jehova Nyasaye nosewacho, omera Hanamel nobiro ira e agola mar jarito kendo owacho ni, ‘Ngʼiew puotha man Anathoth kama Benjamin orito. Nikech en ratiro mari mondo ingʼiewe kendo ikawe, ngʼiewe ne in owuon.’
\p “Ne angʼeyo ni ma ne en wach Jehova Nyasaye;
\v 9 omiyo ne angʼiewo puodho man Anathoth kuom wuod owadgi wuonwa Hanamel kendo apimone shekel apar gabiriyo mar fedha.
\v 10 Ne aketo seyi kendo agoyo amuri, ka joneno obedo, kendo apimo fedha e ratil.
\v 11 Ne akawo barup ngʼiepo, mano mogoye amuri momwon motingʼo singruok kod chike mag ngʼiewo lowo, to gi mano ma ok omuon
\v 12 kendo ne achiwo baruwani ne Baruk wuod Neria, wuod Maseya, e nyim omera Hanamel kod joneno mane ogo seyi e barup winjruok kod jo-Yahudi mane obet e agola mar jarito.
\p 
\v 13 “E nyimgi ne amiyo Baruk puonjgi:
\v 14 ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Kaw barupegi, mago momwon kod ma ok omuon, kendo iketgi e agulu mar lowo mondo omi gibed amingʼa.
\v 15 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Udi, puothe kod puothe mzabibu bende ibiro chak ngʼiew e pinyni.’
\p 
\v 16 “Bangʼ kane asechiwo barup ngʼiepo ne Baruk wuod Neria, ne alamo Jehova Nyasaye kama:
\pm 
\v 17 “Yaye, Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto, isechweyo polo gi piny kuom tekoni maduongʼ kod badi malach. Onge gima tekni.
\v 18 Inyiso herani ne ji alufu to ikelo kum mar wuone ni nyithindgi. Yaye Nyasaye maduongʼ kendo maratego, ma nyinge en Jehova Nyasaye Maratego,
\v 19 chenro magi dongo kendo timbegi lich. Wengeni oyawore ne yore duto mag ji; imiyo ngʼato mich kaluwore gi kite, kendo mowinjore gi timbene.
\v 20 Ne itimo ranyisi kod honni e piny Misri kendo isiko kodgi nyaka kawuono, ei Israel kendo e dier ji duto, kendo pod in ngʼat marahuma nyaka chil kawuono.
\v 21 Ne igolo jogi Israel oa Misri gi ranyisi kod honni, gi lweti maratego kod badi moyarore kod bwok malich.
\v 22 Ne imiyogi pinyni mane isesingone kweregi, piny mopongʼ gi chak kod mor kich.
\v 23 Negibiro kendo gikawo pinyno, to ne ok gilwori kata luwo chikeni; ne ok gitimo gik mane ichikogi mondo gitim. Omiyo ne ikelo kuomgi masichegi duto.
\pm 
\v 24 “Ne kaka oger pidhe madongo but dala maduongʼ mondo gimonje kendo gikawe. Nikech ligangla, kech kod masiche, dala maduongʼ nochiwne jo-Babulon ma monje. Gima ne iwacho osetimore kaka koro inene.
\v 25 To kata obedo ni dala maduongʼ enochiw ne jo-Babulon, in, yaye Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto, wachona ni, ‘Ngʼiew puodhoni gi fedha kendo ngʼiepone mondo obed gi joneno.’ ”
\p 
\v 26 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia:
\v 27 “An Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach ogendini duto. Bende nitiere gima tekna?
\v 28 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Achiegni chiwo dala maduongʼni ne jo-Babulon kendo ne Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon, ma biro monje kendo kawe.
\v 29 Jo-Babulon mamonjo dala maduongʼni nodonji kendo ginimok kuome mach; giniwangʼe pep, kaachiel gi udi kamane ji owangʼoe iya kuom wangʼo ubani ewi tedni ne Baal kendo kuom chiwo misango miolo piny ne nyiseche manono.
\p 
\v 30 “Jo-Israel gi jo-Juda pok otimo gimoro makmana timbe mamono e nyim wangʼa chakre tin-gi; adiera, jo-Israel pok otimo gimoro makmana chwanya gi gik ma lwetgi oloso, Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\v 31 Kochakore odiechiengʼ mane ogere nyaka sani, dala maduongʼni osemedo wangʼo iya kendo miya mirima ma chuna ni nyaka agole e nyim wangʼa.
\v 32 Jo-Israel gi jo-Juda osechwanya gi timbegi duto mamono magisetimo, gin ruodhi mag-gi kod jotelo, jodolo kod jonabi mag-gi, joma chwo mag Juda kod Jerusalem.
\v 33 Negilokona ngʼegi ma ok wengegi; kata obedo ni apuonjogi kendo amedo puonjogi, ne ok ginyal chiko itgi kata luwo puonjna.
\v 34 Negiketo nyisechegi manono e ot ma Nyinga nitiere kendo ginjawe.
\v 35 Negigero kuonde motingʼore gi malo ne Baal e Holo mar Ben Hinom mondo gitim misango gi yawuotgi kod nyigi ne Molek, kata kamano ne ok amiyogi chik mar timo kamano, kata mano ne onge e pacha niginyalo timo gima mono kamano kendo gimi Juda tim richo.
\p 
\v 36 “Iwuoyo kuom dala maduongʼni ni, ‘Gi ligangla, kech kod masiche enochiwe ne ruodh Babulon.’ To ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho:
\v 37 Adiera anachokgi duto gia e pinje duto kamane ariembogie gi ich wangʼ kod mirimba mager; anadwog-gi kae kendo awegi gidag gi kwe.
\v 38 Ginibed joga, kendo anabed Nyasachgi.
\v 39 Anami gibed gi chuny achiel kod tim achiel, mondo omi giluora manokel negiber kod nyithindgi manobi bangʼ-gi.
\v 40 Analos singruok manyaka chiengʼ kodgi: Ok anawe timonegi maber, kendo anamigi giluora, mondo omi kik gilokre giweya.
\v 41 Anabed gi mor kuom timonegi maber kendo adiera anaketgi e pinyni gi chunya duto kod parona duto.
\p 
\v 42 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Kaka asekelo masiche malich kama ne jogi, omiyo koro anamigi mwandu mane asingonegi.
\v 43 Ka puothe mangʼeny osengʼiew e pinyni ma uwacho ni, ‘En kama ninono, maonge ji kata le, nimar osechiwe ne jo-Babulon.’
\v 44 Puothe nongʼiew gi fedha, kendo barupe lowo nogoye sei kendo nogosingo kendo nobedgi joneno e gwengʼ Benjamin, e mier molworo Jerusalem, e mier mag Juda kendo e mier manie piny mantiere got matin, mar tiend gode ma yo podho chiengʼ kendo e Negev, nikech anadwog-gi ka gia e twech, Jehova Nyasaye wacho.”
\c 33
\s1 Singo mar duogo
\p 
\v 1 Kane pod Jeremia oketi e agola kamane irite, wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirone mar ariyo ni:
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho, en ema nochweyo piny, Jehova Nyasaye mane olose kendo oketo mise mare, Jehova Nyasaye e nyinge:
\v 3 ‘Bi ira, kendo anaduoki, kendo ananyisi gik madongo ma ok ingʼeyo.’
\v 4 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho kuom ute manie dala maduongʼni kod kuonde dak mar ruodh Juda ma osemuki mondo tigo kaka pidhe kod ligangla
\v 5 kuom kedo gi jo-Babulon: ‘Ginipongʼ-gi gi ringre joma otho mabiro nego gi ich wangʼ mara kod mirimba. Anapand wangʼa ne dala maduongʼni nikech timbegi duto mamono.
\p 
\v 6 “ ‘Kata kamano, anamigi ngima kendo chang; anachang joga kendo anami gibed gi mor kuom kwe mathoth kod rit mogundho.
\v 7 Anaduog Juda kod Israel koa e twech kendo analosgi gibed kaka ne gin chon.
\v 8 Anapwodhgi kuom richo magisetimona kendo anawenegi richogi duto mag ngʼanyona.
\v 9 Eka dala maduongʼni nomi abed gihuma, ilo, pak kod luor e nyim ogendini duto manie piny mawinjo gik moko duto mabeyo masetimone; kendo ginibed gi luoro mi ginitetni kuom gweth mogundho kod kwe masechiwone.’ 
\p 
\v 10 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Uwuoyo kuom dala maduongʼni niya, “Osedongʼ nono chuth, maonge ji kata jamni modakie.” Kata obedo ni mier mag Juda kod yore mag Jerusalem odongʼ nono kamano, maonge ji kata jamni modakie, to ubiro chako winjo,
\v 11 mor gi ilo kuondego, dwond miaha kod wuon kisera, kod dwond jogo makelo chiwo mar goyo erokamano ne od Jehova Nyasaye. Negiwacho niya,
\q1 “ ‘ “Goneuru Jehova Nyasaye Maratego erokamano,
\q2 nimar Jehova Nyasaye ber;
\q2 herane osiko nyaka chiengʼ.”
\m Nimar anaduog gweth ne piny mane gin-go chon,’ Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\p 
\v 12 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho: ‘Ka eri, mamono kendo maonge ji kata le, tiende ni e dalane duto nobedi kar kwath ma jokwath kwayoe rombegi.
\v 13 E dala manie piny gode, mago mantie e tie gode man yo podho chiengʼ kod mago man Negev, mantiere e gwenge mag Benjamin, e mier molworo Jerusalem kod dala mag Juda, rombe nokal kendo e lwet ngʼatno ma kwanogi,’ Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\p 
\v 14 “ ‘Ndalo biro ma abiro chopo singruokna mar ngʼwono mane aloso gi od Israel kod gi od Juda,’ Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 15 “ ‘E ndalogo kendo e kindeno
\q2 anami Bad Yath makare owuog e koth Daudi;
\q2 enotim gima ratiro kendo nikare e piny.
\q1 
\v 16 E ndalogo Juda noresi
\q2 kendo Jerusalem nodag gi kwe.
\q1 Ma e nying ma ibiro luongego:
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye mamiyo wabedo jo-ratiro.’
\m 
\v 17 Nimar ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Daudi ok nobed maonge gi ngʼato manobedi e kom duongʼ mar od Israel,
\v 18 kata jodolo, ma jo-Lawi, bende ok nobed maonge gi ngʼato machungʼ e nyima seche duto mar chiwo misengini miwangʼo pep, ka giwangʼo misengini mag cham kendo chiwo misengini.’ ”
\p 
\v 19 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia:
\v 20 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Ka inyalo ketho singruokna modiechiengʼ kod singruokna motieno, mondo omi odiechiengʼ kod otieno kik bi e sechegi mowinjore,
\v 21 bangʼe singruokna gi Daudi jatichna kod singruokna gi jo-Lawi ma gin jodolo ma yalo e nyima inyalo kethi to Daudi ok nobed gi nyakware manobed gi loch e kom duongʼ mare.
\v 22 Anami nyikwa Daudi jatichna kod jo-Lawi ma yalo e nyima bed mangʼeny mokalo akwana ka sulwe manie kor polo kendo ma ok nyal pim ka kwoyo manie dho nam.’ ”
\p 
\v 23 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia:
\v 24 “Bende isefwenyo ni jogi wachoni ni, ‘Jehova Nyasaye osekwedo dhoudi ariyo mane oyiero’? Omiyo gijaro joga kendo ok gikawo joga ka oganda achiel.
\v 25 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Ka dipo ni pod ok aketo singruokna godiechiengʼ gi otieno kod chike mogurore mar polo kod piny,
\v 26 eka anakwed nyikwa Jakobo kod Daudi jatichna kendo ok anayier achiel kuom yawuote mondo obed jatelo ewi nyikwa Ibrahim, Isaka kod Jakobo. Nimar anaduognegi mwandugi mi anangʼwon-negi.’ ”
\c 34
\s1 Osiem Zedekia
\p 
\v 1 Ka Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon kod jolweny mage duto gi pinjeruodhi duto gi ji duto mane ni e gwengʼ mane orito ne kedo gi Jerusalem kod dala mane olwore duto, wachni nobiro ne Jeremia koa ir Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho: Dhi ir Zedekia ruodh Juda kendo inyise kama, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Achiegni chiwo dala maduongʼni ne ruodh Babulon, kendo enowangʼe pep.
\v 3 Ok initony ngangʼ e wachni to adiera enomaki kendo nochiwi ne en. Inine ruodh Babulon gi wengeni iwuon, kendo enowuo kodi wangʼ gi wangʼ kendo inidhi Babulon.
\p 
\v 4 “ ‘Kata kamano winj singruok mar Jehova Nyasaye, yaye Zedekia ruodh Juda. Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuomi: Ok enonegi gi ligangla;
\v 5 initho gi kwe. Kaka ji noloso mach mar liel mar miyo wuonu luor; ruodhi machon mane otelo nyimi, mondo omi gilos mach mar miyi luor kendo mar ywak, “Aa, yaye jatelo!” An awuon aketo singoni, Jehova Nyasaye owacho.’ ”
\p 
\v 6 Eka Jeremia janabi nonyiso Zedekia ruodh Juda gigo duto e Jerusalem,
\v 7 sa mane jolweny mar ruodh Babulon ne kedo gi Jerusalem kod mier madongo mamoko mag Juda mane pod odongʼ, ma gin Lakish kod Azeka. Magi kende e mier madongo mochiel motegno gohinga mane odongʼ e Juda.
\s1 Wasumbini owe thuolo
\p 
\v 8 Wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia bangʼ ka Zedekia noloso winjruok gi ji duto man Jerusalem mondo oland ni wasumbini owe thuolo.
\v 9 Ngʼato ka ngʼato ne onego we misumbane ma ja-Hibrania, madichwo kod ma dhako; onge ngʼama ne dongʼ gi ja-Yahudi wadgi e twech.
\v 10 Omiyo jotelo duto kod ji mane odonjo e winjruokni noyie ni giniwe thuolo wasumbini mag-gi machwo kod mamon kendo ok ginibed e twech kendo. Ne giyie, kendo ne giwegi thuolo.
\v 11 To bangʼe negiloko pachgi mi gikawo kendo wasumbinigi mane giseweyo thuolo mi giketogi gibedo wasumbini kendo.
\p 
\v 12 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia kama:
\v 13 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, wacho: Ne aketo winjruok gi kwereu mane agologi gia Misri, e piny mar bedo misumba. Ne awacho ni,
\v 14 ‘E higa mar abiriyo ka higa mar abiriyo ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomu nyaka we ja-Hibrania wadgi thuolo ma osebedo katiyone. Bangʼ ka osetiyone kuom higni auchiel, nyaka iweye thuolo.’ Wuoneu, kata kamano, ne ok owinja kata luoro chikna.
\v 15 Kinde mosekadho machiegni, ne ikwayo weruok kendo ne itimo gima nikare e nyim wangʼa: Un duto ne uyie weyo oweteu thuolo. Bende ne utimo singruok e nyima e ot motingʼo Nyinga.
\v 16 To koro uselokoru kendo usedwanyo nyinga; uduto usekawo wasumbini machwo kod mamon mane useweyo thuolo mondo gidhi kama gidwaro. Usechunogi mondo gibed wasumbini magu kendo.
\p 
\v 17 “Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Pod ok uluora; pod ok uyie weyo oweteu thuolo. Omiyo koro awacho mondo owenu thuolo mondo onegu gi ligangla, masiche kod kech. Anami ogendini manie piny duto bedo gibuok ka ginenou.
\v 18 Chwo duto ma oseketho winjruokna kendo pod ok ochopo winjruok mane giloso e nyima, nakawgi ka nyaroya mane gingʼado nyadiriyo kendo giwuotho e kind lemogo.
\v 19 Jotend Juda gi Jerusalem, jotelo mag agola, jodolo kod ji duto mag pinyni mane owuotho e kind lemo ariyogo,
\v 20 anachiwgi ne wasikgi madwaro ngimagi. Ringregi motho nobed chiemb winy mafuyo e kor polo kod le manie piny.
\p 
\v 21 “Anachiw Zedekia ruodh Juda kod jotende ne wasike madwaro ngimagi, ne jolwenj ruodh Babulon, mosengʼanyo oa kuomu.
\v 22 Anachiw chik, Jehova Nyasaye wacho, kendo anadwog-gi e dala maduongʼni. Giniked kode, ginikawe kendo giwangʼe pep. Kendo anaketh dala mag Juda mondo kik ngʼato angʼata dag kanyo.”
\c 35
\s1 Joka Rekab
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mane obirone Jeremia koa ir Jehova Nyasaye e kinde loch Jehoyakim wuod Josia ma ruodh Juda:
\v 2 “Dhiyo ir anywola mar Rekab kendo igwelgi mondo gibi e achiel kuom agola mar od Jehova Nyasaye kendo imigi divai gimadhi.”
\p 
\v 3 Omiyo ne adhi mondo aom Jazania wuod Jeremia, ma wuod Habazinia gi owetene kod yawuote duto, anywola duto mag joka Rekab.
\v 4 Ne akelogi e od Jehova Nyasaye, e agola mar yawuot Hanan wuod Igdalia ngʼat Nyasaye. Ne entiere machiegni gi agola mar jotelo, mane okalo mano mar Maseya wuod Shalum ma jarit dhood hekalu.
\v 5 Eka ne apango bakunde mopongʼ gi divai kod kikombe moko e nyim chwo mag anywola mag Rekab kendo awachonegi niya, “Madhuru divai.”
\p 
\v 6 To negidwoko niya, “Ok wamadh divai, nikech kwarwa Jehonadab wuod Rekab nomiyowa chikni: ‘Un kata nyikwau ok onego madh divai.
\v 7 Bende kik uger udi, kata komo kodhi kata pidho mzabibu; gigi ok onego ubed godo, to nyaka udag e hembe. Eka unudag kinde marabora e piny kama unie jokwath.’
\v 8 Waserito gik moko duto mane kwarwa Jehonadab wuod Rekab ochikowa. Wan kod mondewa kata yawuotwa gi nyiwa pod ok omadho divai,
\v 9 kata gero udi mondo wadagie kata bedo gi puothe mzabibu, kod puothe mag cham.
\v 10 Wasedak e hembe kendo waserito gimoro amora ma kwarwa Jehonadab nochikowa.
\v 11 To Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon nomonjo pinyni, ne wawacho ni, ‘Biuru, nyaka wadhi Jerusalem wapondne jolweny mag Babulon kod mag jo-Aram kapok gimakowa.’ Omiyo ne wadongʼ Jerusalem.”
\p 
\v 12 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia, kawacho niya:
\v 13 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Dhiyo kendo inyis chwo ma Juda kod jo-Jerusalem ni, ‘Donge unyalo puonjoru kuom ma mi urit wechena?’ Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\v 14 ‘Jehonadab wuod Rekab nochiwo chik ne yawuote ni kik madh divai kendo chikni oseriti. Nyaka kawuononi pod ok gimadho divai, nikech girito chik kwargi. To asewuoyo kinde ka kinde, to kata kamano pod ok umiya luor.
\v 15 Pile ka pile ne aoro jotijena ma jonabi duto iru. Negiwacho niya, “Uduto nyaka uwe yoreu mamono kendo ulok timbeu; kik ulu bangʼ nyiseche manono mondo utinegi. Eka udag e piny ma asemiyou kod wuoneu.” To pod ok uchiko itu kata winja.
\v 16 Nyikwa Jehonadab wuod Rekab oserito chike mane kweregi omiyogi, to jogi pod ok omiya luor.’
\p 
\v 17 “Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Winjuru! Anakel kuom Juda kod ji duto modak Jerusalem kit masira moro amora mahero. Ne awuoyo kodgi, to ne ok giwinja; ne aluongogi, to ne ok gidwoka.’ ”
\p 
\v 18 Eka Jeremia nonyiso anywola mar joka Rekab niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Userito chik mar kwaru Jehonadab kendo useluwo puonjne duto kendo usetimo gik moko duto mane ochikou.’
\v 19 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Jehonadab wuod Rekab ok nobed maonge gi ngʼama tiyone.’ ”
\c 36
\s1 Jehoyakim owangʼo kitap Jeremia
\p 
\v 1 E higa mar angʼwen mar Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda, wachni nobiro ne Jeremia koa ir Jehova Nyasaye:
\v 2 “Kaw kitabu kendo indikie weche duto ma asewacho kuom Israel gi Juda kod ogendini mamoko duto kochakore kinde mane achako wuoyo kodi e ndalo loch Josia nyaka sani.
\v 3 Sa moro ka jo-Juda owinjo kuom masichegi ma achano mar kelo kuomgi, to giduto ginilokre giwe yoregi mamono; eka anawenegi timbegi mamono kod richo mag-gi.”
\p 
\v 4 Omiyo Jeremia noluongo Baruk wuod Neria, kendo Jeremia ne wachone to ondiko weche duto mane Jehova Nyasaye osewachone, Baruk nondikogi e kitabu.
\v 5 Eka Jeremia nokone Baruk niya, “An otama; ok anyal dhi e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 6 Omiyo in dhi e od Jehova Nyasaye chiengʼ lamo gi tweyo chiemo kendo isomne ji koa e kitabuni weche Jehova Nyasaye mane indiko sa mane awachoni to indiko. Somnegi ne jo-Juda duto ma biro koa e miechgi.
\v 7 Sa moro ginikel kwayogi e nyim Jehova Nyasaye, kendo giduto gilokre giwe yoregi mamono, nimar ich wangʼ gi mirima mikelone jogi gi Jehova Nyasaye duongʼ.”
\p 
\v 8 Baruk wuod Neria notimo gik moko duto mane Jeremia janabi onyise mondo otim; e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye nosomo weche Jehova Nyasaye koa e kitabu.
\v 9 E dwe mar ochiko e higa mar abich mar loch Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda, kinde mar tweyo e nyim Jehova Nyasaye nolandne ji duto manie Jerusalem kod jogo mane obiro koa e dala mag Juda.
\v 10 Kochakore e agola mar Gemaria wuod Shafan ma jagoro, mane nitiere e laru man malo e kar donjo mar Dhorangach Manyien mar hekalu, Baruk nosomone ji duto e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye weche Jeremia koa e kitabu.
\p 
\v 11 Ka Mikaya wuod Gemaria, ma wuod Shafan, nowinjo weche duto mag Jehova Nyasaye moa e kitabu,
\v 12 nodhi e agola mar jagoro mane ni e kar dak ruoth, kama ne jotelo nobetie: Elishama ma jagoro, Delaya wuod Shemaya, Elnathan wuod Akbor, Gemaria wuod Shafan, Zedekia wuod Hanania, kod jotelo mamoko duto.
\v 13 Bangʼ ka Mikaya ne osenyisogi gik moko duto mane osewinjo ka Baruk somo ne ji koa e kitabu,
\v 14 jotelogi duto nooro Jehudi wuod Nethania, ma wuod Shelemia, wuod Kushi, mondo owach ne Baruk niya, “Kel kitabu ma isesomone ji kendo ibi.” Omiyo Baruk wuod Neria nodhi irgi gi kitabuno e lwete.
\v 15 Negiwachone, “Bed piny, kiyie, kendo isomnwago.”
\p Omiyo Baruk nosomonegi.
\v 16 Kane gi winjo wechegi duto, ne gingʼiyore giwegi ka giluor kendo giwachone Baruk niya, “Nyaka wanyis wechegi duto ne ruoth.”
\v 17 Eka negipenjo Baruk niya, “Nyiswane, ere kaka ne indiko gigi duto? Jeremia ema nosomoni eka indikogi koso?”
\p 
\v 18 Baruk nodwoko niya, “En kamano, nowachona wechegi duto to nandikogi, kendo ne andiko gi wino e kitabu.”
\p 
\v 19 Eka jotelogo nonyiso Baruk, “In kaachiel gi Jeremia, dhiuru kendo upondi. Kik uwe ngʼato ngʼe kuma untie.”
\p 
\v 20 Bangʼ kane giseketo kitabu ei od Elishama jagoro, negidhi ir ruoth e laru kendo giwachone gimoro amora.
\v 21 Ruoth nooro Jehudi mondo okel kitabuno, kendo Jehudi nokele koa kode ei od Elishama jagoro kendo nosomene ruoth kod jotelo duto kochungʼ e bathe.
\v 22 Ne en dwe mar ochiko kendo ruoth nobet ei ot mar oyo mach e kinde mar chwiri.
\v 23 Ka Jehudi nosesomo laini adek kata angʼwen mar kitabuno, ruoth nongʼadogi gi pala mabith kendo owitogi e kar hoyo mach, nyaka kitabuno duto nowangʼ e mach.
\v 24 Ruoth gi jogo duto mane en godo mane owinjo wechegi ne ok obedo gi luoro moro, kata lepgi ne ok giyiecho.
\v 25 Kata obedo ni Elnathan, Delaya kod Gemaria nokwero ruoth mondo kik wangʼ kitabuno, to ne ok onyal winjogi.
\v 26 Makmana, ruoth nomiyo Jeramel, ma wuod ruoth, Seraya wuod Azriel gi Shelemia wuod Abdil chik, mondo omak Baruk jandiko kod Jeremia janabi. To Jehova Nyasaye nosepandogi.
\p 
\v 27 Bangʼ ka ruoth nosewangʼo kitabu mane otingʼo gik mane Baruk ondiko ka Jeremia somone, wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia:
\v 28 “Kaw kitabu machielo kendo indikie weche duto mane ni e kitabu mokwongo-cha, mane Jehoyakim ruodh Juda owangʼo.
\v 29 Bende nyis Jehoyakim ruodh Juda ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Ne iwangʼo kitabucha kendo iwacho niya, “Angʼo momiyo ne indiko kuome ni ruodh Babulon enobi kendo keth pinyni kendo ogol ji kaachiel gi le kuome?”
\v 30 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho kuom Jehoyakim ruodh Juda: Ok nobed gi ngʼama bedo e kom duongʼ Daudi; ringre nowit oko kendo nomo oko ne liet mar odiechiengʼ kendo ne thoo mar otieno.
\v 31 Anakume gi nyithinde kod jogo marite nikech timbegi maricho; anakel kuomgi kod jogo modak Jerusalem gi jo-Juda kit masira moro amora mane asechanonegi, nikech gitamore winja.’ ”
\p 
\v 32 Omiyo Jeremia nokawo kitabu machielo kendo omiye Baruk wuod Neria jandik muma, kendo kaka Jeremia ne ohulo, Baruk nondiko e kitabuno weche duto mar kitabu mane Jehoyakim ruodh Juda nosewangʼo e mach kendo weche mangʼeny machalre nomed kuomgi.
\c 37
\s1 Jeremia ni e twech
\p 
\v 1 Zedekia wuod Josia noket ruodh juda gi Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon; nobedo gi loch kar Jehoyakin wuod Jehoyakim.
\v 2 En kata jorit mage kata jopinyno ne ok owinjo weche mane Jehova Nyasaye owacho kokalo kuom janabi Jeremia.
\p 
\v 3 Ruoth Zedekia, kata kamano, nooro Jehukal wuod Shelemia gi jadolo Zefania wuod Maseya ir janabi Jeremia gi wachni: “Kiyie to lamnwa Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa.”
\p 
\v 4 Koro Jeremia ne nigi thuolo mondo obi kendo odhi e dier ji, nimar ne pod ok okete e od twech.
\v 5 Jolwenj Farao ne osewuok oa Misri, kendo ka jo-Babulon mane gero pidhe kolworo Jerusalem nowinjo wach mar biro margi, ne gidar gia Jerusalem.
\p 
\v 6 Eka wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne janabi Jeremia niya:
\v 7 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Nyis ruodh Juda, mane oorou mondo unona ni, ‘Jolwenj Farao, mosewuok mondo okonyu, biro dok e pinygi giwegi, Misri.
\v 8 Eka jo-Babulon nodwogi kendo ginimonj dala maduongʼni; ginikawe kendo wangʼe pep.’
\p 
\v 9 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Kik uwuondru uwegi, kuparo ni, ‘Jo-Babulon gadiera biro weyowa.’ Ok giniweu ngangʼ!
\v 10 Kata ka bed ni ne unyalo loyo jolwenj Babulon duto ma biro monjou kendo chwo mohiny kende ema odongʼ e hembegi, giniwuogi oko kendo giwangʼ dala maduongʼni.”
\p 
\v 11 Bangʼ ka jolwenj Babulon nose aa Jerusalem nikech jolwenj Farao,
\v 12 Jeremia nochako wuok e dala maduongʼ mondo odhi e gwengʼ Benjamin mondo oyud pokne e dier joma ni kanyo.
\v 13 To kane ochopo e Dhoranga Benjamin, jatend jorito, ma nyinge en Irija wuod Shelemia, ma wuod Hanania, nomake kendo owacho niya, “Nenore ni iweyowa idokne jo-Babulon!”
\p 
\v 14 “Mano ok adiera!” Jeremia nowachone. “Ok aringi adogne jo-Babulon.” To Irija ne ok nyal winje; kuom mano, nomako Jeremia kendo okele ir jotelo.
\v 15 Igi nowangʼ gi Jeremia kendo negikete ogoye kendo otweye e od Jonathan ma jagoro, mane giloso obedo od twech.
\p 
\v 16 Jeremia noketi e od twech manie bwo ot, kama ne obetie kuom kinde marabora.
\v 17 Eka Ruoth Zedekia nooro mondo okele e kar dak ruoth, kama ne openje akwala niya, “Bende nitiere wach moa kuom Jehova Nyasaye?”
\p Jeremia nodwoko ni, “Nitiere, nikech nochiwi ni ruodh Babulon.”
\p 
\v 18 Eka Jeremia nowachone Ruoth Zedekia niya, “En ketho mane ma asetimoni kata ne jotendi kata ne jogi, momiyo iketa e od twech?
\v 19 To koro ere jonabi mane okoroni ni, ‘Ruodh jo-Babulon ok nomonj pinyu kata in?’
\v 20 To koro, ruodha, yie iwinja. We akel kwayona e nyimi: Kik idwoka e od Jonathan ma jagoro, ka ok kamano to abiro tho kanyo.”
\p 
\v 21 Eka Ruoth Zedekia nochiwo chik mondo Jeremia oket e laru jarito kendo miye makati koa e yore mag jolos makati odiechiengʼ ka odiechiengʼ, nyaka makati duto man e dala maduongʼno norumo.
\c 38
\s1 Odir Jeremia ei bur
\p 
\v 1 Shefatia wuod Matan, Gedalia wuod Pashur, Jehukal wuod Shelemia, kod Pashur wuod Malkija nowinjo gima Jeremia ne nyiso ji duto sa mane owacho ni,
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Ngʼato angʼata modak e dala maduongʼni noneg gi ligangla, kech kata masira, to ngʼato angʼata manodhi ir jo-Babulon nobed mangima. Notony gi ngimane; mi nobed mangima.’
\v 3 Kendo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Dala maduongʼni nyaka chiwne jolweny mar ruodh Babulon ma nokawe.’ ”
\p 
\v 4 Eka jotelo nowachone ruoth niya, “Ngʼatni onego negi. Onyoso chuny jolweny modongʼ e dala maduongʼ ni, kaachiel gi ji duto, gi gigo mowachonegi. Ngʼatni ok dwar dhi maber mar jogi to mana kethruokgi.”
\p 
\v 5 Ruoth Zedekia nowacho niya, “En e lwetu. Onge gima ruoth nyalo timo mondo okwed wachu.”
\p 
\v 6 Omiyo negikawo Jeremia ma giketo e bur mar Malkija, wuod ruoth, mane nitiere e laru mar jarito. Ne giloro Jeremia gi tonde ei burno; ne onge pi e iye, chwodho ema ne nitie, kendo Jeremia nonimo ei chwodho.
\p 
\v 7 To Ebed-Melek, ja-Kush, ma jatelo e kar dak ruoth, nowinjo nine giseketo Jeremia ei bur. Ka ruoth ne obet e Dhoranga Benjamin,
\v 8 Ebed-Melek nowuok oa e kar dak ruoth kendo owachone ni,
\v 9 “Jaduongʼ ma ruodha, jogi osetimo gima mono kuom gigo duto magisetimone janabi Jeremia. Giwite e bur, kama kech biro nege motho ka makati duto orumo e dala maduongʼ.”
\p 
\v 10 Eka ruoth nomiyo Ebed-Melek ja-Kush chik, “Kaw chwo piero adek koa kae kendo ugol janabi Jeremia e bur kapok otho.”
\p 
\v 11 Omiyo Ebed-Melek nokawo jogo kendo odhigo e agola manie bwo kar keno mar dala ruoth. Ne okawo lewni moyiech kod lewni moti kanyo kendo nolorogi piny gi tol ne Jeremia ei bur.
\v 12 Ebed-Melek ja-Kush nowacho ne Jeremia niya, “Ket lewni mokengoregi kod lewni moti e yuothi mondo kik tol ridhi.” Jeremia notimo kamano,
\v 13 mine giywaye gi tol ma gigole oko mar bur. Kendo Jeremia nodongʼ e laru mar jarito.
\s1 Zedekia openjo Jeremia kendo
\p 
\v 14 Eka Ruoth Zedekia nooro wach mondo okelne janabi Jeremia kendo nokelnego e kar donjo mar adek mar hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye. Ruoth nowachone niya, “Adhi penji gimoro. Kik ipanda wach.”
\p 
\v 15 Jeremia nowachone Zedekia niya, “Ka adwoki, donge ibiro nega? Kata ka anangʼadni rieko, bende iniwinja.”
\p 
\v 16 To Ruoth Zedekia nokwongʼore gi kwongʼruokni lingʼ-lingʼ ne Jeremia: “Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye mangima, mosemiyowa muya, ok ananegi kata chiwi ne jogo madwaro ngimani.”
\p 
\v 17 Eka Jeremia nowachone Zedekia niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Ka ichiwori ne jotelo mag ruodh Babulon, ngimani noweni kendo dala maduongʼni ok nowangʼ, in kod joodi unubed mangima.
\v 18 To ka ok ichiwori ne jotend ruodh Babulon, dala maduongʼni nomi jo-Babulon kendo giniwangʼe; un uwegi ok unutony e lwetgi.’ ”
\p 
\v 19 Ruoth Zedekia nowachone Jeremia niya, “Aluoro jo-Yahudi mosedhi ir jo-Babulon, nimar jo-Babulon nyalo chiwa e lwetgi mi gisanda.”
\p 
\v 20 Jeremia nodwoke niya, “Ok ginichiwi.” Luor Jehova Nyasaye kitimo gima anyisi. Eka inine maber, kendo ngimani noweni.
\v 21 To ka itamori chiwori, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye osefwenyona:
\v 22 Mon duto mane odongʼ kar dak mar ruodh Juda nokelne jotelo mar ruodh Babulon. Mon-go nowachni ni:
\q1 Osiepegi mane igenogo
\q2 nowuondi kendo noloyi.
\q1 Tiendegi oselingʼore e chwodho;
\q2 osiepegi oseweyi.
\p 
\v 23 “Mondeu duto kod nyithindu nokelne jo-Babulon. Un uwegi ok unutony e lwetgi to enomaku gi ruodh Babulon; kendo dala maduongʼni nowangʼ mapodhi.”
\p 
\v 24 Eka Zedekia nowachone Jeremia niya, “Kik iwe ngʼato ongʼe twak-wani, ka ok kamano to inyalo tho.
\v 25 Ka jotelo owinjo nine awuoyo kodi, kendo gibiro iri ma giwacho, ‘Nyiswa gima ne iwachone ruoth kendo gima ruoth nowachoni; kik ipandwa ka ok kamano to wabiro negi,’
\v 26 to nyisgi ni, ‘Ne asayo ruoth mondo kik oora adog e od Jonathan mondo atho kanyo.’ ”
\p 
\v 27 Jotelo duto nobiro ir Jeremia mi gipenje, kendo nonyisogi gik moko duto mane ruoth ochike mondo awachi. Omiyo onge gima negichako ginyise, nimar onge ngʼama nowinjo twakgi gi ruoth.
\p 
\v 28 Kendo Jeremia nodongʼ e laru mar jarito nyaka odiechiengʼ ma Jerusalem nokaw.
\s1 Jerusalem okaw
\p Ma e kaka Jerusalem ne okaw:
\c 39
\nb 
\v 1 E higa mar ochiko mar Zedekia ruodh Juda, e dwe mar apar, Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon nodhi gi jolweny mage duto momonjo Jerusalem kendo ne gigoyone agengʼa.
\v 2 To odiechiengʼ mar ochiko e dwe mar angʼwen e higa mar apar gachiel mar loch Zedekia, ohinga mar dala maduongʼno nomuki.
\v 3 Eka jotelo duto mag ruodh Babulon nobiro kendo obet e Dhorangach Madiere: Negal-Shareza ma ja-Samgar, Nebo-Sasekim jatelo maduongʼ, Negal-Shareza jatelo mamalo maduongʼ kod jotelo mamoko duto mag ruodh Babulon.
\v 4 Ka Zedekia ruodh Juda kod jolweny duto nonenogi, negiringo giwuok e dala maduongʼno gotieno ka gikalo e rangach man e kind ohinga ariyo man but puoth ruoth, kendo ka gichomo Araba.
\p 
\v 5 To jolwenj Babulon nolawogi kendo ojuko Zedekia e pewe mag Jeriko. Negimake mi gitere Ribla e piny Hamath ir Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon, kama nongʼadone bura.
\v 6 E Ribla ruodh Babulon nonego yawuot Zedekia koneno bende nonego jo-Juda duto ma joka ruoth.
\v 7 Eka nogolo wenge Zedekia oko kendo notweye gi rateke mag mula mondo notere Babulon.
\p 
\v 8 Jo-Babulon nowangʼo kar dak ruoth kod ute ji kendo negimuko ohinga mag Jerusalem.
\v 9 Nebuzaradan ma jatend lweny mar piny nomako joma nodongʼ e dala maduongʼ moterogi e twech Babulon, kanyakla gi jogo mane osedhi ire, kod joma moko.
\v 10 To Nebuzaradan ma jatend lweny noweyo e piny Juda joma odhier, mane onge gi gimoro; kendo e ndalogo nomiyogi puothe mzabibu kod puothe mamoko.
\p 
\v 11 Koro Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon nosechiwo chike kuom Jeremia kokalo kuom Nebuzaradan ma jatend lweny mar piny kowacho ni:
\v 12 “Kawe kendo irite; kik ihinye to timne gimoro amora mokwayo.”
\v 13 Omiyo Nebuzaradan ma jatend lweny, Nebushazban ma jatelo maduongʼ, Negal-Shareza ma jatelo mamalo kod jotelo duto mag ruodh Babulon
\v 14 nooro wach mondo ogol Jeremia oa e laru mar jarito. Ne gitere ir Gedalia wuod Ahikam, ma wuod Shafan, mondo odwoke dalane. Omiyo nodongʼ e dier jogi owuon.
\p 
\v 15 Sa mane Jeremia nokan e laru mar jolweny, wach Jehova Nyasaye nobirone niya:
\v 16 “Dhiyo kendo inyis Ebed-Melek ja-Kush, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Achiegni timo gik mane awacho ni natim ne dala maduongʼni, ka akelo ne masiche to ok kwe. E kindeno notimgi ka ineno.
\v 17 Jehova Nyasaye wacho ni enoresi odiechiengʼno, ok nochiwi ne jogo miluoro.
\v 18 Enoresi; ok nonegi gi ligangla to initony gi ngimani, nikech igeno kuoma,’ ” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\c 40
\s1 Jeremia owe thuolo
\p 
\v 1 Wach nobiro ne Jeremia koa kuom Jehova Nyasaye bangʼ ka Nebuzaradan ma jatend lweny mar piny nosegonye Rama. Noyudo ka Jeremia otwe gi nyororo e dier joma nomak duto mane oa Jerusalem kod Juda mane oter e twech Babulon.
\v 2 Ka jatend lweny noyudo Jeremia, nowachone niya, “Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi nochiko masirani ne pinyni.”
\v 3 Kendo koro Jehova Nyasaye osemiyo otimore; osetimo kaka ne owacho ni obiro timo. Magi duto notimore nikech nutimo richo ne Jehova Nyasaye kendo ne ok gitimo dwaro mare.
\v 4 To kawuononi aweyi thuolo ka agonyo nyoroche manie ngʼut lweti. Dhi koda Babulon, ka ihero, kendo anariti; to ka ok idwar, to kik ibi. Ne, piny ngima ni e lweti; dhi kamoro amora midwaro.
\v 5 Kata kamano, ka Jeremia ne pod ok owuok, Nebuzaradan nomedo kawacho niya, “Dog ir Gedalia wuod Ahikam, ma wuod Shafan, ma ruodh Babulon oseyiero mondo orit mier mag Juda, kendo idag kode kaachiel gi ji, ka ok kamano to idhi kamoro amora mihero.”
\p Eka jatend lweny nomiye gik moko kod mich bangʼe noweye odhi.
\v 6 Omiyo Jeremia nodhi Mizpa ir Gedalia wuod Ahikam mi odak kode kaachiel gi ji mane odongʼ e pinyno.
\s1 Oneg Gedalia
\p 
\v 7 Ka jotend jolweny duto kod jogi mane pod ni e piny ma tambarare nowinjo ni ruodh Babulon noseyiero Gedalia wuod Ahikam kaka jatelo maduongʼ kendo okete jatelo mar chwo, mon kod nyithindo mane odhier moloyo e piny kendo mago mane ok oter e twech Babulon,
\v 8 negibiro ir Gedalia e dala miluongo ni Mizpa. Jogo ne gin Ishmael wuod Nethania, Johanan gi Jonathan ma yawuot Karea, Seraya wuod Tanhumeth, yawuot Efai ma ja-Netofath, kod Jazania wuod ja-Maakath, kod jogi.
\v 9 Gedalia wuod Ahikam, ma wuod Shafan, nokwongʼore kosingorenegi kaachiel gi jogo mane ni kodgi kawacho niya, “Kik uluor tiyone jo-Babulon. Daguru e pinyni kendo uti ne ruodh Babulon, to unudhi maber.
\v 10 An awuon anadag Mizpa mondo achungʼ karu e nyim jo-Babulon mabiro irwa, to un onego uka olembe, divai, olembe mag ndalo oro gi mo, kendo uketgi e agulniu mag keno, kendo udag e dala ma usekawo.”
\p 
\v 11 Ka jo-Yahudi duto man Moab, Amon, Edom kod pinje mamoko nowinjo ni ruodh Babulon noweyo joma notony ei Juda kendo noyiero Gedalia wuod Ahikam, ma wuod Shafan, kaka jatendgi,
\v 12 giduto negibiro e piny Juda, e Mizpa ir Gedalia, ka gia e pinje duto mane okegie. Kendo negikayo divai mathoth kod olembe mag ndalo oro.
\p 
\v 13 Johanan wuod Karea kod jotend lweny duto ma pod ne nitiere e piny ma tambarare nodhi Mizpa ir Gedalia
\v 14 kendo owachone niya, “Bende ingʼeyo ni Baalis ruodh jo-Amon oseoro Ishmael wuod Nethania mondo okaw ngimani?” To Gedalia wuod Ahikam ne ok oyie gi wachgino.
\p 
\v 15 Eka Johanan wuod Karea nowachone Gedalia malingʼ-lingʼ ka en Mizpa niya, “Weya adhi kendo aneg Ishmael wuod Nethania, to onge ngʼama nongʼe. Angʼo momiyo odwaro kawo ngimani kendo omi jo-Yahudi duto mochokore buti oke kendo jo-Juda motony olal nono?”
\p 
\v 16 To Gedalia wuod Ahikam nowachone Johanan wuod Karea niya, “Kik itim gima chalo kamano! Gima iwacho kuom Ishmael ok adiera.”
\c 41
\p 
\v 1 E dwe mar abiriyo Ishmael wuod Nethania, ma wuod Elishama, mane aa e anywola mar joka ruoth kendo ma bende ne achiel kuom jotend ruoth, nobiro Mizpa gi ji apar ir Gedalia wuod Ahikam. E kinde mane gichiemo kanyakla kanyo,
\v 2 Ishmael wuod Nethania kod ji apar mane ni kode nochungʼ malo kendo onego Gedalia wuod Ahikam, ma wuod Shafan, gi ligangla, ma ginego ngʼatno ma ruodh Babulon noyiero kaka jatelo e pinyno.
\v 3 Ishmael nonego bende jo-Yahudi duto mane nigi Gedalia Mizpa, kaachiel gi jolwenj Babulon mane ni kanyo.
\p 
\v 4 Kinyne ka Gedalia nosenegi, ka pod ngʼato angʼata ne ok ongʼeyo wachni,
\v 5 chwo piero aboro mane olielo tikgi mapoth, manoyiecho lepgi kendo mongʼado dendgi nobiro koa Shekem, Shilo kod Samaria, ka gikelo chiwo mar cham gi ubani e od Jehova Nyasaye.
\v 6 Ishmael wuod Nethania noa Mizpa mondo orom kodgi, ka oywak e sache mane odhi. Kane oromo kodgi, nowachonegi niya, “Biuru ir Gedalia wuod Ahikam.”
\v 7 Kane gidhi e dala maduongʼ, Ishmael wuod Nethania kod chwo mane ni kode nonegogi mi owitogi ei bur.
\v 8 To ji apar kuomgi nowachone Ishmael niya, “Kik inegwa! Wan gi ngano kod shairi gi mo, kod mor kich, mwapando e puothe.” Omiyo noweyogi kendo ne ok onegogi gi joma moko.
\v 9 Koro buche mane owitoe ringre chwo duto mane osenego kaachiel gi Gedalia ne en mano mane Ruoth Asa oloso kaka kar pondone kane okedo gi Baasha ruodh Israel. Ishmael wuod Nethania nopongʼe gi ringre joma otho.
\p 
\v 10 Ishmael nomako jogo mane odongʼ duto ei Mizpa mane gin nyi ruoth kaachiel gi jogo duto mane odongʼ kanyo, jogo mane Nebuzaradan jatend lweny mar piny noketo Gedalia wuod Ahikam mondo oriti. Ishmael wuod Nethania nomakogi kendo negichako ka gingʼado gidhi loka Amon.
\p 
\v 11 Ka Johanan wuod Karea kod jotend lweny duto mane ni kode nowinjo timbe njore duto mane Ishmael wuod Nethania nosetimo,
\v 12 negikawo jolweny mag-gi duto mi gidhi mondo giked gi Ishmael wuod Nethania. Ne gijuke but pi maduongʼ man Gibeon.
\v 13 Ka jogo mane nigi Ishmael omako noneno Johanan wuod Karea kod jotend lweny mane ni kode, negimor.
\v 14 Jogo duto mane Ishmael omako Mizpa nolokore modhi ir Johanan wuod Karea.
\v 15 To Ishmael wuod Nethania kod joge aboro notony oa ir Johanan mi giringo gidhi ir jo-Amon.
\s1 Dar dhi Misri
\p 
\v 16 Eka Johanan wuod Karea kod jotend lweny duto mane ni kode nokawo joma notony duto mane oa Mizpa, ma noreso e lwet Ishmael wuod Nethania bangʼ kane osenego Gedalia wuod Ahikam; mane gin jolweny, mon, nyithindo kod jodongo mane obirogo koa Gibeon.
\v 17 Kendo negidhi nyime, ma gichungʼ Geruth Kimham but Bethlehem ka gidhi Misri,
\v 18 mondo gipondne jo-Babulon. Ne giluorogi nikech Ishmael wuod Nethania nosenego Gedalia wuod Ahikam, mane ruodh Babulon oyiero kaka jatelo e pinyno.
\c 42
\p 
\v 1 Eka jotend lweny duto, kaachiel gi Johanan wuod Karea kod Jezania wuod Hoshaya, kod ji duto chakre matin nyaka maduongʼ nodhi ir
\v 2 janabi Jeremia kendo owachone niya, “Kiyie to iwinj kwayowa kendo ilamnwa Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi ne joma otonygi duto. Nimar kaka ineno sani, kata obedoni chon ne wangʼeny, to koro sani ji matin ema odongʼ.
\v 3 Lem mondo Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi onyiswa kuma wanyalo dhiyoe kendo gima wanyalo timo.”
\p 
\v 4 Janabi Jeremia nodwoko niya, “Asewinjou. Adier nyaka analamnu Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasacha kaka usekwayo; ananyisu gimoro amora ma Jehova Nyasaye owacho kendo onge gima anapandnu.”
\p 
\v 5 Eka negiwachone Jeremia, “Mad Jehova Nyasaye bed ja-adiera kendo janeno makare kuomwa ka dipo ni timbewa ok oluwore gi gimoro ma Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi ooroi godo irwa.
\v 6 Kowinjore kata ka ok owinjore, wanaluor Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa, ma waori ire, mondo omi obed maber kodwa, nimar wanaluor Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa.”
\p 
\v 7 Bangʼ ndalo apar wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia.
\v 8 Omiyo noluongo Johanan wuod Karea kod jotend lweny mane ni kode kod ji duto chakre matin nyaka maduongʼ.
\v 9 Nowachonegi niya, “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, Nyasach Israel, mane uora ire mondo aterne kwayou, wacho:
\v 10 ‘Ka idak e pinyni, anageru kendo ok anatieku; anapidhu to ok pudhou oko, nimar asebedo gi lit kuom masiche masekelo kuomu.
\v 11 Kik uluor ruodh Babulon, makoro uluoro. Kik uluore, Jehova Nyasaye wacho, nimar an kodu kendo anaresu ua e lwetene.
\v 12 Anatimnu ngʼwono mondo omi en bende ongʼwonnu kendo odwoku e pinyu.’
\p 
\v 13 “To ka uwacho, ‘Ok wanadagie pinyni,’ mamano mi ubed ma ok uluoro Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu,
\v 14 kendo ka uwacho ni, ‘Ooyo, wanadhi kendo wadag Misri, kama ok wana neye lweny kata winjo turumbete kata bedo gi kech mar makati,’
\v 15 to uwinj wach Jehova Nyasaye, yaye joma otony modongʼ mag Juda. Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Ka uramo ni nyaka udhi Misri kendo udhi udak kanyo,
\v 16 to ngʼeuru ni ligangla ma uluoro nomaku, kendo kech mabwogou noluu nyaka Misri, kendo kanyo ema unuthoe.
\v 17 Adiera, jogo duto moramo mondo odhi odag Misri noneg gi ligangla, kech kod masira maonge ngʼato angʼata ma notony e chandruok mabiro kelo kuomgi.’
\v 18 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: ‘Kaka ich wangʼ mara kod mirimba aseolo kuom jogo modak Jerusalem, e kaka mirimba ibiro olo kuomu ka udhi Misri. Inibed gir kwongʼ kendo mabwogo ji, gima ingʼadogo bura kendo gir ajara; ok unuchak une kaeni kendo.’
\p 
\v 19 “Yaye jo-Juda modongʼ, Jehova Nyasaye osenyisou ni, ‘Kik udhi Misri.’ Beduru gadiera kuom ma: Asiemou kawuono
\v 20 ni ne uketho ketho malich kane uora ir Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu kendo uwacho ni, ‘Lamnwa Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa; nyiswa gik moko duto mowacho kendo wanatim kamano.’
\v 21 Asewachonu kawuono, to pod ok uluoro Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachu kuom gigo duto mane oora mondo anyisu.
\v 22 Omiyo koro, beduru gadieri kuom ma: Nonegu gi ligangla, kech kod masira kuma udwaro dhiye mondo udagie.”
\c 43
\p 
\v 1 Ka Jeremia notieko nyiso ji weche duto mag Jehova Nyasaye Nyasachgi, ma gin gik moko duto ma Jehova Nyasaye ne oore mondo onyisgi,
\v 2 Azaria wuod Hoshaya gi Johanan wuod Karea kod chwo ma jo-jendeke duto nowachone Jeremia niya, “Iriambo! Jehova Nyasaye Nyasachwa pok oori mondo iwachnwa ni, ‘Kik udhi Misri mondo udag kuno.’
\v 3 To Baruk wuod Neria thuyi kodwa mondo ichiw-wa ne jo-Babulon, mondo ginegwa kata terowa e twech Babulon.”
\p 
\v 4 Omiyo Johanan wuod Karea kod jotend lweny duto kod ji duto ne ok oluwo chik Jehova Nyasaye mar dak e piny Juda.
\v 5 Kata kamano, Johanan wuod Karea kod jotend lweny duto notelo ne jo-Juda duto mane otony mi odwogo mondo odag e piny Juda koa e pinje duto mane okegie.
\v 6 Bende negitelone chwo duto, mon kod nyithindo gi nyi ruoth mane Nebuzaradan ma jatend lweny noseweyo gi Gedalia wuod Ahikam, ma wuod Shafan, kod Jeremia janabi kod Baruk wuod Neria.
\v 7 Omiyo negidhi Misri ka ok giluoro Jehova Nyasaye ma gichopo nyaka Tapanhes.
\p 
\v 8 E Tapanhes kuno wach Jehova Nyasaye nobiro ne Jeremia niya:
\v 9 “Kane jo-Yahudi ne pod rango, kaw kite moko madongo mondo iyik gi lowo e kind matafare mochan e dhoranga dala Farao man Tapanhes.
\v 10 Eka iwachnegi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Analuong jatichna Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon, kendo anaket kom duongʼne ewi kitegi maseiko kae; mi ogur hembe e wigi.
\v 11 Enobi kendo omonj Misri, konego jogo monego negi, komako jogo monego maki, kendo konego gi ligangla jogo monego negi gi ligangla.
\v 12 Obiro moko mach kuom hekalu mag nyiseche mag Misri; enowangʼ hekalu mag-gi kendo enoter nyisechigi e twech. Kaka jakwath tweyo lepe e nungone, e kaka notwe Misri kuome owuon kendo noa kanyo ma ok ohinyore.
\v 13 Enomuk sirni mowal milamo mag hekalu mar chiengʼ man Misri kendo enowangʼ hekalu mag nyiseche jo-Misri.’ ”
\c 44
\s1 Masiche miyudo nikech lamo nyiseche manono
\p 
\v 1 Wachni nobiro ne Jeremia kuom jo-Yahudi modak Misri Mamwalo man Migdol, Tapanhes gi Memfis kod Misri Mamalo:
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Ne ineno masira malich mane akelo kuom Jerusalem kod kuom dala duto mag Juda. Kawuono gidongʼ gunda kendo okethgi,
\v 3 nikech timbe maricho magisetimo. Negimiya mirima ma iya owangʼ kuom wangʼo ubani kendo lamo nyiseche manono ma gin kata un kata wuoneu ne ok ongʼeyo.
\v 4 Ne asiko ka aoro jotichna ma jonabi, mane giwacho ni, ‘Kik utim gima mononi ma ok ahero!’
\v 5 To ne ok gichiko itgi kata winja; ne ok gilokore gia e timbegi mamono kata weyo wangʼo ubani ne nyiseche manono.
\v 6 Emomiyo, mirimba mager nool oko; mine olandore kobebni e dala mag Juda kod yore mag Jerusalem kendo moketogi gibed gundini mokethore kaka gin kawuono.
\p 
\v 7 “Koro ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Angʼo momiyo ukelo masira malich kuomu ka uweyo chwo gi mon, rawere gi nyithindo mayom, makoro onge joma otony koa kuom jo-Juda?
\v 8 Angʼo momiyo uwangʼo iya gi gik ma lwetu oloso, uwangʼo ubani ne nyiseche manono ei Misri, kama osebiroe mondo udagie? Unutiekru kendu uwegi ka uloso ne un uwegi gigo mag kwongʼ gi ajara e dier ogendini duto manie piny.
\v 9 Dibed ni wiu osewil gi timbe maricho mane wuoneu otimo kod mago mane otim gi ruodhi kaachiel gi monde ruodhi mag Juda to gi richo mane utimo kaachiel gi mondeu e piny Juda kod e yore mag Jerusalem?
\v 10 Nyaka chil kawuono pod ok gibolore kata chiwo luor, bende pod ok girito chikena gi buchena mane amiyou kaachiel gi wuoneu.
\p 
\v 11 “Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Aramo chuth ni nyaka akel masira kuomu kendo atiek Juda duto.
\v 12 Anakaw jo-Juda modongʼ mane oramo ni nyaka dhi Misri mondo gidak kanyo. Giduto ginirum Misri; noneg-gi gi ligangla kata ginitho nikech kech. Kochakore ngʼat matin nyaka ngʼat maduongʼ, noneg-gi gi ligangla kata gi kech. Ginibed gir kwongʼ kod bwok, joma ongʼadnegi bura kendo mijaro.
\v 13 Anakum joma odak Misri gi ligangla, kech kod masira, mana kaka nakumo Jerusalem.
\v 14 Onge jo-Juda mane odongʼ mane odhi dak Misri ma notony kata kwo ma ok odwogo e piny Juda, ma gigombo duogoe kendo dakie; onge manoduogi makmana ji moko manok manoringo lweny.”
\p 
\v 15 Eka chwo duto mane ongʼeyo ni mondegi wangʼo ubani ne nyiseche manono, kaachiel gi mon duto mane ni kanyo, ne gin oganda mangʼeny, kod ji duto manodak e piny Misri Mamwalo kod Mamalo, nowachone Jeremia niya,
\v 16 “Ok wanawinj wach miwachonwa e nying Jehova Nyasaye!
\v 17 Adier wanatim gik moko duto mane wawacho ni wanatim: Wanawangʼ ubani ne Ruoth ma Dhako mar Polo kendo wanamiye misango miolo piny mana kaka wan kod wuonewa, ruodhiwa kod jotendwa notimo e dala mag Juda kod yore mag Jerusalem. E kindeno ne wan gi chiemo mathoth kendo ne wamewo kendo ne onge hinyruok moro amora kuomwa.
\v 18 To nyaka aa kinde mane waweyo wangʼo ubani ne Ruoth ma Dhako mar Polo kendo chiwone misango miolo piny, wasebedo maonge gimoro amora kendo ligangla gi kech osenegowa.”
\p 
\v 19 Mon-go nomedo wacho niya, “Kane wawangʼo ubani ne Ruoth ma Dhako mar Polo kendo chiwone misango miolo piny, donge chwowa nongʼeyo nine waloso kek machalo gi kite kendo wachiwone misango miolo piny?”
\p 
\v 20 Eka Jeremia nowachone ji duto, chwo kaachiel gi mon, mane dwoke niya,
\v 21 “Uparo ni Jehova Nyasaye ne ok ongʼeyo wach misengini ma un gi kwereu, kod ruodhiu gi jotendu kaachiel gi jopinyu duto ne otimo e miech Juda kendo e yore mag Jerusalem? Koso uparo ni wiye osewil kodgi.
\v 22 Ka Jehova Nyasaye ne ok nyal dhi nyime gineno timbeu mamono kod gigo magath mane utimo, pinyu nokwongʼ kendo odongʼ gunda maonge gima odakie, mana kaka en kawuono.
\v 23 Nikech usewangʼo ubani kendo usetimo richo ne Jehova Nyasaye kendo pod ok uluore kata luwo chikene kata puonj mage kod dwaro mage, masirani osebiro kuomu, mana kaka unene sani.”
\p 
\v 24 Eka Jeremia nowachone ji duto, kaachiel gi mon, “Winjuru wach Jehova Nyasaye, un jo-Juda duto modak Misri.
\v 25 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho: Un gi mondu usenyiso gi timbeu gik mane usingoru ka uwacho ni, ‘Nyaka wachop singruok mane waketo mar wangʼo ubani kendo chiwo misango miolo piny ne Ruoth ma Dhako mar Polo.’
\p “Dhiuru nyime, kendo utim gima ne usingo! Rituru singruoku!
\v 26 To winj wach Jehova Nyasaye, un jo-Yahudi duto modak Misri: ‘Akwongʼora gi nyinga maduongʼ,’ Jehova Nyasaye owacho, ‘ni onge ngʼato angʼata moa Juda modak Misri manochak oluong nyinga kata kwongʼore niya, “Akwongʼora gi nying Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto.”
\v 27 Angʼiyo kaka dakelnegi hinyruok, to ok kelonegi ber; nimar un jo-Yahudi man Misri nonegu gi ligangla kod kech nyaka tieku pep.
\v 28 Jogo mane otonyne ligangla kendo odwogo e piny Juda koa Misri nobed manok. Eka jo-Juda duto mane odongʼ mane obiro dak Misri nongʼe ni en wach ngʼa matiyo, mara koso margi.
\p 
\v 29 “ ‘Ma ema nobednu ranyisi ni anakumu kaeni, mondo omi ungʼe ni gima asechano timonu notimre.’
\v 30 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: ‘Anachiw Farao Hofra ruodh Misri ne wasike madwaro ngimane, mana kaka ne achiwo Zedekia ruodh Juda ne Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon jasike mane dwaro ngimane.’ ”
\c 45
\s1 Ote ne Baruk
\p 
\v 1 Ma e gima janabi Jeremia nonyiso Baruk wuod Neria e higa mar angʼwen ma Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda, bangʼ ka Baruk ne osendiko e kitabu weche mane Jeremia wachone to ondiko:
\v 2 “Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasach Israel, wachoni, in Baruk:
\v 3 Ne iwacho ni, ‘Mano kaka awinjo malit! Jehova Nyasaye osemedona rem; arumo nikech rem mapek ma an-go kendo aonge gi yweyo.’ ”
\p 
\v 4 Jehova Nyasaye nowacho, “Wachne kama: ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: Abiro muko gik moko duto masegero kendo pudho gik moko duto masepidho e piny ngima.
\v 5 Bende inyalo dwaro gik madongo ne in owuon? Kik idwargi. Nimar anakel masira ne ji duto, Jehova Nyasaye wacho, to kamoro amora midhiyoe anares ngimani.’ ”
\c 46
\s1 Ote kuom Misri
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach Jehova Nyasaye mane obirone janabi Jeremia kuom ogendini:
\b
\p 
\v 2 Kuom Misri:
\b
\p Ma e ote ne jolwenj Farao Neko ruodh Misri, mane oloo Karkemish e Aora mar Yufrate gi Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon e higa mar angʼwen mar Jehoyakim wuod Josia ruodh Juda:
\q1 
\v 3 “Ikuru okumba magu,
\q2 madongo kod matindo,
\q2 kendo uwuog udhi e kedo!
\q1 
\v 4 Gauru farese, idhuru farese!
\q2 Kawuru kereu kurwako oguteu mag lweny!
\q2 Piaguru tongeu, rwakuru okumba mau!
\q1 
\v 5 En angʼo ma aneno?
\q2 Kihondko ogoyogi,
\q1 kendo giringo ka gia kar lweny
\q2 nikech thuondi mag-gi mag lweny oselo.
\q1 Giringo ka luoro omakogi ma ok gingʼi ngʼegi,
\q2 kendo gin-gi luoro malich koni gi koni,”
\q4 Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\q1 
\v 6 “Joma yot ok nyal ringo
\q2 kata joma otegno ok nyal tony.
\q1 E yo nyandwat but Aora Yufrate
\q2 gichwanyore kendo gipodho.
\b
\q1 
\v 7 “Ma en ngʼa magingore ka aora Nael
\q2 kendo mana ka aore ma pigegi bubni?
\q1 
\v 8 Misri bubni ka aora Nael
\q2 kendo mana ka aore ma pigegi bubni.
\q1 Owacho ni, ‘Abiro gingora kendo anapongʼ piny;
\q2 anaketh mier madongo kod ji modakie.’
\q1 
\v 9 Wuoguru, yaye farese!
\q2 Yaye, un joriemb geche, riembgiuru matek!
\q1 Dhiuru nyime,
\q2 yaye un jolweny machwo moa Kush,
\q1 gi Put motingʼo okumbini,
\q2 kaachiel gi chwo Lidia maywayo atungʼ.
\q1 
\v 10 To odiechiengno en mar Ruoth,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego ma en odiechiengʼ,
\q1 ma ochuloe kuor ni wasike.
\q2 Ligangla noneki nyaka owinj ni orome,
\q1 kendo nyaka otiek riyo mare gi remo.
\q2 Nimar Ruoth, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego,
\q1 nochiw misango e piny mantie yo
\q2 nyandwat but Aora Yufrate.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 “Dhiyo nyaka Gilead
\q2 kendo imany yath, yaye Nyar Misri Mangili.
\q1 To kata obedo ni imedo manyo yedhe
\q2 to imenyo kayiem kendo ok inichangi.
\q1 
\v 12 Ogendini nowinj wichkuot momaki;
\q2 ywakni nopongʼ piny.
\q1 Jolweny nochwanyre kuom moro ka moro;
\q2 giduto ginipodhi kanyakla.”
\p 
\v 13 Ma e ote mane Jehova Nyasaye owachone Jeremia janabi kuom biro Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon mondo omonj Misri:
\q1 
\v 14 “Land wachni e piny Misri,
\q2 kendo igo milome e Migdol;
\q1 Memfis gi Tapanhes ni:
\q2 ‘Kawuru kereu kendo ikreuru,
\q2 nimar ligangla nego jogo molwori.’
\q1 
\v 15 En angʼo momiyo
\q2 jolweny magu opie piny?
\q1 Ok ginyal chungʼ,
\q2 nimar Jehova Nyasaye nolwargi piny.
\q1 
\v 16 Ginichwanyre moluwore oluwore;
\q2 giniluowre kuom jowetegi.
\q1 Giniwachi ni, ‘Aa malo,
\q2 wadog ir jowa wawegi;
\q1 kendo e pinywa owuon,
\q2 mabor gi ligangla mar joma thiro ji.’
\q1 
\v 17 E kanyono giniwach ni,
\q2 ‘Farao ruodh Misri en mana jakoko matek,
\q2 nikech thuolo mane en-go nobaye.’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 18 Ruoth wacho niya,
\q2 “Akwongʼora gi nyinga awuon,
\q1 ma en Jehova Nyasaye Maratego,
\q2 ngʼato achiel nobi machalo gi Tabor e dier gode,
\q2 kata ka Got Karmel mantie but nam.
\q1 
\v 19 Pang gigi mar dhiyoe twech,
\q2 un joma odak Misri,
\q1 nimar Memfis nowe gunda,
\q2 kendo tieke chuth maonge ngʼama nodagie.”
\b
\q1 
\v 20 “Misri en nyaroya maber neno,
\q2 to kalabugo birone koa yo nyandwat.
\q1 
\v 21 Jolweny mondiki chal gi nyiroye machwe.
\q2 Gin bende ginilokre kendo giring kanyakla,
\q2 ok giniriti,
\q1 nimar odiechiengʼ mar masira biro kuomgi,
\q2 kinde margi mar kum.
\q1 
\v 22 Misri nokudhi ka thuol maringo
\q2 ka jasigu masudo machiegni gi teko;
\q1 giniked kode gi ledhi,
\q2 mana ka chwo matongʼo yiende.”
\q1 
\v 23 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Ginibet bungu mare,
\q1 kata obedo ni oyugno kamano.
\q2 Gingʼeny moloyo dede, ok nyal kwan-gi.
\q1 
\v 24 Nyar Misri nomi wichkuot,
\q2 kendo nochiwe ne jogo moa yo nyandwat.”
\p 
\v 25 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho niya, “Achiegni kelo kum kuom Amon ma nyasach Thebes, kuom Farao, kuom Misri gi nyisechene kod ruodhi mage, kod jogo mogeno kuom Farao.
\v 26 Anachiwgi ne jogo madwaro ngimagi, ne Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon gi jotende. To kata kamano ji nodhi nyime dak Misri kaka chon,” Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 27 “Kik iluor; yaye jatichna Jakobo;
\q1 bende kik ibwogi, yaye Israel.
\q2 Adiera abiro resi e piny mabor,
\q1 kaachiel gi nyikwayi
\q2 e piny mane otergie twech.
\q1 Jakobo nodhi nyime ka nigi
\q2 kwe gi dak maonge luoro,
\q2 kendo onge ngʼama nobwoge.
\q1 
\v 28 Kik iluor, yaye Jakobo jatichna, nimar an kodi.
\q1 Kata obedo ni atieko ogendini
\q2 duto ma asekeyou e diergi,
\q2 ok anatieku chuth.
\q1 Anakumu to mana gi bura makare;
\q2 ok anaweu ngangʼ ma ok akumou,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\c 47
\s1 Ote kuom jo-Filistia
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mar Jehova Nyasaye mane obirone janabi Jeremia kuom jo-Filistia kapok Farao nomonjo Gaza:
\b
\p 
\v 2 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Neuru kaka pige gingore e yo nyandwat;
\q2 ginibed ataro mopongʼ.
\q1 Giniyieny e piny
\q2 kod gimoro amora manie iye,
\q1 mier gi jok modak eigi.
\q2 Ji noywagi;
\q2 jogo duto modak e piny nodengi.
\q1 
\v 3 Ka giwinjo
\q2 koko mar tiend farese ma giro,
\q1 kod koko mar geche wasigu
\q2 to gi moor tiend gechegi.
\q1 Wuone ok nokony nyithindgi;
\q2 lwetgi kalandhidhi nomaki.
\q1 
\v 4 Nimar odiechiengʼ
\q2 osechopo mondo otiek jo-Filistia duto,
\q1 kendo gengʼo joma notony duto
\q2 mane nyalo konyo Turo kod Sidon.
\q1 Jehova Nyasaye ochiegni tieko jo-Filistia,
\q2 jogo mane otony moa e dho nam mar Kaftor.
\q1 
\v 5 Jo-Gaza noliel wigi
\q2 manyiso ni gin gi kuyo;
\q1 kendo jo-Ashkelon noket malingʼ thii.
\q2 Yaye un joma otony manie pewe,
\q2 unungʼadru nyaka kara angʼo?
\b
\q1 
\v 6 “Uywak ni, ‘Yaye ligangla mar Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 ibiro yweyo nyaka karangʼo?
\q1 Dog ei olaloni;
\q2 chungʼ kendo ilingʼ thi.’
\q1 
\v 7 To ere kaka onyalo yweyo
\q2 ka Jehova Nyasaye owuon osechiko,
\q1 ka osechiwo chik
\q2 mondo omonj Ashkelon to gi dho nam?”
\c 48
\s1 Wach kuom Moab
\p 
\v 1 To kuom Moab:
\b
\p Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel wacho:
\q1 “Mano kaka nobed malit ne Nebo,
\q2 nimar enokethe.
\q1 Kiriathaim nokuod wiye
\q2 kendo enomake;
\q1 kar pondogi nobed kama
\q2 inyiero kendo nomuke.
\q1 
\v 2 Pak mar Moab ok nobedi kendo;
\q2 ji nochan kethruokne ei Heshbon kagiwacho kama:
\q2 ‘Biuru, watiek pinyni.’
\q1 Yaye joma odak Madmen,
\q2 un bende ligangla nolawu mulingʼ thii.
\q1 
\v 3 Winj ywak moa Horonaim,
\q2 ywak mar duwruok maduongʼ gi kethruok.
\q1 
\v 4 Moab nokethi;
\q2 nyithinde matindo noywagre.
\q1 
\v 5 Giidho ka giluwo yo madhi Luhith,
\q2 gi ywak malit ka gidhi;
\q1 e yo maridore kadhi Horonaim
\q2 kendo ywak malit mar kethruok winjore.
\q1 
\v 6 Ringuru! Ringuru ukony ngimau;
\q2 muchal gi bungu manie thim!
\q1 
\v 7 Nikech ugeno kuom timbeu kod mwandu mau,
\q2 un bende nomaku,
\q1 kendo Kemosh noter e twech,
\q2 kanyakla gi jodolo mage kod jotelo mage.
\q1 
\v 8 Jaketh gik moko nobi e dala
\q2 ka dala kendo onge dala ma notony.
\q1 Holo noum kendo got mar mesa nomuki,
\q2 nikech Jehova Nyasaye osewacho.
\q1 
\v 9 Ket chumbi kuom Moab,
\q2 nimar enotieke;
\q1 miechgi nodongʼ gunda,
\q2 maonge ngʼama nodagi eigi.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 “Okwongʼ ngʼat mayom yom e tich Jehova Nyasaye!
\q2 Okwongʼ ngʼat ma okano liganglane ma ok ochwerogo remo!
\b
\q1 
\v 11 “Moab oseyweyo chakre tin-ne,
\q2 ka divai mowe mos e aguche,
\q1 ma ok ool koa ei agulu achiel
\q2 kiloko machielo kendo pod ok odhi e twech.
\q1 Omiyo ndhathe pod nikare,
\q2 kendo tik mare ok olokore.”
\q1 
\v 12 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q1 “Kinde biro, ma anaor ji manopuke oko,
\q2 kendo gini ole oko;
\q2 giniwe agulni mage nono kendo toyo agulni mage.
\q1 
\v 13 Eka Moab wiye nokuodi gi Kemosh,
\q2 mana kaka od Israel wiye nokuot,
\q2 kane gin-gi geno kuom Bethel.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 “Ere kaka inyalo wacho ni, ‘Wan jokedo,
\q2 ji mathuondi maroteke e lweny’?”
\q1 
\v 15 Ruoth, ma nyinge Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho niya,
\q1 “Moab nokethi kendo mier mage nomonji;
\q2 yawuote mabeyo noter e kar nek.
\q1 
\v 16 Podho mar Moab osechopone;
\q2 masichene nobi mapiyo.
\q1 
\v 17 Ywageuru, un jogo duto modak machiegni kode,
\q2 un jogo duto mongʼeyo humbe;
\q1 wachuru ni, ‘Mano kaka otur odunga mar loch maratego,
\q2 mano kaka otur ludh duongʼ!’
\b
\q1 
\v 18 “Auru malo e duongʼu ulor piny
\q2 kendo ubedi e lowo motwo,
\q2 yaye jodak mar Nyar Dibon,
\q1 nimar ngʼama oketho Moab nobi
\q2 mondo oked kodu,
\q2 kendo otiek miechu madongo mochiel motegno gohinga.
\q1 
\v 19 Chunguru e bath yo kendo ungʼi,
\q2 un joma odak Aroer.
\q1 Penj dichwo maringo
\q2 kod dhako maringo, ni,
\q2 Angʼo mosetimore?
\q1 
\v 20 Okuod wi Moab,
\q2 nimar ongʼinje matindo tindo.
\q1 Dengi kendo iywag matek!
\q2 Land e Arnon ni Moab okethi.
\q1 
\v 21 Ngʼado bura osebiro
\q2 e got mar mesa kuom Holon,
\q2 Jaza kod Mefath,
\q1 
\v 22 kuom Dibon,
\q2 Nebo kod Beth Diblathaim,
\q1 
\v 23 kuom Kiriathaim,
\q2 Beth Gamul kod Beth Mion,
\q1 
\v 24 kuom Kerioth gi
\q2 Bozra, kuom mier duto mag Moab,
\q2 man mabor kod mago man machiegni.
\q1 
\v 25 Tung Moab ongʼad oko;
\q2 bade otur,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 26 “Kete omer,
\q2 nimar osetamore winjo Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 We Moab odwanyre e ngʼokne;
\q2 we obed gima ijaro.
\q1 
\v 27 Donge Israel ema ne ijaro?
\q2 Bende nomake e dier jokwoge,
\q1 ma itengʼone wiyi gi achaya sa moro
\q2 amora miwuoyo kuome?
\q1 
\v 28 Jwangʼuru miechu
\q2 kendo udagi e kind lwendni,
\q1 un joma odak Moab.
\q2 Chaluru ka akuch odugla maloso ode e dho rogo.
\b
\q1 
\v 29 “Wasewinjo sunga mar Moab,
\q2 sungane mokadhore gi miriambo,
\q1 sunga mare gi jendeke
\q2 mare kod ngʼayi mar chunye.”
\q1 
\v 30 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Angʼeyo mirimbe to oonge tiende,
\q2 kendo ngʼayi mage ok nyal gimoro.
\q1 
\v 31 Emomiyo aywak kadengo kuom Moab,
\q2 nimar kuom Moab duto aywak,
\q2 aywago jo-Kir Hareseth.
\q1 
\v 32 Aywagou, kaka Jazer ywak,
\q2 yaye mzabibu mag Sibma.
\q1 Bedeni kar machopo e nam;
\q2 negichopo nyaka e nam mar Jazer.
\q1 Jaketh gik moko osepodho e olembegi
\q2 mochiek kod olemo mar mzabibu.
\q1 
\v 33 Ilo gi mor orumo e puoth olembe
\q2 kod puothe mag Moab.
\q1 Asechungo chwer mar divai koa
\q2 e kuonde mibiyogie;
\q1 onge ngʼama nyonogi gi koko mar ilo.
\q2 Kata obedo ni nitiere koko,
\q2 ok gin koko mar ilo.
\b
\q1 
\v 34 “Dwond ywak mag-gi winjore
\q2 koa Heshbon nyaka Eleale gi Jahaz,
\q1 koa Zoar nyaka chop Horonaim gi Eglath Shelishiya,
\q2 nimar kata pige mag Nimrim bende osetwo.
\q1 
\v 35 E Moab anatiek jogo matimo misengini
\q2 e kuonde motingʼore gi malo,
\q2 kendo ma wangʼo ubani ne nyisechegi,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 36 “Omiyo chunya ywagorene Moab ka asili;
\q2 oywagore ka asili ne jo-Kir Hareseth.
\q2 Mwandu mane giyudo oserumo.
\q1 
\v 37 Wich ka wich oliel
\q2 kendo yie tik ka yie tik ongʼad oko;
\q1 lwedo ka lwedo otongʼ
\q2 oko kendo nungo ka nungo oum gi law ywak.
\q1 
\v 38 Ewi tat udi duto man Moab
\q1 kendo e laru mar galamoro
\q2 onge gimoro makmana ywak,
\q1 nimar aseketho Moab ka
\q2 agulu motore maonge ngʼama dwaro,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 39 “Mano kaka otieke! Mano kaka gidengo!
\q2 Mano kaka Moab loko ngʼeye kopondo nikech wichkuot!
\q1 Moab osebedo gir ajara,
\q2 gima bwogo ji duto man bute.”
\p 
\v 40 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Ne! Otenga fuyo kochiko piny,
\q2 oyaro bwombene ewi Moab.
\q1 
\v 41 Kerioth nomaki
\q2 kendo kuondegi mag pondo nokaw.
\q1 E odiechiengno chunje mag jolwenj Moab
\q2 nochal gi chuny dhako mamuoch kayo.
\q1 
\v 42 Moab notieki kaka oganda
\q2 nikech ne otamore winjo Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 43 Masira maduongʼ gi bur matut
\q2 kod otegu ritou, yaye jo-Moab,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 44 “Ngʼatno manotem tony
\q2 nikech masira nolwar e bur matut,
\q1 ngʼatno manotem kawuok ei bur matut,
\q2 nomak gi obadho;
\q1 nimar anakel magi
\q2 kuom Moab e higa mar kum,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 45 “E tipo mar Heshbon
\q2 joma noringo odongʼ ka ok nyal,
\q1 nimar mach osemoko liel Heshbon
\q2 kendo ligek mach osewuok e dier Sihon;
\q1 owangʼo lela wangʼ Moab,
\q2 kod choke wich mag jongʼayigo!
\q1 
\v 46 Mano kaka inine malit, yaye Moab!
\q2 Jo-Kemosh otieki;
\q1 yawuoti oter e twech,
\q2 kendo nyigi oket wasumbini.
\b
\q1 
\v 47 “Kata kamano anaduog gweth mag Moab
\q2 e ndalo mabiro,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\p Ma e giko mar ngʼadone Moab bura.
\b
\c 49
\s1 Wach kuom Amon
\p 
\v 1 Wach kuom jo-Amon:
\b
\p Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Onge yawuowi e Israel?
\q2 Oonge gi jarit girkeni mage?
\q1 To kare angʼo momiyo Molek osekawo mwandu Gad?
\q2 Angʼo momiyo joge odak e dalane?”
\q1 
\v 2 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “To ndalo biro,
\q1 ma anagoye koko mar lweny
\q2 mondo oked gi Raba mar jo-Amon;
\q1 enobed pith mar kethruok,
\q2 kendo gwenge molworogi nowangʼ.
\q1 Eka Israel noriemb
\q2 jogo mane oriembogi,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 
\v 3 “Dengi, yaye Heshbon, nimar Ai okethi!
\q2 Ywaguru, yaye joma odak Raba!
\q1 Rwakuru lepu mag ywak kendo uywagi;
\q2 ringuru koni gi koni,
\q2 e alwora mar dala,
\q1 nimar Molek noter e twech,
\q2 kaachiel gi jodolo mage kod jotelo mage.
\q1 
\v 4 Angʼo momiyo usungoru kuom holo mau,
\q2 sungruok kuom holo mau manyak?
\q1 Yaye nyako ma ok ja-ratiro,
\q2 igeno kuom mwandu magi kendo iwacho niya,
\q2 Ngʼama biro monja?
\q1 
\v 5 Anakel luoro kuomu koa
\q1 kuom jogo duto man butu,”
\q2 Ruoth, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego ema owacho.
\q1 “Un duto noriembu,
\q2 kendo onge ngʼama nochok joma noringo moke.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 “Kata kamano bangʼe, anaduog mwandu jo-Amon,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\s1 Wach Kuom Edom
\p 
\v 7 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho kuom Edom:
\b
\q1 “Bende pod nitie rieko ei Teman?
\q2 To puonj oselalne jorieko?
\q2 To rieko mag-gi osetop?
\q1 
\v 8 Lokreuru kendo uringi,
\q2 ponduru e rogo mopandore,
\q1 un joma odak Dedan, nimar anakel masira
\q2 ne Esau e kinde ma anakume.
\q1 
\v 9 Ka jopon olemb mzabibu obiro iru,
\q2 donge digiwe olemb mzabibu matin?
\q1 Ka jokwoge obiro gotieno,
\q2 donge gibiro kwalo mwandu magu kaka ginyalo?
\q1 
\v 10 To analony Esau duk;
\q2 anael kuondege malingʼ-lingʼ,
\q2 mondo omi kik opondi.
\q1 Nyithinde, wedene gi jomodak bute nolal nono,
\q2 kendo ok nochak obed chutho.
\q1 
\v 11 Weuru kiye mau; anares ngimagi.
\q2 Mondu duto ma chwogi otho,
\q2 bende nyalo keto geno mag-gi kuoma.”
\p 
\v 12 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho: “Ka jogo ma ok owinjore omadh kikombe nyaka madhe, to angʼo momiyo ok anyal kumi? Ok initony ma ok okumi, to nyaka imadhe.”
\v 13 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Akwongʼora gi nyinga awuon, ni Bozra nokethi kendo nobed gir bwogo ji, gir jaro kendo nobed gir kwongʼ, kendo mieche duto nokethi chuth.”
\q1 
\v 14 Asewinjo wach koa kuom Jehova Nyasaye kama:
\q2 Jaote oseor mondo owach ne ogendini niya,
\q1 “Chokreuru mondo umonje!
\q2 Chungʼuru malo wadhi e kedo!”
\b
\q1 
\v 15 “Koro abiro miyo udok matin
\q2 e kind ogendini, kendo joma ijaro e dier ji.
\q1 
\v 16 Luoro musemiyo ji kod
\q2 sunga manie chunyu osewuondou,
\q1 un jogo modak e kind lwendni,
\q2 modak kuonde motingʼore gi malo mar got.
\q1 Kata obedo ni ugero uteu mabor ka od otenga,
\q2 koa kuno abiro dwokou piny,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 17 “Edom nobed gima bwogo ji;
\q2 jogo duto makalo bute nohum nono,
\q2 kendo gininyiere ka gineno adhondene duto.”
\q1 
\v 18 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Mana kaka Sodom gi Gomora nokethi,
\q2 kaachiel gi mier mokiewo kodgi,
\q1 e kaka en bende nobedi maonge
\q2 ngʼato angʼata modak kanyo kendo.
\b
\q1 
\v 19 “Ka sibuor mabiro koa
\q2 e bungu moyugno mar Jordan nyaka
\q2 kar kwath man-gi lum,
\q1 anariemb Edom oa e pinye kadiemo wangʼ.
\q2 En ngʼa mowal manyalo yiero ne ma?
\q1 En ngʼa machalo koda kendo manyalo chungʼ koda?
\q2 Koso jakwath mane manyalo chungʼ koda?”
\b
\q1 
\v 20 Emomiyo, winj gima Jehova Nyasaye
\q2 osechano timo ne Edom,
\q1 gima oseramo ni nyaka otimne joma odak Teman:
\q2 Nyithi rombe bende nokaw;
\q2 enoketh chuth kuondegi mag kwath nikech gin.
\q1 
\v 21 Piny noyiengni kowinjo ni ologi;
\q2 ywakgi nowinjre nyaka e Nam Makwar.
\q1 
\v 22 Ne! Otenga nofu kochomo malo
\q2 kendo piny koyaro bwombene ewi Bozra.
\q1 E odiechiengno chunje jolweny mag Edom
\q2 nochal gi chuny dhako mamuoch kayo.
\s1 Wach kuom Damaski
\p 
\v 23 Kuom Damaski:
\q1 “Hamath gi Arpad luoro omako,
\q2 nimar giwinjo wach marach,
\q1 chunygi omoko,
\q2 kendo nigi chandruok ka nam mogingore.
\q1 
\v 24 Damaski osebedo maonge teko,
\q2 osea gi ngʼwech,
\q1 kendo achiedh-nade osemake;
\q2 lit gi rem osemake,
\q2 kaka rem mar dhako mamuoch kayo.
\q1 
\v 25 Angʼo momiyo ok osejwangʼ
\q2 dala maduongʼ mongʼere; dala mamor godo?
\q1 
\v 26 Adiera, joge matindo nopodh e yore;
\q2 jolweny mage duto nolingʼ thi odiechiengno,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego owacho.
\q1 
\v 27 “Anawangʼ ohingini mag Damaski;
\q2 notiek kuonde mochiel motegno mag Ben-Hadad.”
\s1 Wach kuom Keda kod Hazo
\p 
\v 28 Kuom Kedar gi pinyruodhi mag Hazor, mane Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon omonjo:
\b
\p Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Chungʼuru malo,
\q2 kendo umonj Keda,
\q2 mi utiek joma aa yo wuok chiengʼ.
\q1 
\v 29 Hembegi gi jambgi nokaw;
\q2 kar dak margi nowal oko,
\q2 kaachiel gi mwandugi duto kod ngamia.
\q1 Ji nogonegi koko ni,
\q2 ‘Masira maduongʼ koni gi koni!’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 30 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Ringuru piyo uayi!
\q1 Daguru e rogo matut,
\q2 un joma odak Hazor.
\q1 Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon nigi paro marach kuomu;
\q2 osechano timonu marach.
\b
\q1 
\v 31 “Chunguru kendo umonj pinyni momewo,
\q2 modak kodhil,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho,
\q1 “piny maonge dhorangeye kata lodi;
\q2 joge odak kendgi.
\q1 
\v 32 Ngamia mag-gi noyaki
\q2 kendo kweth mag dhogi nope.
\q1 Anake joge mantie kuma bor e tunge piny
\q2 kendo anakelnegi masira koa koni gi koni,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 33 “Hazor nobed thim mar ondiegi,
\q2 kama ojwangʼ nyaka chiengʼ.
\q1 Onge ngʼama nodag kanyo;
\q2 onge ngʼama nodag e iye.”
\s1 Wach kuom Elam
\p 
\v 34 Ma e wach Jehova Nyasaye mane obirone janabi Jeremia kuom Elam, e ndalo chakruok mar loch Zedekia ruodh Juda:
\b
\p 
\v 35 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, wacho:
\q1 “Ne, anatur atung Elam,
\q2 girgi maduongʼ mar tekogi.
\q1 
\v 36 Anamonj Elam gi yembe angʼwen moa
\q2 e tunge angʼwen mar polo;
\q1 anakegi e yembe angʼwen-go kendo onge piny ma
\q2 jo-Elam momaki ok nodhiye.
\q1 
\v 37 Anami Elam ongʼengʼ e nyim wasike,
\q2 e nyim jogo madwaro tieko ngimagi;
\q1 anakel masiche kuomgi,
\q2 ma en mirimba mager,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\q1 “Analawgi gi ligangla
\q2 manyaka atiekgi.”
\q1 
\v 38 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Anaket koma mar duongʼ ei Elam,
\q2 kendo atiek ruodhe kod jotende.”
\b
\q1 
\v 39 “Kata kamano anaduog mwandu Elam
\q2 e ndalo ma biro,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.
\c 50
\s1 Wach Babulon
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mane Jehova Nyasaye owacho kuom Babulon kod piny jo-Babulon kokalo kuom Jeremia janabi:
\q1 
\v 2 “Nyisuru kendo landuru e dier ogendini,
\q2 tingʼuru bandera kendo landuru;
\q2 kik upand gimoro, to wachni,
\q1 ‘Babulon nomaki;
\q2 Bel wiye nokuodi,
\q2 Marduk luoro nogo ngoga.
\q1 Gige mopa nokuod wigi
\q2 kendo nyisechegi manono nopongʼ gi luoro.’
\q1 
\v 3 Piny moa yo nyandwat nomonje
\q2 kendo pinye nodongʼ gunda.
\q1 Onge ngʼama nodag e iye;
\q2 ji kaachiel gi le noringi.”
\b
\q1 
\v 4 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “E ndalogo, sa nogono,
\q1 jo-Israel gi jo-Juda nodhi kaachiel
\q2 ka pi wangʼ-gi chwer,
\q2 ka gidwaro Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachgi.
\q1 
\v 5 Ginipenj yo madhi Sayun
\q2 kendo gilok wengegi kochiko kuno.
\q1 Ginibi kendo ginitwere kuom
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye e singruok mochwere,
\q2 ma wich ok nowil godo.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 “Joga osebedo rombe molal;
\q2 jokwathgi osewitogi,
\q1 kendo osemiyogi bayo e gode madongo.
\q2 Negibayo e gode madongo gi gode matindo,
\q2 kendo wigi ne owil gi kargi mar yweyo.
\q1 
\v 7 Ngʼato angʼata mane oyudogi nokidhogi;
\q2 wasikgi nowacho niya,
\q1 ‘Ok wan joketho,
\q2 nimar negitimo richo ni Jehova Nyasaye,
\q1 kar kwadhgi madiera,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye, geno mar wuonegi.’
\b
\q1 
\v 8 “Ringuru uwuog Babulon;
\q2 ayeuru e piny jo-Babulon,
\q2 kendo uchal gi diek motelone jamni.
\q1 
\v 9 Anami ogendini maroteke
\q2 moriwore moa yo nyandwat obi omonj Babulon.
\q1 Ginikaw keregi mondo gimonje,
\q2 kendo koa yo nyandwat enomake.
\q1 Aserni mag-gi nochal gi jolweny molony,
\q2 ma ok duogi gi lwetgi nono.”
\q1 
\v 10 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Omiyo Babulon noyaki;
\q2 jogo moyake nokaw gik moromogi.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 “Nikech un gi ilo kendo umor,
\q2 un joma ketho girkeni maga,
\q1 nikech uchwe ka nyaroya machamo lum
\q2 kendo ugiro ka farese,
\q1 
\v 12 minu wiye nokuodi malich;
\q2 ngʼatno mane onywolou nobed gi wichkuot maduongʼ.
\q1 En ema nobedie ngʼat matin kuom ogendini,
\q2 nochal thim, piny motimo ongoro, kama otwo.
\q1 
\v 13 Nikech ich wangʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 ok nobed gi joma odak e iye,
\q1 to enobed gunda chuth.
\q2 Jogo duto makalo Babulon,
\q1 nobed gi bwok maduongʼ
\q2 kendo nyiere nikech adhondene duto.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 “Kawuru kereu e alwora mar Babulon,
\q2 un duto maywayo atungʼ.
\q1 Bayeuru gi asere! Kik uwe asere moro amora,
\q2 nimar osetimo richo ne Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 15 Gone koko kuonde duto!
\q2 Otingʼo bade kanyiso ni oloye,
\q1 kuondene mag ngʼicho motingʼore gi malo podho,
\q2 ohinga mage imuko.
\q1 Nikech ma e chulo kuor mar Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 chulneuru kuor;
\q2 timneuru kaka osetimo ni joma moko.
\q1 
\v 16 Gol jachwoyo oko e Babulon,
\q2 kod jakeyo gi pande mar keyo.
\q1 Nikech ligangla mar ngʼama thiro ji
\q2 we ngʼato ka ngʼato odog ir joge,
\q1 we ngʼato ka ngʼato
\q2 oringi odhi e pinye owuon.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 “Israel chalo gi rombe mokee
\q2 ma sibuor oseriembo.
\q2 Mano mane okwongo kidhe ne en ruodh Asuria;
\q1 mano mogik mane oturo chokege
\q2 ne en Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon.”
\p 
\v 18 Emomiyo ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho:
\q1 “Anakum ruodh Babulon gi pinye
\q2 kaka ne akumo ruodh Asuria.
\q1 
\v 19 To anaduog Israel e kare
\q2 mar kwath kendo enokwa e Karmel kod Bashan;
\q2 noyiengʼ e gode matindo mag Efraim gi Gilead.”
\q1 
\v 20 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “E ndalogo, e sechego,
\q1 nomany ketho Israel, to onge manoyudi,
\q2 kendo ne richo Juda, to onge manoyudi,
\q2 nimar anangʼwon-ne jogo mane odongʼ mane aweyo.”
\b
\q1 
\v 21 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Monj piny Merathaim kod jogo modak Pekod.
\q1 Lawgi, neg-gi kendo utiekgi duto.
\q2 Timuru gimoro amora masechikou.
\q1 
\v 22 Koko mar lweny ni e piny,
\q2 koko mar kethruok maduongʼ!
\q1 
\v 23 Mano kaka nyundo mar piny ngima otur
\q2 kendo obarore!
\q2 Mano kaka Babulon odongʼ,
\q2 gunda e dier pinje!
\q1 
\v 24 Achikonu obadho,
\q2 yaye Babulon, kendo nomaku kapod ok ungʼeyo;
\q2 noyudu kendo omaku nikech ne ukwedo Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 25 Jehova Nyasaye oseyawo kare mar kano gige lweny,
\q2 kendo ogolo gige mag lweny mag mirimbe,
\q1 nimar Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto kendo Maratego nigi tich monego ti
\q2 e piny jo-Babulon.
\q1 
\v 26 Bi imonje gi kuma bor.
\q2 Yiech deche mage; choke ka pith mar cham.
\q1 Tieke chuth,
\q2 kendo kik obed gi ngʼato moro amora motony.
\q1 
\v 27 Neguru nyirwedhi mage duto;
\q2 we gidhi e kar yengʼo!
\q1 Mano kaka gininee malit!
\q2 Nimar odiechiengʼ osechopo,
\q2 kinde monego kumgi.
\q1 
\v 28 Winjuru jo-Israel maringo
\q2 kod matony koa Babulon,
\q1 mawacho e Sayun ni mano kaka
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachwa osechulo kuor,
\q2 kuor nikech hekalu mare.
\b
\q1 
\v 29 “Chikuru jo-aserni
\q2 mondo omonj Babulon,
\q1 jogo duto maywayo atungʼ.
\q2 Chokreuru bute; kik uwe ngʼato pondi.
\q1 Chuleuru nikech timbene;
\q2 timneuru kaka osetimo.
\q1 Nimar ok osewinjo Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 Jal Maler mar Israel.”
\q1 
\v 30 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Emomiyo, joge matindo nogore piny e yore;
\q2 jolweny mage duto nonegi odiechiengno.”
\q1 
\v 31 Ruoth, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho niya,
\q1 “Ne, ok adwari, yaye janjore,
\q2 nimar odiechiengi osechopo,
\q2 kinde mari mar kum.
\q1 
\v 32 Janjore nochwanyre kendo podhi
\q2 kendo onge ngʼama nochunge malo;
\q1 anamok mach e dalane manowangʼ
\q2 jogo duto man machiegni kode.”
\p 
\v 33 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Jo-Israel ithiro,
\q2 kaachiel gi jo-Juda bende kamano.
\q1 Joma ne omakogi nomakogi matek,
\q2 ma ok nyal weyogi gidhi.
\q1 
\v 34 Kata kamano Jawar margi en ratego;
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego e nyinge.
\q1 Enokonygi gi nyalone duto
\q2 mondo omi gibed gi yweyo e pinygi;
\q2 to jo-Babulon nomi obed gi tungni.”
\b
\q1 
\v 35 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Ligangla notiek jo-Babulon!
\q1 Notiek jogo modak Babulon
\q2 kendo notiek jotende kod joge mariek!
\q1 
\v 36 Ligangla notiek jonabi mage
\q2 mag miriambo! Ginibed joma ofuwo.
\q1 Ligangla notiek jolweny mage!
\q2 Luoro maduongʼ nomakgi.
\q1 
\v 37 Ligangla notiek faresege
\q2 gi gechene kod welo duto mane ondiko e lweny!
\q1 Ginibed ka mon.
\q1 Ligangla notiek kuondegi mag
\q2 kano mwandu kendo nokwalgi!
\q1 
\v 38 Pige mag aoregi nodwon matuo.
\q2 Nimar en piny mopongʼ gi nyiseche manono,
\q2 ma gin nyiseche mamiyo neko nomaku.
\b
\q1 
\v 39 “Omiyo gige thim kod ondiegi nodag kanyo,
\q2 kendo kanyo tula nodagie.
\q1 Onge gima nobedie kendo
\q2 onge ngʼama nochak odagie e tienge duto.”
\q1 
\v 40 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Mana kaka Nyasaye noketho Sodom gi Gomora,
\q1 kaachiel gi mier mokiewo kodgi,
\q2 e kaka en bende nobedi maonge ngʼato angʼata,
\q2 modak kanyo kendo.
\b
\q1 
\v 41 “Neuru! Jolweny biro koa yo nyandwat;
\q2 oganda maduongʼ kod ruodhi mangʼeny itugo koa e tunge piny.
\q1 
\v 42 Gimanore gi atungʼ kod tongʼ;
\q2 giger kendo gionge ngʼwono.
\q1 Gimor ka nam mogingore
\q2 ka giriembo faresegi;
\q1 gibiro ka ji mochanore komanore
\q2 gi gige lweny mondo gimonju, yaye Nyar Babulon.
\q1 
\v 43 Ruodh Babulon osewinjo humbgi;
\q2 kendo bedene onge gi teko.
\q1 Rem malich osemake,
\q2 ka rem mar dhako mamuoch kayo.
\q1 
\v 44 Mana ka sibuor mabiro koa
\q2 e bungu moyugno mar Jordan,
\q1 nyaka kar kwath man-gi lum,
\q2 e kaka anariemb Babulon oa e pinye kadiemo wangʼ.
\q1 En ngʼa mowal manyalo yiero ne ma?
\q2 En ngʼa machalo koda kendo manyalo chungʼ koda?
\q2 Koso jakwath mane manyalo chungʼ koda?”
\b
\q1 
\v 45 Emomiyo, winj gima Jehova Nyasaye osechano timo ne Babulon,
\q2 gima oseramo ni nyaka otimne piny jo-Babulon:
\q1 Nyithi rombe bende nokaw;
\q2 enoketh chuth kuondegi mag kwath nikech gin.
\q1 
\v 46 E kinde ma Babulon nomaki piny noyiengni;
\q2 ywakne nowinjre e dier pinje.
\c 51
\p 
\v 1 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Ne, anakel chunje maketho
\q2 Kuom Babulon gi jo-Leb Kamai.
\q1 
\v 2 Anaor ji moa e pinje mamoko Babulon
\q2 mondo odhi opiedhe ka miudhwe kendo mondo oketh pinye;
\q1 ginikwede e yo mora amora e odiechienge
\q2 mar masira.
\q1 
\v 3 Kik jadir asere rid atungʼ mare,
\q2 kata kik orwak okumba mare.
\q1 Kik ingʼwon-ne joge matindo;
\q2 tiek jolweny mage duto.
\q1 
\v 4 Ginineg-gi Babulon,
\q2 kendo hinye ahinya e yorene.
\q1 
\v 5 Nimar Israel gi Juda pod
\q2 ok ojwangʼgi Nyasachgi, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego,
\q1 kata obedo ni pinygi opongʼ
\q2 gi ketho e nyim Jalno Maler mar Israel.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 “Ringuru ua Babulon!
\q2 Ringuru ukony ngimau!
\q1 Kik tieku nikech richo mag-gi.
\q2 En kinde ma Jehova Nyasaye chuloe kuor;
\q2 enochule gima owinjore kode.
\q1 
\v 7 Babulon ne en kikombe mar dhahabu
\q2 e lwet Jehova Nyasaye; nomiyo piny duto omer.
\q1 Ogendini nomadho divai mare;
\q2 emomiyo koro neko osemakogi.
\q1 
\v 8 Babulon nolwar apoya nono
\q2 kendo notieke. Deng nikech en!
\q1 Miye yath ne rem mare;
\q2 sa moro onyalo chango.
\b
\q1 
\v 9 “ ‘Ne wanyalo thiedho Babulon,
\q2 to ok onyal chango;
\q1 waweyeuru, kendo ngʼato ka ngʼato odhi e pinye owuon,
\q2 nimar osengʼadne bura mochopo e polo,
\q2 ogingore mochopo e polo.’
\b
\q1 
\v 10 “ ‘Jehova Nyasaye oseketowa joma kare;
\q2 biuru, we wawache ei Sayun,
\q2 gima Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachwa osetimo.’
\b
\q1 
\v 11 “Piaguru aserni, kauru okumbini!
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye osethuwo ruodhi mag Media kodgi,
\q1 nikech chenro mare en ketho Babulon.
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye nochul kuor ni hekalu mare.
\q1 
\v 12 Tingʼuru banderane e ohinga mag Babulon!
\q2 Med jolweny mamoko kijiwogi,
\q1 ket jorito keregi, ikreuru mar monjogi!
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye nodhi nyime gi chenro mare,
\q2 buche moketo mondo otimre ni jo-Babulon.
\q1 
\v 13 Un joma odak machiegni gi pige mangʼeny
\q2 kendo momewo gi mwandu mangʼeny,
\q2 gikou osechopo, sa ma itiekoue.
\q1 
\v 14 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego
\q2 osekwongʼore gi nyinge owuon:
\q1 Adier anakelnu ji mangʼeny, ka bonyo,
\q2 kendo ginikog gi ilo nikech loch molowugo.
\b
\q1 
\v 15 “Nochweyo piny gi tekone;
\q2 ne ochako piny gi riekone,
\q2 kendo oyaro polo gi ngʼeyo mare.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka omor ka polo, to pige manie polo wuo;
\q2 omiyo boche polo dhwolore koa e giko piny.
\q1 Ooro mil polo gi koth,
\q2 kendo okelo yamo koa e kuondege mag keno.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 “Ji duto parogi ok ti kendo gionge ngʼeyo;
\q2 jotheth duto wigi kuot gi nyisechegi manono, ma githedho.
\q1 Kido mage moloso gin gik manono;
\q2 gionge muya eigi.
\q1 
\v 18 Gionge tich, gin gik minyiero;
\q2 ka ndalogi mar ngʼado bura ochopo, to ginilal nono.
\q1 
\v 19 Jalno ma en Pok mar Jakobo
\q2 ok chal kodgi,
\q1 nimar en e Jachwech mar gik moko duto,
\q2 kaachiel gi dhood girkeni mare,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego e nyinge.
\b
\q1 
\v 20 “In e odungana mar lweny,
\q2 gira mar kedo, in ema atiekogo ogendini,
\q2 in ema akethogo pinjeruodhi,
\q1 
\v 21 akonyora kodi kuom tieko faras gi jaithne,
\q2 in ema atiekogo gach lweny kod jariembe,
\q1 
\v 22 in ema anegogo dichwo gi dhako,
\q2 in ema anegogo jaduongʼ kod rawere,
\q2 in ema anegogo wuowi kod nyako,
\q1 
\v 23 in ema anegogo jakwath gi rombe,
\q2 in ema anegogo japur gi rwedhi,
\q2 in ema anegogo ruodhi gi jotelo.”
\p 
\v 24 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “E nyim wangʼu anachul Babulon kod jogo duto modak Babulon kuom gigo maricho magisetimo e Sayun.”
\q1 
\v 25 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Ok adwari, yaye got maduongʼ maketho,
\q2 un joma ketho piny ngima.
\q1 Anarie bada kuomu,
\q1 anadhiru piny kua e geng got,
\q2 kendo ami ubed ka got mowangʼ.”
\q1 
\v 26 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “Onge lwanda mane kaw kuomi mar gero kona,
\q1 kata kidi moro amora mar keto mise,
\q2 nimar unudongʼ gunda nyaka chiengʼ.
\b
\q1 
\v 27 “Tingʼuru bandera e piny!
\q2 Gouru turumbete e dier ogendini!
\q2 Ikuru ogendini mondo oked kode;
\q1 luonguru pinjeruodhigi Ararat,
\q2 Mini kod Ashkenaz mondo oked kode.
\q1 Yieruru jatend lweny mondo oked kode;
\q2 oruru farese mangʼeny ka bonyo.
\q1 
\v 28 Ikuru ogendini
\q2 mondo oked kod ruodhi mag Medes,
\q1 jotendgi kod jodong-gi duto,
\q2 kaachiel gi pinje duto ma gitelonegi.
\q1 
\v 29 Piny tetni kendo nigi rem mapek,
\q1 nimar chenro mar Jehova Nyasaye
\q2 kuom Babulon osiko mondo piny Babulon odongʼ gunda,
\q2 maonge ngʼama nodag kanyo.
\q1 
\v 30 Jolwenj Babulon oseweyo kedo;
\q2 gidongʼ e kuondegi mochiel motegno mag lweny.
\q1 Tekogi orumo; gisebedo ka mon.
\q2 Kuondegi mag dak osemoke mach;
\q2 lodi mage mag rangeye otur.
\q1 
\v 31 Jangʼwech achiel luwo bangʼ
\q2 machielo kendo jaote luwo bangʼ jaote machielo,
\q1 mondo olandne ruodh Babulon
\q2 ni dalane maduongʼ mangima osemaki,
\q1 
\v 32 kuonde mikalogo aora osemuki,
\q2 odundu wangʼ,
\q2 kendo jolweny luoro omako.”
\p 
\v 33 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel, wacho:
\q1 “Nyar Babulon chalo gi kar
\q2 dino e seche minyone;
\q2 kinde ma ikaye chiegni chopo.”
\b
\q1 
\v 34 “Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon osetiekowa,
\q2 oserundo pachwa,
\q2 oselokowa agulu ma iye ninono.
\q1 Ka thuol osemuonyowa
\q2 kendo osepongʼo iye gi chiembwa,
\q2 mi osengʼudhowa oko.”
\q1 
\v 35 Joma odak Sayun wacho niya,
\q2 “Mad masira ma gisekelonwa bed kuom Babulon.”
\q1 Jerusalem wacho niya,
\q2 “Mad rembwa bed ewi joma odak Babulon.”
\p 
\v 36 Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
\q1 “Ne, anabed jakori kendo anakonyi e bura;
\q2 anami nembe two kendo thidhna mage notwo.
\q1 
\v 37 Babulon nobed pith mar kethruok,
\q2 kar dak ondiegi, gima bwogo ji,
\q1 kendo gima inyiero,
\q2 kama onge ngʼama odakie.
\q1 
\v 38 Joge duto ruto ka sibuoche matindo,
\q2 gilengʼore ka nyithi sibuor.
\q1 
\v 39 To ka ochiewgi,
\q2 analosnigi nyasi mi gimer,
\q1 mondo gikog gi mor;
\q2 eka ginindi nyaka chiengʼ ma ok ginichiew,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\q1 
\v 40 “Anatiekgi ka rombe mitero kar yengʼo,
\q2 ka imbe kod diek.
\b
\q1 
\v 41 “Mano kaka Sheshak nomaki,
\q2 sunga mar piny ngima norum!
\q1 Mano kaka Babulon nobedi
\q2 gima lich makelo bwok e kind ogendini!
\q1 
\v 42 Nam nogingre kuom Babulon;
\q2 apakane mawuo noume.
\q1 
\v 43 Miech jo-Babulon nodongʼ gunda,
\q2 kama otwo kendo piny motimo ongoro,
\q1 piny maonge ngʼama odakie,
\q2 kama onge ngʼama kalo e iye.
\q1 
\v 44 Anakum Bel e Babulon
\q2 kendo anami ongʼog gima ne osemuonyo.
\q1 Ogendini ok nochak ochokre ire.
\q2 Kendo ohinga mar Babulon nogore piny.
\b
\q1 
\v 45 “Wuoguru oko uayi kuome, joga!
\q2 Ringuru ukony ngimau!
\q2 Ringuru uaye mirima mager mar Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 46 Kik chunyu jogi kata bedo maluor
\q2 ka wach mofwongʼ owinjore e piny;
\q1 wach mofwongʼ achiel biro higani,
\q2 machielo noluwe,
\q1 wach mofwongʼ mar masira e piny,
\q2 kendo mar jatelo ma ok dwar,
\q2 jatelo machielo.
\q1 
\v 47 Nimar adiera kinde biro ma anakum
\q2 nyiseche manono mag Babulon;
\q1 pinye duto nobed gi wichkuot
\q2 kendo joge duto mosenegi nolware iye.
\q1 
\v 48 Eka polo gi piny kod gik moko duto manie igi
\q2 nokog gi ilo nikech Babulon,
\q1 nimar koa nyandwat
\q2 jonek nomonje,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 49 “Babulon nyaka podhi
\q2 nikech jo-Israel mane onegi,
\q1 mana kaka ji duto,
\q2 mosenegi e piny osepodho nikech Babulon.
\q1 
\v 50 Un joma osetonyne ligangla,
\q2 auru kendo kik ugalru!
\q1 Paruru Jehova Nyasaye e piny mabor,
\q2 kendo upar Jerusalem.”
\b
\q1 
\v 51 “Ochawa, nimar oseyanywa
\q2 kendo wichkuot oumo wengewa,
\q1 nikech joma oa e pinje mamoko
\q2 osedonjo e kuonde maler mar od Jehova Nyasaye.”
\b
\q1 
\v 52 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
\q2 “To kinde biro,
\q2 ma anakume nyisechege manono,
\q1 kendo e pinye mangima
\q2 joma nigi adhonde nobed gi rem malit.
\q1 
\v 53 Kata ka Babulon ochopo e lwasi
\q1 kendo ger ohingage motegno kuno,
\q2 to anaor ji mondo okethe,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye wacho.
\b
\q1 
\v 54 “Ywak winjore koa Babulon,
\q2 koko mar kethruok maduongʼ,
\q2 koa e piny jo-Babulon.
\q1 
\v 55 Jehova Nyasaye noketh Babulon;
\q2 nomi koko olingʼ thi.
\q1 Apaka mag wasigu nowuo ka pige mopongʼ;
\q2 koko mar dwondgi nowinjre kendo.
\q1 
\v 56 Jaketh nobi ketho Babulon;
\q2 jolweny mage nomaki,
\q2 kendo atungʼ mag-gi notur.
\q1 Nimar Jehova Nyasaye en Nyasaye
\q2 machulo kuor ni ji kuom richogi;
\q2 enochul duto.”
\q1 
\v 57 Ruoth, ma nyinge en Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho niya,
\q2 “Anami jodonge kod jogo mariek mer,
\q1 jotendgi, jodong-gi kod jolweny bende;
\q2 gininindi nyaka chiengʼ kendo ok ginichiew.”
\p 
\v 58 Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
\q1 “Ohinga mar Babulon mangʼongo nolwar piny
\q2 kendo dhorangeye mage maboyo nomoke mach;
\q1 ji chandore kayiem nono,
\q2 tich matek mar jotich en mana ramoki mach.”
\p 
\v 59 Ma e ote mane Jeremia janabi omiyo jatend jotije Seraya wuod Neria, ma wuod Maseya, kane odhi Babulon gi Zedekia ruodh Juda e higa mar angʼwen mar lochne.
\v 60 Jeremia nondiko e kitabu kuom masiche duto mano bi kuom Babulon, mago duto mane osendiki kuom Babulon.
\v 61 Nowachone Seraya, “Ka ichopo Babulon, ne ni isomo wechegi mondo owinji.
\v 62 Eka iwachi ni, yaye Jehova Nyasaye, isewacho ni ibiro ketho kae, mondo omi dhano kata le kik dag e iye; enodongʼ gunda nyaka chiengʼ.
\v 63 Ka itieko somo kitabuni, twe kidi kuome kendo idire Yufrate.
\v 64 Eka iwachi ni, ‘E kaka Babulon nonim ma ok nochak ochungʼ kendo nikech masira ma anakel kuome. Kendo joge nopodhi.’ ”
\p Weche Jeremia ogik kae.
\b
\c 52
\s1 Jerusalem opodho
\p 
\v 1 Zedekia ne ja-higni piero ariyo gachiel kane obedo ruoth, kendo nobedo e loch kodak Jerusalem kuom higni apar gachiel. Min mare ne nyinge Hamutal nyar Jeremia ma aa Libna.
\v 2 Ne otimo richo e nyim Jehova Nyasaye, mana kaka Jehoyakim notimo.
\v 3 Magi duto notimore ne Jerusalem kod Juda nikech mirimb Jehova Nyasaye, kendo giko to ne oriembogi oko e nyime.
\p Koro Zedekia nongʼanyone ruodh Babulon.
\p 
\v 4 Omiyo e higa mar ochiko mar loch Zedekia, e odiechiengʼ mar apar mar dwe mar apar, Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon nodhi gi jolweny mage duto momonjo Jerusalem. Negilworo dala maduongʼno kendo ne gigoyone agengʼa koni gi koni.
\v 5 Dala maduongʼno ne ogone agengʼa nyaka higa mar apar gachiel mar Ruoth Zedekia.
\p 
\v 6 E odiechiengʼ mar ochiko e dwe mar angʼwen kech mane ni e dala maduongʼno nomedore makoro ne onge chiemo mane ji nyalo chamo.
\v 7 Bangʼ mano ohinga mar dala maduongʼno nomuki, kendo jolweny duto noringo ka tony gotieno ka gikalo e rangach man e kind ohinga ariyo man but puoth ruoth, kata obedo ni jo-Babulon nolworo dala maduongʼno kamano. Negiringo ka gichomo Araba,
\v 8 to jolwenj Babulon nolawo Ruoth Zedekia kendo ojuke e pewe mag Jeriko. Jolweny mage duto noringo oweye moke,
\v 9 kendo negimake.
\p Ne gitere Ribla ir ruodh Babulon e piny Hamath, kama nongʼadone bura.
\v 10 E Ribla ruodh Babulon nonego yawuot Zedekia koneno; bende nonego jotelo duto mag Juda.
\v 11 Eka nogolo wenge Zedekia oko, notweye gi rateke mag mula kendo notere Babulon, kama ne okete e od twech nyaka chiengʼ mano thoe.
\p 
\v 12 E odiechiengʼ mar apar mar dwe mar abich, e higa mar apar gochiko mar loch Nebukadneza ruodh Babulon, Nebuzaradan jatend jolweny marito ruoth, ma en achiel kuom jodong ruodh Babulon, nobiro Jerusalem.
\v 13 Nowangʼo hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, kar dak ruoth kod udi duto man Jerusalem. Bende nowangʼo udi duto moger mabeyo.
\v 14 Jolweny duto mag Babulon mane ichiko gi jatend jolweny marito ruoth ne omuko ohinga duto moluoro Jerusalem.
\v 15 Nebuzaradan jatend jolweny notero e twech jomoko kuom joma odhier kod jogo mane odongʼ e dala maduongʼno, kaachiel gi jogo molony e tij lwedo kod joma noringo modhi ir ruodh Babulon mondo otony.
\v 16 To Nebuzaradan noweyo jopinyno moko mane odhier ahinya mondo oti e puothe mag mzabibu kod puothe mamoko.
\p 
\v 17 Jo-Babulon nomuko sirni mag mula, rachungi mag taya kod Karaya Maduongʼ mar mula mane ni e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye kendo ne gitero mulago duto nyaka Babulon.
\v 18 Bende negikawo agulni, opawo, gir ngʼado otambi mar taya, tewni mikwoyogo remo, bakunde kod gik moko duto molos gi mula mane itiyogo e hekalu.
\v 19 Jatend jolweny marito ruoth nokawo besen, gima iwangʼoe ubani, tewni mag kwoyo remo, agulni, rachung taya, dise kod bakunde mitiyogo e misango miolo piny, ma gin gik moko duto molos gi dhahabu maler kata fedha.
\p 
\v 20 Mula mane ogolo e sirni ariyo, gi Karaya Maduongʼ kod rwedhi apar gariyo mag mula e bwoye kod rachungi minyalo tingʼ mane Ruoth Solomon olosone hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye, ne pek ma ok nyal pim.
\v 21 Siro ka siro borne ne romo fut piero ariyo gochiko kendo alwora mare ne romo fut apar gochiko; sirnigo norokore kendo moro ka moro kore ne romo gi lith lwedo angʼwen.
\v 22 Gima chalo agulu mar mula mane ni e ewi achiel kuom sirni borne kadhi malo ne romo fut aboro kendo nokede gi gik mongʼinore ongʼinore molwore koni gi koni. Siro machielo man-gi gik mongʼinore ongʼinore, ne chal kod mokwongo.
\v 23 Ne nitiere gik mongʼinore ongʼinore piero ochiko gauchiel e bethe sirni, kwan gik mongʼinore ongʼinore duto ne gin mia achiel mane olworo gima otwangʼ mongʼith.
\p 
\v 24 Jatend jolweny marito ruoth nomako Seraya jadolo maduongʼ, gi Zefania jadolo maluwe kod ji adek ma jorit dhoot hekalu moterogi e twech.
\v 25 To kuom joma ne odongʼ e dala maduongʼno, nomako jatelo mane ochungʼ ne jolweny, kod ji abiriyo ma jongʼad rieko ne ruoth. Bende nomako jagoro mane tichne en ndiko nying joma onego bed jolweny kod jodonge piero auchiel mane oyudi e dala maduongʼno.
\v 26 Nebuzaradan jatend lweny nomakogi duto mokelogi Ribla ir ruodh Babulon.
\v 27 Ruoth nogolo chik mondo neg-gi Ribla kanyo, e piny jo-Hamath.
\p Omiyo Juda noter e twech mabor gi pinye owuon.
\b
\li4 
\v 28 Ma e kwan mar joma Nebukadneza notero e twech:
\b
\li1 e higa mar abiriyo,
\li2 mane gin jo-Yahudi alufu adek gi piero adek;
\li1 
\v 29 e hik Nebukadneza mar apar gaboro,
\li2 ji mia aboro gi piero adek gariyo moa Jerusalem;
\li1 
\v 30 e hike mar piero ariyo gadek,
\li2 jo-Yahudi mia abiriyo gi piero angʼwen gabich mane oter e twech gi Nebuzaradan jatend lweny.
\b
\li4 Giduto ne gin ji alufu angʼwen mia auchiel.
\s1 Owe Jehoyakin thuolo
\p 
\v 31 E higa mar piero adek gabiriyo mar twech Jehoyakin ruodh Juda, e higa mane Evil-Merodak obedo ruodh Babulon, nogonyo Jehoyakin ruodh Juda kendo oweye thuolo koa e od twech e odiechiengʼ mar piero ariyo gabich mar dwe mar apar gariyo.
\v 32 Nowuoyo kode modembore kendo nomiye kom duongʼ moloyo ruodhi mamoko mane ni kode e twech Babulon.
\v 33 Omiyo Jehoyakin nolonyo lepe mag twech kendo e ndalo ngimane duto ne ochiemo pile pile e mesa ruoth.
\v 34 Odiechiengʼ ka odiechiengʼ ruodh Babulon ne miyo Jehoyakin pok mowinjore kode ndalo duto mag ngimane, nyaka odiechiengʼno mar thone.
